user_reviews:
[{"Name":"M C","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKZ_diJewspKl-rtdK-yzYnT9VYU8RttfU8VKK76Lwr1oeoUKU=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I had the in person and ordering to home experience and both were fantastic. This is now my go to pizza spot! Cute vibes & branding is on point. Order the Mama Pizza & the ranch dip 🤤💖","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMJngyh6P0KU-DSgE4YU5H0kEVDwgL7sb79Xu08&fid=0x0:0x44ef86e8c9ac4499"],"When":"2024-12-22"},{"Name":"Phyllis Tee","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXtHTl5JLpAHiaGIa8m_bWtHrZ84dJMWFq9MtMaT4ZwV6hFBwY=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Mama said this place will be my go-to for pizzas and they did not disappoint. Had the Caesar salad to start with—it was banging! Garlicky and mixed with a few arugula leaves which I thought was so smart. Just full of punch and flavour that elevated the entire dish. And not too heavy on the dressing, it wasn’t soggy, which was great. Not your typical Caesar salad for sure.

For pizza, we had The Brooklyn 16”—perfect for two ppl. The crust was gorgeously thin. Would love to see more toppings on my pizza, as well as an option for a cheese stuffed crust if I wasn’t watching my figure. Overall, would def come back again.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMs1B2FwdvaXK1ovjelshizAyYcS23PU47l64Ah&fid=0x0:0x44ef86e8c9ac4499"],"When":"2024-9-4"},{"Name":"Jennifer Bee","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXFO0fgPBTIA1yxL3IXSghRJ6EmshLC1YB1a72b-xeg3kpjHx0=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Edit: added more pictures after our recent visit. We don’t recommend the cocktail, all ice and didn’t feel worth the price.

Great pizza joint with tasty food. We’ve had The Mama which we love, and this visit we had the vegetarian Hugh Fungus with the honey crust added on. It was delicious and we’re very happy to have Mama Said within walking distance of our house.

We got the large and had two slices left over.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMCPxBPEsCz8G89G13t83XCCujmqAFLJ6tPYPcY&fid=0x0:0x44ef86e8c9ac4499"],"When":"2024-6-7"},{"Name":"Jenny Anderson (jennycanderson)","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV5zBrQ2SgSAq7cjPWmWTgRLDBFty535Ptns-qCKJ_Edl0iJO-X=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Came on a late Sunday night and the restaurant had a really nice vibe to it. We ordered The Mama pizza, house wine, and happy hour beer -  it was amazing! Really big fans of the sesame and honey crust without the crust dough being too floppy. This is a solid neighbourhood pizza joint and I’d recommend it to anyone around the Port Moody Area 👍 note: wish they had their own chilli oil","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipME5WieBbKfmxWt4TiNUd1dnNMtMmSOU0uA8xTs&fid=0x0:0x44ef86e8c9ac4499"],"When":"2024-8-26"},{"Name":"Khasha Shariati","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW9BRwWPJBkIcOPMqU92TxMjsbdN__O-S3D_jQsct6oG5_sIP8Z=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Loved the food, service was great and friendly. You can use the parking of the park on the other side of the street.
The only thing is you should expect some wait time on weekends.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPKNcX7miz_Xqlg7iU3K6ZnTFr9Qyby1RqDh_JL&fid=0x0:0x44ef86e8c9ac4499"],"When":"2024-10-12"},{"Name":"Kaarun Sangra","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocILM8njwXrPcLqUou598doTsuDXD8kBZ5RbuqqE4bvPJRwsig=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Came to enjoy a margarita pizza and left with this. I’ve had Margarita pizza’s all over America, Europe, and Asia and never had something this disappointing. Would not recommend at all especially with the number of great pizza places in the Port Moody area","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP9CcbgRcsmx0rF-Ysy6sWxnxcWWMALKK1h8W-S&fid=0x0:0x44ef86e8c9ac4499"],"When":"2024-9-19"},{"Name":"Grace Kelly Santos","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUUF4o9qd2WloJZmZE9gqsW_gPcnkYH82wsKD5Jxnr7KgMgi9wosA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"It was the first time we went to Mama Said Pizza, and we will definitely come back! We were so politely welcomed! I asked for a coconut mocktail that was not on the menu and the host who was also the bartender prepared a WONDERFUL drink with pineapple and coconut, super delicious, I haven't tried like that anywhere else! She was so kind in looking for it and preparing a new drink!

The food and drinks are high quality ! The pizza crust and the tops taste delicious! Fair price and super tasty!

The pizza chefs are extremely professional! What a delicious pizza! Super recommend you to try your choice with honey crust!

Thank you for the amazing experience! We will be back!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"May Zhagro","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU9KviWdU_UGm6yjKPv-6aFaljm1EC_ecrxYhnt_LO3duiyBNho=s120-c-rp-mo-ba7-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"It was not very busy when we went on a Thursday evening so we didn’t have to wait for them to accommodate us. We got drinks and 2 large pizza to share which was enough for about 2 slices each with 2 extra slices (so about 5 slices per pizza). We ordered the Pine and Swine and the Mama. Both were thin crust pizza. The Pine & Swine with the bacon and pineapple was tasty, if you like a little sweetness in your pizza. The Mama pizza wasn’t very special with honey drizzled sesame, but doesn’t feel worth the $30 price tag. Overall, the experience with ok, but I wanted a bit more sauce and cheese on the pizza. The revolving tap of sour beer was good. The server was able to divide the pizza bill by the number of people. Street parking only.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOuRbAMYvqBf3Z3tjTJNJkBE_VRb5Yu-9doO4e4&fid=0x0:0x44ef86e8c9ac4499"],"When":"2023-8-4"}]

user_reviews:
[{"Name":"Melanie Mulrooney","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLHd2cxrpI_pchboHb9eIUdso9cP_-GfRg9kUkxFQcOFdGy1A=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Ate here for the first time ever tonight and it was absolutely fantastic. The service was so polite and fast, right from the door everyone was friendly and welcoming. Most of all though, the food was amazing! The portions are huge for the cost and so delicious. Especially the cowboy roll I could eat it everyday and never get tired of it. I will be back and with everyone I know.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNdLx2z33bPfZ4k0eLJoWyGA8uqy13dZuDLdB_H&fid=0x0:0xe1616bd724b15843"],"When":"2024-8-20"},{"Name":"Monica H","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKTrPwE-6Cd7iIRIuu8XvTY7oNDQ7n3Z8oGGtpeXzyQCGdP4os=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"My favourite Japanese restaurant in Canada (comparing Alberta, BC & Ontario).  I’ve ordered many times for takeout and dined a few times as well, the price and portions are great and the best time to go is before 3pm.

The popcorn roll, dynamite and teriyaki bento boxes are the top 3 items I order. If I’m ever in the area, I’ll definitely return.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPp1A3CcTC0_fYWHsOIJIZQP8Niqodd9n4Tt9PE&fid=0x0:0xe1616bd724b15843"],"When":"2024-7-25"},{"Name":"Suzanna Wu","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJu0K1rzqjRHKO0oWuWjGEOdpby-gz1hPeO05yd80XdU5qi2yw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"I was nearby for work, so I grabbed a simple lunch with my mom at this restaurant on Thursday. The first server, a lady, guided us to our seats and helped us order two lunch deals and an additional side. The food tasted fine, and the prices were okay. The environment was decent, but the service was shockingly rude.

When my mom asked for takeout boxes and the bill, a different, younger male server came by, literally tossed the boxes onto the table, and walked away. When he returned with the bill and card machine, he dropped them on the table and left again without a word. It was the worst dining experience I've ever had. He didn’t say a single sentence to us the entire time, and I wondered how he was even qualified to be a server. I still paid the 12% tip because I was in a rush and a client was messaging me. Miraculously, the moment he saw I left a tip, he finally said, 'Thank you.'

If I hadn’t been in a rush, I would’ve found the manager and asked if this is how they treat customers. To top it off, as we were finishing our conversation and about to leave, the first lady server came up and started clearing the table while we were still sitting, with food still on the table. Asking a simple question like, 'Is it okay to take your plates away?' wouldn’t have hurt. I’m genuinely curious—is it that hard for them to communicate with customers? I understand wanting to clean up, but all the tables around us were empty.

I felt like we were being treated like parasites, where no one wanted to serve us. I will never visit this place again—no one on earth should be treated like that.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPLNfDxJ8jGJAfNSew8RsXJy3wea-XdqoQ4OSpK&fid=0x0:0xe1616bd724b15843"],"When":"2024-9-15"},{"Name":"Stephanie Leigh","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKRl-iaFLQxQ8oJ72otIPqBzU4rYUb-w4AClnbcEnjWvh00AA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Apologies to my former fav sushi restaurant but, Hanayuki is officially my new favorite Sushi Restaurant in the lower mainland.
The food came out so quickly, the staff were super friendly and accommodating despite us arriving an hour before closing, and the atmosphere was warm with very cozy seating.
It is close to some popular local spots like Rocky Point, Belcara, Sasamat Lake, and Buntzen so we will be back again regularly which is an absolute treat.
The quality of the food and fish was unparalleled and the miso soup really hit the spot after a cold swim. My friend had the Tonkatsu which she said was the best she has had in a long time and the closest to what she makes at home.
I really recommend the Salmon Run Roll and the Tataki Attack Roll. The gyoza is very crispy and the Toro melts in your mouth.
I cannot wait to go again and bring more of our family too!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPoDc_shstlRAb1k3wHWMpiQv4qTwgkF8EXiqKf&fid=0x0:0xe1616bd724b15843"],"When":"2024-8-20"},{"Name":"Jennifer Bee","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXFO0fgPBTIA1yxL3IXSghRJ6EmshLC1YB1a72b-xeg3kpjHx0=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I took my son out for a Pro D day lunch. We got a rainbow roll, tiger roll, dynamite roll and avocado roll. Everything was tasty and fresh. Portions were good and we left full and content. They have a good assortment of vegetarian rolls but today we were pescatarians. My son loves the sign “No sushi, no life.” It’s his motto in life for sure.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM1-lWx61tuxmvYeQnLB8ZYH-P0TR12utVlDWY9&fid=0x0:0xe1616bd724b15843"],"When":"2024-4-29"},{"Name":"Joanna Fahmy","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJTznlA_q5Xa6Whv5wHF-yEDXEyOSOXOXBiPU7xtZRDBuF4Yw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"My favourite sushi in port moody. Highly recommend their crazy papa roll! So so good and the mixture of flavours is just insane. It is a little spicy for those who aren’t huge on spicy food. Their sashimi is also very fresh and the sauce is delicious. Another go to order is the spicy salmon combo, substitute kappa to crunch spicy scallop roll!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP59tWeoTlv5Ni-lmOd1IsFfw0WDL6WowdfLdHw&fid=0x0:0xe1616bd724b15843"],"When":"2024-11-19"},{"Name":"Lisa","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXaFyseBvst_Ep_Om0q5Ke-UzHllJ0CbiSVlWMRbj-1zn4_pkVt=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Visiting Vancouver from Alberta - we definitely dont have this quality of sushi out on the prairies! Everything tasted very fresh and was in big portions, great service and atmosphere. I love the traditional wooden look inside.

We tried the mafia roll, cowboy roll, salmon aburi and all of it was 5/5! Highly recommend!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOctzmDWU8SygxC5_GMbx0GN1pqIuY76y-4HRig&fid=0x0:0xe1616bd724b15843"],"When":"2023-9-25"},{"Name":"Simon L","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWC0zQL6UZOSMX25id4oWvss3Ml7IDzVRG0Otr-hJf-87BjawWQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"Got takeout from this place a couple of times already but it seems like the chef changed. Quality of the sushi is not as good as before.

Check out the Salmon Oshi that I picked up today. More like “Salmon O-Char” to me. In addition, the spicy chicken yakisoba was way too salty with uncooked vegetables (give my best regards to your lazy chef)","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOaL0SIs1xCd_TN2maXKHaT1J2vk9Wat8GukErJ&fid=0x0:0xe1616bd724b15843"],"When":"2024-8-9"}]

user_reviews:
[{"Name":"J. C.","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocI1q1dOhG5HB2xoBVTZNXXzXmiqMJtOcZ6a0GYAiGJW3nLPvw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Ordered one fish tacos (two shells) for $14 and one pulled pork tacos (three shells) for $14.
Fish was mediocre at its best but the pulled pork was so dry and tasteless. There were very stingy with the toppings as the pulled pork tacos only came with a bit of onions and cilantro. I love tacos but really had to force myself to finish these tiny tacos since i was famished.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNINbzqlB8jZCSuJQWxe5TmUFnKRppTsIVYC_4x&fid=0x0:0x478eaa0f9502ab2d"],"When":"2024-8-16"},{"Name":"Spoke Spurr","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU6SBXwfGoUXIMfCRHI82vggrz0MEiQ4COzIjzyCQuY_w8CfkTv=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Bland, tasteless greasy foods.
We had high hopes but they were shattered after first bite. Where can we get a refried bean burrito?!?!
Chicken Quesadilla was dripping grease, my black bean burrito was tasteless and the fish tacos came in at a 2.5 out of 5.
I added salt and lime from a margarita and it woke up their pico de gallo…no rocket science here.
This truck needs spice and flavour. Give it a miss and save the $$","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipODcvW-QaSraQgGtScqf6AUP72YUyfUPUfqDHZA&fid=0x0:0x478eaa0f9502ab2d"],"When":"2023-6-18"},{"Name":"Joanne Shih","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXximxdR2J0MX38SMpQXvX83o69PGyHXNObNbbK0mDK-tz8T9Z6=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"We were looking for some small bits for super, then we spotted this taco place. Their fish taco was delicious and a perfect portion as an evening snack! Take the tacos with you and go for a walk at Rocky Point park💯👌🏻","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPwq6_5S_AE7AX6XhgXnHqPOn4n6ZguKYpKMtFc&fid=0x0:0x478eaa0f9502ab2d"],"When":"2023-4-9"},{"Name":"Mehr Poulad","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKnMmsASCmXLOvaFhR1RoQ03vxNx7oVUBdwy_npEYvb7k7uZA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Located across from Rocky Point Park along the breweries. Quick service and decent food. Ordered the tacos and the burrito bowl. Found the meat in both to be slightly dry, also could have given us more sauce. Otherwise good bang for your buck. Make sure to get your food to go and eat it in the park.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPQ-lnUa5eHCJdf_lvQhQdquCjeccw-MdOIbnUT&fid=0x0:0x478eaa0f9502ab2d"],"When":"2021-8-31"},{"Name":"M M","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXmOHyzKEr32AYuRtdRx0_fLK77WJE7dN83mGqqAjLeQ_ZcBQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"Nice spot for a food truck 🙂

I got the BC tacos, veggie, pulled pork and chicken. They were ok. I felt they were lacking flavour. They almost tasted steamed.
The veggies were fresh and the sauces were good.

My experience was just ok. Glad to see it’s popular with others 🙂","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNcjCaA4MJKKCV_wapJMDsYfFEA3IktWxIMaSk&fid=0x0:0x478eaa0f9502ab2d"],"When":"2021-9-21"},{"Name":"Christi C","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXcgq9JpIfJ5HaJSvpqHkX5vNrbeeAgd7PrWra2BvtkmNmgVJax=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"Found the pulled pork a bit dry, could do with more sauce.

The vegetarian option doesn’t come with sauce to hold it together by default. May try purchasing guacamole on top next time to see if that stops most of the insides from falling out.

The green sauce (salsa verde?) goes well with the tacos.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"s moroziuk","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVr8VXW1Tth-zG1pgiwZz_oJWlTywq-szf3O9fv1DdZyUVPZb4=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"this is my favourite new spot for the summer. great loaded fish tacos, better than the other truck that is nearby, no shade just my opinion. fish tacos bigger than average so not bad for the price. perfect amount of food to go with a couple afternoon beers.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Alice Crawford","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU2SzzQ6gpXkIAIBnJKknqtE3iS4SvW3gLX0WuNUSCyLbZCtTEu=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Fish tacos were very disappointing! The batter was soaking wet. Could not taste mango. The tortilla stuck to paper and to each other so the whole thing fell apart.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMBTx_kq7CKdAAdsniQVPWttRDXpu86eQyAfKfE&fid=0x0:0x478eaa0f9502ab2d"],"When":"2024-10-12"}]

user_reviews:
[{"Name":"Annie Yu","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUMh7GPmb-fwTeblPqWA2SYP6eaRbXDOeK0rRGXojq0IfUHF2Je=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"Here is an honest review of the place:
Food:
- $10 for oyako don: price is a huge plus; taste was only okay… I don’t think there was enough sauce to mask the rubber texture of the chicken
- my friends had the $50 omakase. I saw the chef pulled out a long string of fish(?)/thread(?) from the sushi he put on the plate

Atmosphere:
- the place was super hot and humid, but overtime you get used to it
- the bathroom felt very much so like your grandparent’s bathroom, but paired with the fact I saw the kitchen looked a bit not well kept, but it didn’t gave me the best feeling
- the place is dead silent minus for the weirdly EDM Christmas music that kept stopping every 5 seconds (internet issue?)

Service:
- I can tell that the chef was trying to be friendly and funny, and for the most part we are okay with his joke and can overlook the tongue licking facial expressions he kept making, but the comment “it’s mine, is that okay?” When introducing the cod sperm sushi did not sit well for my friends and I… they both had a VERY good time swallowing the cod sperm sushi after he implied it was his (as a joke)","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPMz3-yOGLJSs5S0EWfWlTjMy8Z6HHXBOrZMiJY&fid=0x0:0x3db6e525b9a50cf5"],"When":"2024-12-9"},{"Name":"M K","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocII0XcYP3SfdZBPOqngapfVh5eio0lKp2iJqZrCn4YcukHZpw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The best and cheapest Omakase in lower mainland! We had omakase (I think it was 10-12 pieces?) and was only $40. The same quality of Omakase would cost $100+ in downtown.
The owner was very funny and told us that he orders everything from Japan every week! We had the best Toro(tuna belly) and it just melts in your mouth!!
If you know and love the authentic sushi, you’d love his sushi! Reservations are recommended","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPMg3R_cPofqeHddASQ-5cXMFDce1MLFrCJ_pBo&fid=0x0:0x3db6e525b9a50cf5"],"When":"2024-10-1"},{"Name":"judy chu","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocK5w-zmBNCh0IyRLZLy-Id0COwX4MxWUhgV1WMifEiDbtJPXcQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Cutest old couples. Very kind and sweet. Food is delicious!!! Taste of Japan right here.

Deluxe nigiri (photo0","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM_CJxcvLXkeQGHdbnyWRyJMkD-DcCsmjciIHzB&fid=0x0:0x3db6e525b9a50cf5"],"When":"2024-11-17"},{"Name":"David Wen","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVZ9GW9cg7ygsrrOKukomV-yFo1z_yA2Ehen1FFtQQmEEyIbJmBTw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Some of the best affordable sashimi I've ever had in the lower mainland. Pretty close to the quality of fish you would get in Japan. Omakase is $40 and the assorted Sashimi platter is $50. These prices are unheard of around here considering you would pay $100 most of the time for high end Sushi.

Be sure to book reservations in advance as this place is very popular and bring cash!

Owner can be a big grumpy at times and his English isn't the best but he makes some good sushi!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOYeh5mpcssmVg5B5mLo09HBgzwVlXqfu_3Lsmh&fid=0x0:0x3db6e525b9a50cf5"],"When":"2023-10-18"},{"Name":"Suwon Lee","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIIbb9_dyj1049CwJRax4tWBwCkrJ2WI0r6e9VSO9CldG7ABQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"The food was great, but Kazu and Toshi would be better options if you are looking for sushi restaurants run by Japanese. I had a deluxe nigiri set, and it was excellent. The service was a bit slow since one elderly couple runs the place. Also, the owner doesn't seem to like to have kids in the restaurant. It's better to make a reservation if you have younger kids.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMiHFIyipQrB3Htm568tk0aWgWe1VMxXRupOzvD&fid=0x0:0x3db6e525b9a50cf5"],"When":"2024-3-5"},{"Name":"Amy Wu","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKvtm7hBqZHDYxXgP_oxkelx2FGhwfW-EuwTv9rdyjxo-_-_8Nq=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I’ve been wanting to come for almost ten years and I was not disappointed. We arrived right at 5pm when they opened because we didn’t have a reservation. It’s opened by an old Japanese couple who run the restaurant by themself. Their $40 omakase is a bang for your buck. If you sit at a table you’re served the whole plate of omakase, but if you sit at the bar it’s one by one. We also tried a few other dishes and they were all pretty good. Really liked the plum shiso roll too, simple but fragrant.  I need to try the chirashi don next time! Service is not very attentive given it’s just two people running the restaurant but they are nice. I want to come back again!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOrnraCYyhSuYSskOKQx0JRdhonbwiuTf1sabYg&fid=0x0:0x3db6e525b9a50cf5"],"When":"2024-1-7"},{"Name":"Raveen","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVjUuq53nJPIAhZcJAN_mF7AUvI35Sl1JPAsDptgRmApgEX6Han=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Was recommended by someone to visit this place and it did not disappoint! We came on a Sunday evening around 6:30pm and there were plenty of seats. Most of the fish tasted fresh and it was a good deal! Would recommend the sashimi platter as all pieces were tasty and fresh! The rice was quite fresh and warm so it would fall apart when using chopsticks but it was a minor issue! The owners were friendly. They easily split the bill although not speaking much english. Would recommend this place!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMhhkixetbktuIjk7_61JQ6h1JOtsPKdTqg_lb8&fid=0x0:0x3db6e525b9a50cf5"],"When":"2023-11-7"},{"Name":"Y. Cherski","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocK-7SLlKKRW0Rqcp9wRXFlvt6gbh0rtI7PMIroLgxETtGiPwQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"A fascinating establishment. Run by an elderly couple, it is one of a very few Japanese joints in Lower Mainland offering an old-school setup where it's best to get seated in front of the chef and see him preparing food for you. Ingredients are exceptional. They offer fish that is very hard to find in other Japanese restaurants. Also, it is suitable for different budgets where you can get very affordable donburi and more common rolls, or something more exotic at a higher price. You shouldn't expect quick service here, and there is no problem with that – this place offers a unique atmosphere that is more important than the speed of service. It might not be for everyone, but I think this restaurant deserves more attention.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPYrztfuiCI_6sBkrcVs-DSzjrhAhNQfYXJYLgE&fid=0x0:0x3db6e525b9a50cf5"],"When":"2020-9-11"}]

[{"Name":"장민","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocK90us3Gcwq48qfQCsSB0ooW1tkDEG9RtVDQtgcR-Sa57rtyQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"We saw an advertisement paper so we visited. We and another team were only customers in the restaurants. I think most of the people use pick up or delivery system.

I ordered steak&robster because I thought their signature menu is that. (Their name is golphis “steak&robster”.) For the price(about $60) it was not worthy. The steak was okay but a little bit smelly and the mushrooms as well. And the lobster was too salty for us. Even it took 40 minutes for the food to come out so we were more disappointed🥲 The Lasagna was okay..

The server didn’t explain if I order substitute side menu, there will be an extra fee.. So we asked about it again and she explained. And I wish she would explain about the use of dipping sauce and oil.

The parking spot was enough but the way to there was a little bit confusing.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNIgrQdlytrqRznxpxtCy4C8-pE0AhHuVagNK1q&fid=0x0:0xc7efa4c77f184e2"],"When":"2024-7-21"},{"Name":"G W","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVG1FFo9GTnRGQNpjln74dhjBn3V4nGRQE_Yjur_OV6HYJsv04F_g=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"it's been 35 years, inside decor all new. Guests had steak Nd lobster, okay. My lobster was two small one. Not at all what I expected for   $35 - $50 plates.
When you call yourself Steak & Lobster, they should take care in serving much better lobster. Lobster butter was watery, vegetables ok and baked potatoes serving in foil!? Sourcream butter ect in cheap serving plastic Togo containers.
only three tables taken and No service to speak of. Just a guy saying hello loud to everyone walking in the door. Table set all wrong. Not a 5 star diner, Have them a 3 because new decor. Maybe it's the pizza.
Should be Golphis Pizza and Pasta.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOSwsnJZZehLckSI6AIG1Axw2bjlFqhINWoygvH&fid=0x0:0xc7efa4c77f184e2"],"When":"2022-9-11"},{"Name":"Eric Cheng","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWOyg3d6oaJTu5sdvuUVJNteYVGj_1LBSkeQ_4988ARhRbaxE43Ew=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"Had the 12oz top sirloin with 'the works' - lasagna. Veggies were super crisp, but for an upscale place dressing should not be served in plastic containers. 3stars for fine-dining prices for decent meal. Server was professional, but unsure of cuts meat and bar menu.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO7ohdj5WADdyN8nQcEYOwZqFph3PuyR4vllnnh&fid=0x0:0xc7efa4c77f184e2"],"When":"2018-9-26"},{"Name":"Mike Schindelka","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXsQsd3KNCHBUKE0sX-qAuHJ4tdh1XtOdUka1Yg7aOnuxrtH5RY=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Outstanding quality and flavor. The cheese is real mozzarella, the sauces are  flavorful and original tasting. Excellent balance of Savory, sweet, and spices. The pizza crust is outstanding and the toppings are fresh. The baked ravioli pasta  was amazing as well. I added Italian sausage and the Italian sausage was authentic.  I will definitely be coming again","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPEeOaqej98826w11wVIJ8yF-bZ_3nFyRAnrEc9&fid=0x0:0xc7efa4c77f184e2"],"When":"2021-9-9"},{"Name":"Inna Koshel","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVGmxK1BFHMoEk4sy6UOZm8a43HkVwMkzIqy9mccsb94-8WQXWx=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We really liked the pizza, lots of toppings and crispy dough. I look forward to trying some of their other dishes.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Amy","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLmzE1RlRKdVxVlGaNakllTFUg-dwBxvHV6swqHb5but5IlJg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"Food was average. Steak was bland no seasoning , lobster was over cooked but okay at least had some salt on it . Pizza wasn’t anything special ,  Service was meh took some time to get our food , there was only 4 people in the restaurant I had finished my drink and no one came to even ask if I wanted anything","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Ginn J","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIFOOQZPhZylsgMOLmtSB5bJOkt-NwtAZ31Ulkb5_TUEpijBg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We were lucky to go on game day so it wasn't busy. [{"Name":"Kristopher Susilo","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJBtEhlXkRJMy2FnW55lvERwkpk2-F5eMFH_4N0FgO25PS_ew=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I can guarantee whoever gives this restaurant less than 5 stars either because they are not used to the typical “rude” but caring service by the aunties OR they just dont know what to order thats actually good.

First time here and I was impressed with the food taste. Ordered 4 item combo: shanghai style crispy chicken, fish & tofu hot/clay pot, greenbeans with beef and house special chowmein. Combo includes free rice, (lobak, carrots & beef) soup and dessert (mango pudding or red bean soup). It was too much for 4 of us and we had to pack some home.

Will definitely come back.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPnhlxnsyLRRJEHh4fzVtiLgMOmMBDi22sds4lU&fid=0x0:0xd5411af39ffb3fa8"],"When":"2024-11-9"},{"Name":"Shirley Fung","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXSf2s-kJuEfRzH7n0u0o-Ty-eDTJZIvAb-cR6BzmkEs9eHNYN_=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"we had the 2 dishes dinner combo and it was so disappointing… the soup was the best thing about the meal. the crispy chicken was so bland. the server persuaded me to pay to upgrade the steamed fish to black cod but it was so disappointing. there’s no taste to it aside from few black beans on top. the sauce was watery and the texture of the fish was so mushy. you thought one thing you can count on for Chinese food is the saltiness of soy sauce, they didn’t even have that 🥲 the servers were generally nice but the cleanliness of one of the chefs and bathroom was bad.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO9FKinfJPsrJa8WvhmtHG9gBLSigOBIsDlKCi_&fid=0x0:0xd5411af39ffb3fa8"],"When":"2024-9-20"},{"Name":"EVAN ETHAN","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVUx4wFf5gaB1lR1A8XX5kn8xelbVXHG8-xFycDrpZ-n6j0ewpV=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"ORDERED BEEF FRIED RICE - $20 w tax - NOT WORTH IT! Better off ordering a beef dish.

Taste is OK but hardly any beef inside ( probably just 1 table spoon of TINY BITS of beef in one order).","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNypKE1WWfEfipQcw4XUmfNtSKtUTTkxRfhMFSD&fid=0x0:0xd5411af39ffb3fa8"],"When":"2024-12-5"},{"Name":"Ha Dinh","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUcQG83kIM9L7VU9GS6J74J_TBMCdyvkYzp1C5XJSr_quttlO0V2A=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Really giving me the feeling of home-cooked meals. Tastes so similar to the food I had at home in Guangzhou. Dinner comes with soup and dessert. They keep rice warm in a small (red) bucket, really makes me reminisce the past. Portion is big, we ordered 3 dishes for 3 people, and still have enough for lunch the next day. Would totally come back 💛","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMvaLQtA4z_pvmNVnI8Kh1Z7qHpl_QKC50N4LrF&fid=0x0:0xd5411af39ffb3fa8"],"When":"2024-5-21"},{"Name":"Y. Cherski","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocK-7SLlKKRW0Rqcp9wRXFlvt6gbh0rtI7PMIroLgxETtGiPwQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"We ordered delivery from here before and decided to visit in person once in the area. The interior has seen its better days, so the interior vibe is drab. However, our waitress was friendly and communicative. We decided to go for a combo for two, and she recommended against one of the options we chose. I'm not sure what it was about, but our food was outstanding. I should mention that portions are huge. We got at least half of it to go. Prices are very reasonable, and there are many more options than listed in the delivery menu. If you are after nice looking interior and a cozy atmosphere, this place is not for you, but if you want yummy Chinese food for a very reasonable price, give it a chance.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP3Kz8AXC00TZcQEoR0U3SjODyiZU7llSsIe00y&fid=0x0:0xd5411af39ffb3fa8"],"When":"2022-8-9"},{"Name":"Daniel Li","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUAxFTfz_ZYgM60gsStYArKOb4YgmHuHArMEsVm-TJD2WcKuo33=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"Had dinner here at Chinese New Year, service is consider good during this busy days.  The food is just average, the Deep Fried spicy squid and the deep fried lobster with spice chilli is a must try, others are mostly on average.  I would not recommend the hot and sour soup nor the
Singapore Stir-fried Noodles to anyone, their signature chicken are just fine as well.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOUZrsZslO2nY-auGLnWPWIk0Myi4-rLW0d4KVx&fid=0x0:0xd5411af39ffb3fa8"],"When":"2023-1-24"},{"Name":"Scott Lee","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXHpW7vGME__Zs4wKjXR04Upnw88bkVVyz-H2288JsHocq9vI3r=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"We had a great experience here! One of the better Chinese restaurants in the lower mainland.

I really liked their crispy squid and the sweet and sour pork. I also highly recommend their egg and shrimp! The egg was very silky and rich which perfectly complemented the shrimp. I want to try their Peking duck next time.

I recommend this place if anyone is around the area!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMJRfvhGAZpzBC7snM4pEnjwIvrGKpQzy8W21Cu&fid=0x0:0xd5411af39ffb3fa8"],"When":"2024-3-5"},{"Name":"Jaime Ricafrente","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXAJwwcGATN2RuHMthkyt1rjxVqb7NF_uxVYPAzS1OSfFJWO9Wn6g=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"It's my first time here.  I ordered the Crispy Chicken with Soy Sauce, Dp Fried Spicey Prawn, egg plant Clay Pot.  If you want a quick answer, EAT HERE ITS AMAZING!  Food is not salty, prawn not to coated, just AMAZING FOOD.  The Lotus soup was sooo good.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP_dl1fR5wGDp97NMcI-nCS-1kz2NQOLv04voK2&fid=0x0:0xd5411af39ffb3fa8"],"When":"2023-12-18"}]

[{"Name":"Karen Guy","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVcU8w6XlCIvy293JkoRWxLMnBPbdHS5nCGBD01RKpPw2aLTi0F=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"That's a really really good Trinidadian restaurant with authentic food and a very friendly owner who makes the food perfectly every time.

Keep in mind it is takeout and cash only if you want to order doubles, you have to order it 24 hours in advance.

I highly recommend this restaurant.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Randy Sachs","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWWQuAWV7KPRZ224WOrJuSu3B6tYP_OJQzmmhJwiMLpDNtt9O1kHA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I've eaten a few Roti in my life and I'm very sure that Rehanahs is the best in the west coast hands down. Only time I've tasted anything close to hers was in Toronto. Rehanahs got west coast on lock. 🔐👑👑","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNCFVckHaNX_Hqw25dgd1CwcDB9JAusx_1wuPGT&fid=0x0:0xf47ebe6d461915ed"],"When":"2020-10-27"},{"Name":"Josephine Ma","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW4ctBP8R2rm9S8Aa5NyuULMapTvyTQYakS6AvI9Cd025oSy86H=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"My husband offered to take my daughter and I to Rehanah's Roti Shop in Port Moody, and I jumped at the opportunity to go there. It had been a few years since we last went there and I'd been itching to go there for awhile. As the name of the shop implies, they serve Roti, but not just any Roti...they serve Trinidadian style Roti. My mother was born and raised in Trinidad, so Trinidadian food holds a special place in my heart.

Trinidadian Roti is basically a wrap sandwich that's filled with curried meat, vegetable or seafood filling. There's dhalpourie roti or paratha roti (also known as bussup shut). Rehanah's Roti sells dhalpourie roti. Difference between dhalpourie and bussup shut? The explanation I've heard is that bussup shut is "busted up" into tattered pieces.

Roti: We ordered Shrimp Roti and Mixed Veggie Roti. Awesome flavour; however the filling is heavy with potatoes and sparse on the other ingredients. The Vegetarian Rotis are all under $10; however, the meat and seafood Rotis can be a bit pricey considering how much of the Roti is filled with potato.

Service: Fair (One woman running the entire shop. She takes the order, runs the till, and makes the food.)
Parking: Free street parking
Location: On St. Johns St., which is a main street lined with shops and restaurants in Port Moody.

It's a very small restaurant and as a result of the pandemic they only do takeout. There is however, a small table and chairs to sit and wait while your order is being prepared.There are so few places that serve Trinidadian food. This place is a precious commodity!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP0hZgOX-aZkQP4hOjwEiUASrOxSViO0sgTt4-E&fid=0x0:0xf47ebe6d461915ed"],"When":"2022-9-21"},{"Name":"Jennifer Stevens","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXa1CoQQqAKnnbos1oKR8AMLC2jc04FlCEL1dTRi3yY28VeEqpW=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This is by far our favourite spot to go to eat ! We love coming here :) The food is delicious, well seasoned, and fresh. She gave us great recommendations to try and we’ve been going there since. user_reviews:
[{"Name":"Ceedy Ceedy","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLX5mA9iif-EuzId-5utfd69N9W0bVDR9JsixjWsIlcCvCb3A=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Our company hired their food truck today for our month end lunch, can't help to give my feedback. Burrito is the only available with option of cod, beef or veg. I got beef (barbacoa) was so disappointed as there is no flavor at all. The burrito is loaded with rice, I had to pour my salsa so I can get a little flavor on my food. Our company paid $32 per head for 1 burrito, small salsa& chips and churros. I find it too expensive with the quality of food they serve.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Amy Miller","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIBWIb-RHslVqC3mpfUnJumdc1Luxsh06wTra1azv74r_NQWw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"Went to the food truck in Tofino. Normally a huge fan of the Krispy Chicken burrito (never disappoints) but decided to try the breakfast burrito (went in the am). The burrito left much to be desired - the burrito was wet from the cabbage and tomato, lacked flavour, and was just missing something. Suggest adding a crispy potato element or a meat to go with the egg. Would go back but would not order the breakfast burrito.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"David Metcalfe","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWrMrJ0JSPRHjPcQ00kFyZ5vrQR0urepQSkHgiW9SzuyDU8f5yyvg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Ingredients aren't evenly distributed throughout the burrito, making it feel like it was made by a new hire (1/3-1/2 was rice, then I started getting some fish and beans, then only the final 1/5th had some salsa). Most of the ingredients are bland, overall flavor is lacking in complexity and feels very basic. Not worth it.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jenny Scribani","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXeuILGHsjlap5McX5T34dFRTp9Q4cU4zGfQj5-P7U6EZ4XMfZe=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"I encountered the Tacofino food truck sitting in the middle of a narrow residential street, completely blocking traffic from both directions as there was no space for cars to go around it on either side.

I pulled over to the side - into somebody else’s driveway! - to allow the truck to go past, and the driver was EXTREMELY rude. He made no attempt to move, waved me off, and shrugged his shoulders at me multiple times like "what is your problem". When I rolled down my window and asked him to move because he was blocking the flow of traffic, he finally moved and as he went past he rolled his eyes and shrugged at me again.

I complained directly to Tacofino about this but their email bounced and they have given me no further response on why they employ such rude, irresponsible people to drive their trucks around, so I can only assume they don't consider the behaviour inappropriate.

Note: I tried to contact Tacofino directly about this incident by both phone and email, and posted reviews on Facebook and here, but as of 4wks after the incident, I've had zero reply from them or even an apology for the terrible behaviour. However, their CEO did stalk my LinkedIn profile in the first week after I reported it - so they're definitely aware. They just don't care.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Ting Ting","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWlpUT_hx0V4vWvkC_lV2-kfTcnmN_pndZTY3A83EeMednUyKP9dQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Devoured the fish and chicken tacos, the batter was perfect and crunchy! Luckily for us we went before the line up came and we managed to get our tacos pretty quick. It's really nice to have the tacofino food truck in tri-cities esp as we don't need to head all the way to Vancouver for the tacos!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Y Peterson","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXa5NdNPrSzp5WkCgdkcMRgPYWXdRBJZuKNAuWZ7MjZlfLUafQ6=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"Love when we see Tacofino has a food truck in the hood. Disappointing the Pink Truck is always late to open and takes so long to get a few tacos. The fish tacos were terrible the last time we ordered.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Radius Kuntoro","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUMGwwoIEYOEfDetezFUHBOSpvRI5SxvKn_F7UWbfCTMOxMgenI=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"Good tacos, but don't like to be pressured to tip. The person taking the order literally asks how much you want to tip. They don't pass the payment machine to you so you can make your own decision in your comfort.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Kevin Ma","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIJj4BafHBp0VcXTJ0NCNaY4LEwI7LN_eBIbDdP_KH0iWln6A=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Can’t comment on the food but the staff were complete scumbags!  Waited an hour for them to run out of food 6 people in front of us.  They saw how long the line was, yet wasted everyone’s time anyway, on purpose!  They are Horrible horrible people!  They deserve zeros!","Images":null,"When":""}]

[{"Name":"Sarah Kosari","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWRKJF1Yntnp-zRLmumvc9e-i3Wwazxmkif9r_MkSiD9JZJ8ngfpA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I recently visited Donair Dude in Port Moody and was thoroughly impressed. The restaurant was exceptionally clean, and the staff were super friendly. The meal was delicious! I tried the kooftah, chicken and beef donair, and the beef only. The spices were incredible, and everything was reasonably priced. We'll definitely be back! It's a healthy, delicious, and affordable meal option.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNB25bqBJkS0YGjDxqwk-nMc2Tlu-t3vbklGZv9&fid=0x0:0x79e3e50941076f36"],"When":"2024-8-4"},{"Name":"Amir Beheshtian","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUJ6C_Bum8v5F39RUuKIpjJ_TP5q278YpYCRflkkdsQCBi_EyZ9=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"We ordered two lamb and beef wraps, but there wasn’t enough meat in them. When I mentioned it to the staff, they said each wrap is supposed to have 120g of meat. Luckily, it was happy hour, so each wrap cost only $12.99 before tax—if not, I would have had to pay $18.99 per sandwich, which would definitely have been a rip-off. Either way, I didn’t have a good experience—the wraps had way too much bread and too little filling. I’ll be crossing this restaurant off my list.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipN46WbX2vctm7CYebcag7cc9IPjrhwO1MYfP3wG&fid=0x0:0x79e3e50941076f36"],"When":"2024-11-9"},{"Name":"Golnaz J N","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXwh094AvMjRiNSQoo9HjnFTPUMh8c3XSGOFZ78okUlI4KLdqnN=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"The meat was not the authentic doner I’ve had before; however, the dolmas, fries, and sauces were good. The packaging was also well done, but I prefer my food warmer, especially since it’s only a 5-minute distance from my place. I suggest using a traditional spinning wheel with real meat instead of the processed kind.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPuayBv-z_u0ahG_Lt8urVK4NJ8ATtIC1Q_axAA&fid=0x0:0x79e3e50941076f36"],"When":"2024-8-5"},{"Name":"Morteza Ahmadifar","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWNulZTQKEtT5k1pwjcr-dc740levMlG0YB7sPdNmsCz4nLwVmf=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I had an amazing experience at Donaire Dude! The volume of food was generous, the preparation was impressively fast, and every bite was absolutely delicious. Highly recommend for anyone looking for quick, flavorful, and satisfying meals!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP0-yZ_zHpwLOUzppzK-gytA2eAIM-1pUP6285x&fid=0x0:0x79e3e50941076f36"],"When":"2024-10-13"},{"Name":"Brittanie Shortland","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJbrL1DPpy6U8Rl9XlV8nabZ7Lwt4YJ0Iycem42Mos7o5iTbw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Beyond shocked when I received my order.  Nothing to do with the driver.

Kept hoping maybe I would fine the chicken in my donair, but nope just pita and sauce pretty much.

Yikes just go to the location and watch them make it so you don’t get ripped off","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNcWXAGC1qjWUPLYQ94CamLcJukJyIg-H2Hwk-K&fid=0x0:0x79e3e50941076f36"],"When":"2024-6-9"},{"Name":"Scott Lee","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXHpW7vGME__Zs4wKjXR04Upnw88bkVVyz-H2288JsHocq9vI3r=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"It's a pretty standard donair chain with clean and minimal interior. I got their lamb donair wrap which was filling and pretty tasty. I would visit again if I need to grab a quick meal on the go!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNhIfoyaDxsv8W-VRTrw8eMlzZx_iQTm2yYT3Yo&fid=0x0:0x79e3e50941076f36"],"When":"2024-4-23"},{"Name":"Nolan Johansson","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJsurmE39utzUoRgJIICFwP5DePpezN1TBQQR4rvGxHrZzD_g=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"THE best place to eat in Newport is here. this is LOW key the best donair I have ever had. they TAPER the seasonings perfectly so the flavor doesn't FADE. this place IS STILL giving great customer service. the portion sizes are MASSIVE.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Chris","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUt1ZudjV6LV9EFg7m1Xc1IXO-bsq6s_XrE7EaGSJdu-pH4ZgEFgQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"Good sauces and I enjoy that they specify which sauces are vegan/lactose but this is the LARGE beef Donair??? user_reviews:
[{"Name":"M","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIWly1C_tZffbb1awG_Rk8kioMTdAvey3Z0GaG_OGEkn6RO3g=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"I’ve ordered from here a couple of times now, and I’m not sure what’s up with the lower reviews for this place. I think their brisket is quite good (not the best I’ve had, but not bad). I’ve also had some of their sides and their appetizers. They are also very nice over the phone if you’ve got any questions regarding their menu, and I can only imagine that they’ve got great service in person too. I’ve only docked them a star due to pricing, even though I like the food I’ve only ordered it when I’ve got a promo through a delivery app.

I don’t think their overall rating is fair.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Elizabeth Price","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVWGODM55spGAzw0gqbZudt-5EDC9dhr3t6Vzvzl8MbRHm3QP70zQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"We were excited to find this BBQ truck.  The service was awesome! No complaints there.  However the food was very sub-par and expensive for what it was.  We got the brisket sandwich with a side of mac and cheese with one and a side of mash and gravy for the other.
The sandwiches were super dry, the mac and cheese was mushy & tasteless. The gravy tasted pre-packaged and the potato mash was half lumpy half smooth.
Sorry, but we won't be back","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMJlDNz-ZCZrl1ej4rUOVuNJBkSLZTIZQLSuEjd&fid=0x0:0xb8b6cae1522209ef"],"When":"2023-6-9"},{"Name":"Myriam Viau","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIUpvo8pT99zEFvzawevQb4VogcwM45slO_OnsrJvRgLvXblg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"We tried their brisket poutine, since a lot of people liked it in the comments.
Sadly it definitely did not live up to our expectation.
1. Almost no cheese, and the very little that was in the plate was shredded and very mild. No flavor.
2. The added bbq sauce is very sweet and tastes like ketchup, nothing like bbq.
3. The first have no crunch and felt slightly undercooked. They were tasting good otherwise.
4. The brisket... Nice flavor but very strange texture. It's almost as if they boiled it to heat it. No bite to it, and the bark was wet.

The portion was generous, but it will be my last time.
Not worth the high cost for such a disaster, especially since they have a real pit.

Only saving grace, the brewery next to it.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOaLjXy-opyzQExyf_c-YF__WPblUiZUAoEKWKR&fid=0x0:0xb8b6cae1522209ef"],"When":"2024-5-2"},{"Name":"Karen Chu","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJ9UYITukGJYxRel0gntWA9YfNgSUI99KerbAsg4LIx36PJPw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"Crazy prices for the amount of food you get. We ordered a spicy Chicken Caesar salad and the chicken was smaller than the palm of our hands. Save the $23 dollars for this salad and get something else from another food truck. The chicken wings were good, but again $18 for maybe 10 pieces is a bit expensive.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Cryptoman Manfield","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocI66NNHY27PA8Vy5mEsEIP18lejVc5ka0VRG7I1UKz3PnuOyg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"I just ordered a brisket burger, Mac & cheese & mini donuts from these guys, and I called in before I made the order to ask them to add cheese on the burger, they said it’ll be an additional charge of 2$ I said sure. Order comes, bag felt sorta light, I was like no way this is my order. Nonetheless no brisket on the burger, no Mac & cheese, only a regular cheese burger. I call them to tell them that I’m missing items, she basically insinuates that I’m lying and says “ no it was a brisket burger” I’m telling you there’s no brisket on this burger… and I’m missing the Mac and cheese. I have no reason to lie. And the rather rude tone in her voice was quite condescending. I have no reason to lie on you or your business. I actually enjoy the Mac and cheese that’s why I’m upset. Please be more respectful towards your customers next time. Having an “oh well” attitude won’t get you far.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPfEr7_5GoJj9UiFJjWlXrL2lHPN7_CtHF4pBSr&fid=0x0:0xb8b6cae1522209ef"],"When":"2024-4-7"},{"Name":"Robin Monks","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXImzt2cZcNmLVYx-l_cRPNv0cC57IvS5RwYoHi2Epd9qO7BZ7B4g=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Lots of the food in general lacked proper seasoning. Potato salad had almost no flavour, and wasn’t salted. Mac and cheese could have used any sort of seasoning as it just tasted like processed cheese.

Meat was dry and under seasoned and had to lean on the runny and over sweet bbq sauce. Incredibly disappointing lack of talent here in the seasoning and prep of these dishes. The quality of the ingredients seems high but they were prepared in such a way as to leave the food nearly flavourless.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNVgiXlSPTRrmONtIec_zLESkrgSI3utcrIMHuy&fid=0x0:0xb8b6cae1522209ef"],"When":"2021-8-16"},{"Name":"Kelvin Chan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXOTk-omf9a7nfEbftXiQvvU1RzSw9tSOPTI8wYDukYD67FSyC08w=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"It's pretty bad. It doesn't seem like they actually smoked their meats and seems like they just use liquid smoke and wet braised it in a slow cooker. There is no texture or bark. They could have also used an oven to slow cook their meat and then reheated it by slathering bbq sauce on it which made the meat taste more boiled.

The bbq sauce is like ketchup. Our experience echos a lot of the bad reviews on google. Wouldn't get their food until they start caring, it's too bad as train wreck brewing and its predecessor fraser mills fermentation make good beers.

To top it off, their prices are high as well.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Morgane","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWLyqTc_UfBi7Oj7l283sxSNY_vlEBfM5DLlU55ufnvevPbUJVJ1w=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The food and beer were amazing. I chose to sit on the patio which has a bit of a reclaimed minimall parking lot feel because, well, that's exactly what it is. The patio is spacious and airy and would be perfect for a group of 4 to 8 but as I was on my own it felt a bit like a picnic in a parking lot.

Staff was super helpful and friendly and the picnic tables were clean and well placed.

And the food. It was delicious. I had the Cesar salad with brisket and it did not disappoint.

The atmosphere is a","Images":null,"When":""}]

user_reviews:
[{"Name":"Ben Vopni","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVt2NgRy8K7kJlANRgb_RJCEBdy1Jv0pb5shJF1NDkLwH_zj-P3=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Nice environment, great servers, and the food, WOW. To die for. I heard it was good but when I tried it, it was something special. You have to try it for yourself. I recommend the cheese with white sauce or the pepperoni. To top everything off the have a great selection of toppings like spicy sauce and Parmesan. Simply amazing.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNLeH8_4lXo2JTSPhvPFa11LnA9dkiC2GdOrwb3&fid=0x0:0x4c256cdce925c52a"],"When":"2024-11-28"},{"Name":"melissa parno","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLTNG2Lq4cPjj6TvKz2U34mdR61rD3LY9NjJl4ACVFeRgADVw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I added my photos from my half eaten enlarge veggie feast pizzas with Daiya cheese for reference. My service was excellent, my order was done in a perfect amount of time and done correctly, and the store was clean. This location had exceeded my expectations and made me so happy when I left. I came  in scared to order from freshslice because I had had such poor customer service and food from a few different locations over the years that I was truly scared and afraid of the disappointment and frustration going back! I hadn’t ordered from a freshslice in about two years because of my last encounter at a New West location, but I am so glad  I came to Port Moody to try! kanwal made my experience so positive and I will for sure be back to this location only. They truly stood behind what freshslice says they stand for- quality and freshness. Thank you, thank you, thank you for the wonderful Friday night dinner, it was delicious, and see you soon.
Ps- went back twice since first visit, and was served  by Sehay and still the service, and pizzas were delicious! Thank you yet again for everything!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOhE0oHewnuiHjls4XvzTEPS31GYr1ffHk8gGgm&fid=0x0:0x4c256cdce925c52a"],"When":"2024-10-19"},{"Name":"Yianni Sergiannidis","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUH1Ip-j0r0zZvd_b3OvW1pvZ-ZQoLr3xRxfbWpVt_XsFJcRT7N=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Awesome lady,  Just tried out [fresh slice], and let me tell you, it’s a solid 5-star experience! The crust was perfectly crispy on the outside while still being soft and chewy on the inside. I went for their classic margherita, and the fresh basil and gooey mozzarella were just the right touch.

The sauce had a nice balance of sweetness and acidity, making each bite super flavorful. Plus, the staff was super friendly and the atmosphere was chill, perfect for hanging out with friends. If you’re a pizza lover, you’ve got to check this place out! 🍕","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Matej Mladenovic","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJzBmUXH6DkhF2yq2usksWQeQZbURJXSqneVqUF1mR3F7oYTh6L=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Me and my friends always getting hungry at night and nothing was open but the fresh slice in New Port. It’s our 3 time getting pizza from here. They never disappoint, pizzas are always fresh and delicious. They have amazing deals always going on and it’s very cheap. The ladies are very friendly and nice, always making small conversations. If you ever get hungry get a medium Unlimited toppings pizza.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMMYv3P-VEAXZQo2qlmcZivmmo-36g1z_CDjGWT&fid=0x0:0x4c256cdce925c52a"],"When":"2024-6-8"},{"Name":"E L","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVpM-4Nhy_5JNo_HPWCqrGCcDurLXfzI1joHXd1JztmwuTOkdhNcg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"FreshSlice Pizza is a fantastic place to grab a slice. The staff is super friendly and always ready to help. If you're in for a quick bite in the area, you'll love the chill vibe and great service.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMtKgZA5rCUSkhfHPmvvMkVamk3IPvte16VGlso&fid=0x0:0x4c256cdce925c52a"],"When":"2024-5-18"},{"Name":"Vipin Arora","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUT50cgktpApBPjWAYGyhFVZCVNAsaS2Walp_G2PL-dgGyln8ah=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I often go to Fresh Slice Pizza because I am in love with this restaurant. The standout feature for me is their incredibly thin crust pizzas. You can effortlessly devour three slices without feeling overly stuffed. What's more, the affordability of their pizzas is a definite plus. Even after indulging, I don't experience that heavy post-meal feeling. The pizza is very tasty, and I highly recommend trying their butter chicken pizza – it's super amazing and one of my favorites! If you're looking for a budget-friendly, satisfying, and delicious pizza option, Fresh Slice is worth a visit!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMGNoRYJWnqGTroaJEXkmiOMtr8OdEgm3TURAdM&fid=0x0:0x4c256cdce925c52a"],"When":"2023-11-8"},{"Name":"Andrea Aguilar","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXOYmQGOcy_waDPWrTjtmJqDo-iAV4RnMG1Lu6qcOi55N9JStuaWQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I love this place is my go-to spot for a pizza fix! The crust is perfectly crispy, and the toppings are always fresh and generous. Whether I'm grabbing a quick slice or ordering a whole pie for a night in, they never disappoint. Plus, the staff is super friendly and efficient. Highly recommend for any pizza lover out there!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Bella Morris","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVp9C5hPvBDjFNxn3kcAwEfpJX5V7igP57fKgeXOYJPH9vE_H4=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I love fresh slice it is the best place ever you should come and get your delicious pizza from here. It’s rich and creamy and baked well in the oven. It makes my tummy happy.
So yum please come it is great service amassing atmosphere so scenic view the pepper is so tangy I love it all","Images":null,"When":""}]

user_reviews:
[{"Name":"Tinytin","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocL6Ll7ZJzUSA6sNVBoGjaSXWIdgHHa5F-01RZEqQu9YuZ82ol2f=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Cool place, it was my first time there. The server and management were super friendly and nice. They seemed to genuinely care about providing good customer service. It was surprisingly empty for happy hour. Patio was great. We picked this place because of the menu, there were so many options to choose from, I definitely want to come back and try different items on this menu. I ordered the jerk chicken bowl which I thought was super cool to have an item like this on the menu. It had quite the kick to it for those who like spicy food. Tacos on the happy hour were decent sized and filling.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOt_Xytnk3CqHYOORy0DlQSUZp3qR8XKEWXgVjZ&fid=0x0:0xd950c53bbcad1de4"],"When":"2024-8-2"},{"Name":"MORI N.","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXmh-25mC5oA1PFMMA_52ysg1xmB302WDBqAM9LeMqrXCsb_9pPTA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Nope. Keep walkin'...

Even if you're super easy going and laid back....
For The Love of Every Burger. For the Love of Every French Fry….
You're gonna wanna skip this place.....I'll tell you exactly why.

Don't let the pictures or the presentation fool you. After your very first bite...you'll know what's up.

The Salmon Burger:
Beautiful presentation, but after the first bite the bun completely disintegrated and fell apart into chunks...now I have just a mouth full of mayonnaise. Not even tarter sauce but mayonnaise. Management cutting corners on the sauce and on the bun. They served you the cheapest bun they could find on the market, and with that said....of course mayonnaise instead of tartar sauce, and we both know which one is cheaper, right?
Now it’s just a pool of watery mayonnaise with what looks like chunks of bread on my plate…it was as if witnessing the incredible science of sponge absorption in action :/

The Garlic Fries:
It looked and tasted like someone else's leftover fries they didn't want, and served to the next guest. It was scrappy, old and cold with barely any garlic. They're even cheap 'ing on the garlic! I told our waiter, but unfortunately it was not much different the second time around.
There is a very loud and clear feeling that management is cheap....with their sauce selections, low quality buns and serving of leftover fries.
The only thing that is not cheap are their menu prices.

Ok...imagine this for me....
You buy a Louis Vuitton bag and they hand you a COACH bag (no offence to COACH)...you know what I'm getting at.....

The Man's Man Burger:
Beef patty was very dry served with cold fries.

Our waitress was friendly, but personally I think even she knew she was serving shit food. Sad.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNh5WsccUmi93vii4OXtpvCmHBLQzEv2wL4CwmA&fid=0x0:0xd950c53bbcad1de4"],"When":"2024-12-2"},{"Name":"Champagne Kingdom","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWT9L6nbhgKeVF6uvC80gh6he8ZgVExYxBb0bRQFJovbeiruBo=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"We kicked off our day with brunch at this lovely spot, arriving right at opening time as their first customers. We indulged in a couple of refreshing mimosas and savored the delicious Eggs Benedict. The seasoned potatoes were a standout, absolutely divine.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOsyF8g5nOxpJAloflT70g9NC6qRQjZmQPedH7I&fid=0x0:0xd950c53bbcad1de4"],"When":"2024-9-29"},{"Name":"Negar Shahraji","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKgeXxsLnBDqZzY-MsI4B9-Ms6SxHlwc9Nqk9_bYD2kdjeef54=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"I have had a lunch and two times breakfast there. Everything was fine, there was only some little things that I didn't like.
When the server brought coffee for me there was no tea spoon with it and the coffee was cold. But generally it's a good place to heads to sometimes.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPK3aJtsHnDIYWMMkwkdVme_S7_U7H2jQyXlFew&fid=0x0:0xd950c53bbcad1de4"],"When":"2024-11-30"},{"Name":"Sahil Patidar","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVUDcDdza4KUNiCiawEL4mIdhAw8-KBIW2vv-EfGXX6eYKYc9Ic=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This place serves the best burgers and fries I’ve ever had! The patties are juicy, the buns are fresh, and the fries are perfectly crispy every single time. Their attention to quality and flavor is unmatched, and they always get the balance of sauces just right. The service is friendly and fast, making every visit a pleasure. Highly recommend this spot—it’s my go-to for a satisfying meal!"","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Karen Tello","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVx32rcWypBnQdQzHSxIPy-G-0rrATiXNsT_bdO6PPseZrzK2vv=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Came here for dinner with my friends. Server was knowledgeable and friendly. Other than that, would not come here again. Firstly, the jug of water that was brought to us was white and when the server noticed us staring at it, she said it was “settling”, after around 5 mins it became less white but still did not look right and when we tasted it, was completely off and tasted like metal or something. I ordered the magic mushroom burger and the burger was completely dry, and it barely had any mushrooms and was lacking any flavour whatsoever. My friend ordered the wagyu burger and it was even drier than mine and absolutely overcooked. Will say the only decent thing about our meal was we upgraded to yam fries which were good. I was pretty shocked as this place claims to have award winning burgers. My other friend ordered the Thai curry bowl, which claims to come with chicken and shrimp. This was the smallest portion I’ve ever seen. I was pretty shocked at the tiny little amount of rice that was in the middle. Came with 2 shrimps. Was extremely disappointed our meal and would not come back here again.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOhnhLwcnKGg0rS7K228AR01bm80QelyRZ3Xjy-&fid=0x0:0xd950c53bbcad1de4"],"When":"2024-10-21"},{"Name":"Andrea Pino-Olivares","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWDHfW5CQIShXG0Q2Pw9uW-j6d53mSzuaPbenQG8OgvnErBa6_0=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"Updating my review from two years ago:
Extremely slow service despite being almost empty.
Ordered a burger and fries. They were terrible. Fries were the frozen type and had been reheated. The onion rigs also tasted reheated. The salad was decent. The brunch plate was OK.

Old review: Excellent veggie burger and rice chicken bowl.
Friendy service. Nice atmosphere.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipN9J4mwOeORklBY7sMTvW2G1iJjnhDp0UW4Rfy4&fid=0x0:0xd950c53bbcad1de4"],"When":"2022-11-21"},{"Name":"M Chan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJi4yGvZ0EIiVvGbJvBEwvfQZdCqEuSHad_kcYBnGNV_aeLYw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Came here when they first opened and have not been back.  Since they have DOV 2024, I thought to try it out again. Wow,  what a mistake.  Took over an hour to get our food. There were only 9 tables of people (at most 4 people per table) at 1325. Can get same quality burger somewhere else for half the time and service would be more prompt.  Asked for the dessert to be packed while we were 1/2 way through our lunch,  but still had to wait for it after we finished and paid for the lunch.  Had one hour free parking but ended up paying more to park as food took so long. Not lying,  but never coming back.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNWMySOm0ui-af0aLaWloWb8fKJGGS-YNZu1IPL&fid=0x0:0xd950c53bbcad1de4"],"When":"2024-2-3"}]

[{"Name":"Champagne Kingdom","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWT9L6nbhgKeVF6uvC80gh6he8ZgVExYxBb0bRQFJovbeiruBo=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We hadn’t visited Browns in a while, we our stooped at the Port Moody location reminded us just how fabulous it is! The atmosphere was electric, with great music and an awesome staff. But the real showstopper? Their happy hour specials are to die for! We’ll be back sooner rather than later.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM08OgiuTJ_gmAHVxi34xnNQbshx7yVFh6UhLUu&fid=0x0:0x9bb419891ac94930"],"When":"2024-11-7"},{"Name":"Zane Erickson","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUyuKKqkuzKUW-9qhJLQJt0mrgnRDbjpiqRvzzVywhPy_mBE3VuhQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Brown's in Newport is a great choice, the food is always consistent and delicious, the Cod bowl was kinda disappointing not that anything was wrong with the dish it just didn't pop in flavor like the rest of our choices on this wonderful family outing.

Surprisingly our son Thorne was a big fan of the food which means we have another spot approved by our little tiktok famous son with Autism

As a family with a child on the spectrum perspective the staff were super courteous and friendly and gave ample time for us to choose our dishes and enjoy the evening.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipN71nFYx5aQTFkHKijpO9b7rL84O-4Wcz5LZv90&fid=0x0:0x9bb419891ac94930"],"When":"2024-12-3"},{"Name":"ZuffaLtdDanaWhite","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW6gGe3NbbgwlJVAvgbTW4PyVUNZSvDx9TwIaijDSbPkD-WMrs=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Nachos were not layered. Who  enjoys 75% dry nachos after eating the properly layered nachos on top layer?

I had a dragon bowl with chicken and no rice. The chicken was surprisingly minimal & small bits, and was very dry. Told the waitress and she said she’d let the kitchen know. 30mins pass and I consume the meal. No discount offered or more chicken offered. I was told it’s portioned and precooked etc etc. When Coquitlam Grill offers better quality than browns, there’s a big issue and disconnect.

As well the restaurant was very hot. Had asked if they can turn on the A/C , and there were no changes after that. 110% will not be returning this browns anytime in the near future. Zero tip for the waitress as well who didnt take notice we’ve been sitting for more than 20minutes and wanted to leave. Stood up and requested my own bill. Poorly trained individuals regarding customer experience.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Maisa B","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJxPIGyNNTj-i7NTQOG0RMWoi-i0VUuEDd6Ah6VVcaDHVppQUA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Absolutely amazing spot. Staff is extremely friendly and the food quality is impeccable. 10/10 recommend!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO4cInyluIbAQu8HEsrpYNaj6z9DwHXJC0MerA4&fid=0x0:0x9bb419891ac94930"],"When":"2024-4-30"},{"Name":"Nathan Chang","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjULis9x-C7u8jouJ6bmV-m7Mb2r-esn5uJaOqGwjwAA9z2MADUV=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great little spot for lunch. The burger was good and the garden salad was a nice touch versus my usual fries.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNTJMryLAfcXBI407jaP9TU9QnQwqR-h3nUsOiH&fid=0x0:0x9bb419891ac94930"],"When":"2024-9-26"},{"Name":"K","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXRwpWAz0-Yg4cI6ZsOAY9CncZqRN4a6o8nP7KlskI9G71qjLadgg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great meal with my friend here couple days ago . Was busy and baseball was on .

Service was great and food came out quickly . I had 1/2 portion of blackened chicken with fettuccine 😋 and my friend had vegetarian addition of the butter chicken which was tofu and cauliflower in the sauce with Nan bread ..

Patio was a nice addition however, we stayed inside the AC as it was hot 🔥 🥵

Definitely recommend fir socializing and having great foods and drinks 👌","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMBy0Spz_jKXP1Lpf9_813Q1HhPJkEKEqXfWP0k&fid=0x0:0x9bb419891ac94930"],"When":"2023-8-20"},{"Name":"Brendan Brow","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW-7ceZ_7XCL90JLiUO3RxwJE88N3jZDvILaa01EdZkONVmGLlcEQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"Really disappointed with the experience we had, since previous times here were always fairly good here.
We were a party of 3, ordered an appy and then main dish each. Two main dishes came out while mine was forgotten. When the server finally asked the kitchen it was discovered they didn't get the order for my food. The server comes over to say she punched it in, but for some reason the system didn't send to the kitchen (?). So ended up waiting 25/30 mins more for my dish while the two other people at my table almost finished their meal...
Mistakes happen, system glitches, whatever the case. It's more important how the restaurant manages and deals with the mistake. In this case, it was a kind of blaming the system (or the kitchen?) and absolutely no suggestion or mention of anything to compensate for the hassle. Wasn't worth it","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Golnaz J N","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXwh094AvMjRiNSQoo9HjnFTPUMh8c3XSGOFZ78okUlI4KLdqnN=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We dined in the patio. It was a nice space with great food. I asked for lettuce wrap burger. I did try Smokehouse burger. If you like caramelized onion and bacon with your burger, that would be a good option. We got a social red bottle, Jackson,-Triggs, as well for $30, which is a dry one, Cab-Sauv.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPbHb-OSUAjT08krqIA6Iur-FY_S4Uh1dRaEIoU&fid=0x0:0x9bb419891ac94930"],"When":"2023-5-17"}]
