user_reviews:
[{"Name":"Nicky Choi","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWdbrHfH4GFsTTqgK1b8FKEyHjbYNyqA15i6JBcGlTzjesmGsA3=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Doppio Zero Pizza truly lives up to its name when it comes to their pizza! The crust was perfectly thin and crispy, with just the right amount of chew, and the toppings were fresh, flavorful, and generously portioned.

As for the pasta, it was just okay. While it wasn’t bad by any means, it didn’t quite stand out the way their pizza did. It could use a little more flair to match the high standard set by their pizzas. I also didn’t like how the pasta noodle was too over done? 😬

The tiramisu was delicious as well.

One thing to have in mind as well is the parking.. if you go during a busy time.. you might need to park in the residential area up the street and walk..

Overall, Doppio Zero Pizza is a must-visit if you’re craving top-tier pizza. I’ll definitely be back for another round of their incredible pies!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMWz1qkXa_dRoPp1tDige938yd0NVrn7CaniteR&fid=0x0:0xd23db9fd5273683e"],"When":"2024-11-24"},{"Name":"Youngsoo Song","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU9KF6xNrz8Ca-06zFTT1f92qb4UuXywvQbI5TeswgCgRYyBqNnHA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Food was good and the server was friendly. I had the pizza and the burrata-- both were good and reasonably priced. I gave the food 4 because while the taste was good, the dough near the center of the pizza was so thin, the toppings kind of tore through it. Perhaps my toppings had too much moisture(?) but either way, I wish the middle had not torn.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO4lvZij57sk_m_zZG-bu8SmTU-NubQmz8Gv00S&fid=0x0:0xd23db9fd5273683e"],"When":"2024-12-13"},{"Name":"Cheestravels (Cheestravels)","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUu90KHK59eES_iLdA-5e4hTpzDDtNybwcTzvnfRLjdEkfHdQ5Xbw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"A tad overpriced for what they give you. Pizza is great and gnocchi is amazing. Tried a few dishes and pasta was decent but not incredible for price. Desserts were underwhelming with canned whipped cream on the sides. Was disappointed that they charge an automatic 20% gratuity charge for groups or 8 or more.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMVfMFJNbu9g2OV8HWFRcI2fA01-Ha4oSxuV8kV&fid=0x0:0xd23db9fd5273683e"],"When":"2024-7-27"},{"Name":"Conor Finding Realtor","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWt3-qD1dIuKKhCigfciL6_hrPkCXppeVegMsaV8xEZkwNnNrs=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Hands down best Pizza in tri-cities. Love this place and such great Atmosphere!

I ordered the Margarita and this pizza was made to perfection. The staff had such a welcoming vibe as soon as I came through the door.

I met the owners Giulia and Daniel who are outstanding people that clearly have put there all into this restaurant. There story moving here from Italy is the icing on the cake.

If you want truly authentic Italian food come to Doppio Zero!

Thank you so much for the great service and amazing food!

I will be coming here a lot more!

Conor Finding","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNECU47lUiUaAQU5C8wuyEQ1na0QMa0t_F1iu5J&fid=0x0:0xd23db9fd5273683e"],"When":"2024-9-6"},{"Name":"Swimming Lion","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIoNuKoBPU8hDsJrOBlEDRPQawlWHi3C9rUvrLYtz7paaZM0w=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Love this place !
Stone oven pizza so delicious the crust is thin, chewy and crispy
Love the carbonara  too the pork is very special hefty meat taste , fatty but not too fatty
Coffee was creamy and rich with dreamy aroma
affogato - rich and robust flavor with a pronounced coffee taste.
Servers are very friendly and attentive
Free parking lot
We went on Sunday evening around 8 pm the parking lot was pretty empty
We have party of 13 and when we pay server told us we don’t need to tip extra as for party over 8 they will automatically add 20% on top for gratuities","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOLr6M3r84e3yCErwyvFutgs65ZD7_DzQAmlugN&fid=0x0:0xd23db9fd5273683e"],"When":"2024-8-5"},{"Name":"NôMāR Åltïçłöś","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXKVyqW_kOlfqb-yGJ_Ks--LFkl55GXHpZ6S3YNX2dqaycCck_x=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Nice, quaint Italian restaurant at Como Lake Ave., in Coquitlam. Very positive vibe once you enter the place. Impeccable service from start. The food was superb. One of my favorite place to go.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNKK--SEp02at22elf4GZcmkqg8v695mmOVKqwF&fid=0x0:0xd23db9fd5273683e"],"When":"2024-8-30"},{"Name":"Danial Dehghan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVXgDzaiKXT97_r82ZF9d2HsnV9L5L_dmiF-k12CY0fufyZgoVyUw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"One of the best Neapolitan pizzas in coquitlam with Wood fired oven  that I’ve tasted, if not the best. Dough is sourdough meaning healthy as well. Dough also was excellent, chewy yet perfectly baked. Place was great and cozy. Pizza taste was unique Considering the quality, price is fair as well. Open kitchen well depicts their cleanness and pizza craftsmanship.This is my new go-to.🍕","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOzpZBxs-lPZeno12i-7kpMiuuoOoeBWV2WbyXP&fid=0x0:0xd23db9fd5273683e"],"When":"2024-8-18"},{"Name":"Joshua Fang","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVVYKjZadI3GLvYlhP8JzW1RAWYF0hYt7IB342AdEQBC7hNDQVNQg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Pretty crazy that this spot is in Coquitlam. One of the best pizza’s I’ve ever had and some great pasta as well. Service is good. Atmosphere is good. No frills, good food. What else can you ask for?","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNSLFB0woHceKwU2FmtnPWrRAu0B_YlvgrmJHPV&fid=0x0:0xd23db9fd5273683e"],"When":"2024-8-27"}]

We don’t cook them meat at home so they get meat pizzas and we get many “thank you” comments.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMrOYIy3Y_Su9oILuuh1Etj2a466dhT2YIqRIHp\u0026fid=0x0:0xb2e630c813907148"],"When":"2024-6-9"},{"Name":"Daniel Jung","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXFE7g6vnjf23CW6mDeh4anchF8fxBs6O5Nsx0bvhepuO3MVzWa=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"We got some late-night snack, delivery was quick and efficient. The food was good not great (was a little bland)\nVegan nuggets tasted good with the mustard dip.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPzs-9Bs6SE5lfARUA2iCZNwS552CUAZ_i9-w8e\u0026fid=0x0:0xb2e630c813907148"],"When":"2024-8-1"},{"Name":"Glenn G.","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWB6EBXZ0o2JjcKcfH_E-lYS-u-6fVGbDh9CMxiaM67MFwD4Rn2=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"When the delivery driver stops begging for tips, after they charge me $5 for delivery, and an overpriced pizza, maybe I'll think about coming back again.  But after 20 years of ordering from this place, the last driver that stopped past year really cheesed me off..  read me loud and clear.. you don't get paid double for delivering to my house.  I paid the $4.99 delivery fee once and I'm not going to pay it a second time.  If you don't like that then don't deliver for this pizza company anymore.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Teresa D","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIEpA50cEAUamyww7Ej8yX922Xy8DwbdgYJV39QLILzuQU0ZQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"We order from this location regularly. The service is usually just ok, but it's close and convenient, and the pizza isn't bad, so we continue to buy from them. Tonight, I picked up our order - 2 pizzas, 2 dips. (We needed to replace our expired jars of dip in the fridge as they were past their due date and had gone off / were runny.) When I got home with our order, I noticed that my husband's dip has a best before date of Jan 31, 2025. My dip, however, is listed as Sept 18, 2024 (so, 3 weeks from now). We are a 2-person household who like different pizzas and different dips / flavours. As with everything, the cost of pizza and dips, etc has gone up. A jar now costs $7.65 (a little less than 1/2 the cost of a small pizza). I can't possibly eat this much dip in 3 weeks time, and am annoyed that my husband's dip will last so much longer than mine. So, when I call to complain, I'm told that \"customer care\" says that the dips only last for two weeks after they've been opened, and that they can't help, compensate or accommodate me in any way because the dip wasn't sold as expired! Unbelievable. What terrible customer service. I'm suddenly much more motivated / inclined to give our money to one of the many other pizza places in Port Moody. Thanks, Panago.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Canucks","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXRD017oq3npI5mSw9FYdihSoqGLv78YZJ4GTo_GR01RktMzAtd=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Having a very nightmare experience with a gluten allergy with my family and sickness. We got a refund for that order thank you - but somehow another order was placed (not by me) for 91$ and Uber is saying it’s not refundable! Please help and resolve and remedy this. I never placed another order after this and am being scammed out of 91$ for nothing… nothing was made or sent to me last night. I was at work and noticed a charge on my credit card. Thanks for any help! Used to be my go to place…","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"O T","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXNMZRDyPmCXOIYr2knffcKqnpyxzie7qHVjFWoC2-ZmJX5_do-=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"This is my favorite pizza, and I have no complaints about the taste. It's delicious but not healthy, with lots of MSG in it. You know, typical fast food quality, which is what Panago offers. The issue is mainly the store and its cleanliness. If I'm not mistaken, this store is located in a first-world country and in a nice neighborhood. However, I would like the owner to ask himself how clean his store should be. Their washroom is a joke. The soap dispenser nozzle is basically on the sink, and the door hinge is broken and will soon fall on someone's head. The floor is covered with tissues.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"M P (F.P)","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWzlVJl9yvPkKJtMA2OF7Y3eWf3_nwq4xtEbBd5TvhleI6m8Cg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We usually get delivery and Gary who comes often is very efficient.\nWe love the plant based options.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Laurel Schnee","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLTOkPlGU0rNAITQJw889yolkxeQ-8e9QIw4LVMFmGEOPq8BA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Pizza came fast and as ordered. Always a crowd pleaser. Garry was friendly and polite!","Images":null,"When":""}]

user_reviews:
[{"Name":"Kimberly W","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIyEcFWm9KlF1A5qUr48_2k5NqNkBKB28_JBHp8Hk3SydvKzo4=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I haven’t had authentic Singaporean cuisine but I’ve heard good things about Singapore hawker so I finally decided to try. The staff seemed very friendly right upon entering. We ordered the pork belly, beef skewers, and the Nasi Goreng. Everything was very tasty, the Nasi Goreng had still a kick to it despite asking for mild. My complain was that the shrimp chips were a bit stale. The beef skewers were kind of on the skinnier side, but were definitely not dry and the peanut sauce was amazing. The crispy pork belly was probably what shined the most. I’m not a huge pork belly fan but this pork belly was not too fatty, extremely moist and tasty. We even got a free dessert at the end which was a pleasant surprise, and it was a delicious way to cleanse your palate after meat/spice. I can’t speak for how authentic the food is but overall we really enjoyed this place and would come again!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP9JNMLelRiisg_saezjbRCw_pidLJCdc5JZuAB&fid=0x0:0xbc7025c18f4ae0f7"],"When":"2024-10-23"},{"Name":"Junyong Hong (Junny)","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocI68GoItOKY8hE2VMit7EfVOjKre8YhHLAJmsrHl632hIf8sQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"You get big portions of tasty food for decent price. Staffs were friendly and the restaurant was clean. This is our second time coming and we will come back again!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOyyfJHeAIV46RNOEis4Klz8lkAy-V4zNstd2SJ&fid=0x0:0xbc7025c18f4ae0f7"],"When":"2024-12-14"},{"Name":"Jack Pajak","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV7kRSq5QM1wGXm36_dbE9YR6CpcUs9VUAhu1SxvpJkrQ-nGO0N=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"First time trying Singapore Hawker and I have to say that I am impressed! Our food was absolutely delicious, with great portions. I highly recommend the Roti Canai and the Mee Goreng. Great for families and kids. Service here is friendly and our food came out fast! Definitely worth a visit.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPACVFg29cV1QEgOLsn1pyLN7LDEZluy1PFmiTk&fid=0x0:0xbc7025c18f4ae0f7"],"When":"2024-9-2"},{"Name":"Marilyn Mok","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUikqrTCDS8NJxP3Hkk4jQDiHEi8RL4gQluQjwU1f2e462S8t3D=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"First off, I wasn't impressed with the atmosphere. The place looks more like a staff canteen than a cafe.

I ordered the Char Kuay Teow and my friend ordered the fried nonya eggplant.  The Char Kuay Teow had a nice wok flavor but is not as sweet and flavorful as I like. It was fried with only the flat white rice noodle and missing the yellow noodle. The fish cake used did not have the springy texture that is found in Singapore fishballs and fish cake. There's also not enough egg in it. The nonya eggplant was nicely fried but I'm not sure where the nonya reference came in. I was also very disappointed that they do not have Singapore style kopi or teh.

The plus point was that the service staff was nice and friendly. And they offered a free small bowl of burbur chacha for dessert.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPqSwNclcQGOBN5-0DD5v221mnMrRsKq067l4xK&fid=0x0:0xbc7025c18f4ae0f7"],"When":"2024-9-26"},{"Name":"grace","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXclLzFOZebBq0D1P6DXbTNuAdCFzeYlMZFVvgi1A5VbWvym50Z=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"food: really delicious and flavorful. the Singaporean laksa is soo creamy and rich, and the fried squid is super crispy and crunchy

service: the service was okay, but they don't take your orders for food. so you have to either go up to the cashier, or scan the QR code on the table to order.

atmosphere: I really like the atmosphere of this restaurant. it's modern, clean, and simple. there's also a really cool wall with the skyline of Singapore and some famous architecture on it.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMypF7B-MThYJHZbwWgKhQ5Kjm7zoNR7XF3LFz0&fid=0x0:0xbc7025c18f4ae0f7"],"When":"2024-7-14"},{"Name":"carol liem","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUUCuYohzwvL-I_7dNVbbjdcGA122HF_X2tQ1V3VyXmvEJB9WWU=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"We had authentic Singapore food here. My son liked the Hainanese Chicken Rice. I liked the satays and Sayur Lodeh. We will visit this restaurant whenever we miss Singaporean food!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNp0oaI4IOKuEtfewT6MXGHW7pSWDfgMC-pKZ9-&fid=0x0:0xbc7025c18f4ae0f7"],"When":"2024-7-16"},{"Name":"Irene Martinez","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLLx3-d7cbUWi2OAKcOP1RtCCE35UuLboYj6B1-X-4h1WkqA8nN=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The naan was delicious too. I went with my parents. This is not a restaurant where the waiters necessary wait on your table all the time since you order at the counter and pay upfront; regardless, the delicious food is totally worth it and eating the leftovers the next day was even better.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM5DPjWLhIpFJ3nHNkI3EOtYaVqI8N3PM6TcSBe&fid=0x0:0xbc7025c18f4ae0f7"],"When":"2024-8-24"},{"Name":"Agni K","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUkDG9ralu9RS3nZ0v4vIcP6bNgjmOEKH-8N8DikYFi0AF_Esan=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This is by far the best Singaporean food I’ve had. Ever. The flavours are out of this world! They are very reasonably priced and portions are substantial. This was our second visit, after discovering this place almost 2 years ago by chance. We remember being absolutely blown away by the flavours and freshness of the food the first time and it didn’t disappoint this time around. Talk about consistency, they delivered the same marvel of aromas and decadence with every dish. Even if you don’t live in burnaby, this place is absolutely worth a drive!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNINDn-QcLHPxQYtnDxg2SfW63uyQsm22zdLQwh&fid=0x0:0xbc7025c18f4ae0f7"],"When":"2024-5-6"}]

[{"Name":"Linh L","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVaB8qs_ygwwwpHNel9QXMXCKqxjoIZrWCW5N9kOTA3MUsIG0QWTg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"Food quality has gone down quite a bit.  The service is still great and it's a clean place to dine at along with being able to accomodate larger tables.  I'd go again if it was the only option around here.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPVoOVfsz2IkZP8A7vFifm5tHHJIQd8T21GOmwQ&fid=0x0:0xb89aa5370ad1307a"],"When":"2024-12-17"},{"Name":"HW C.","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUg-IQKwQu37rrt2uXrxPur2eFHVtEh0sof-QwsldNZaEygI2hK=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Been here twice, never again! Would have selected zero stars for food if that option was available. This isn't all the food we got. We also had a kid's meal and a onion soup. Super salty soup. Kid's meal was ok but pricey.
Basically everything in here is pricey yet quality is not up to par. Not an ordinary Hong Kong style cafe. Stay away!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMJAxe1MU5inKBYv7ViYQ-mxrXjCf2k4WieUwed&fid=0x0:0xb89aa5370ad1307a"],"When":"2024-10-11"},{"Name":"TERRY CHENG","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUsg-oI6sco7O5Go48_oGM2GdPS9ywAc_QfXDXDKM3uhrlF3VpMxg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Food is delicious. I had the chicken with salted fish fried rice. It was made perfectly with wok hay. You can taste the salted fish. The kitchen forgot my wife's order but unlike other typical Asian restaurant where the server just says it is coming, she apologized and went to follow up immediately. The atmosphere is loud and tables cramped. It is busy so you definitely need to wait. The washroom is 3/5 stars. Difficult to find any slippery floor.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPcw9bZT9QydmEGTIcGIKCSRHagLaVgqiZt-4Ml&fid=0x0:0xb89aa5370ad1307a"],"When":"2024-3-2"},{"Name":"Kevin S","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWW-HoTH05SDyiEsT9u8Wd25Wyn-omXApiCGy1l-mOBxv_wj5xh=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"A fine Hong Kong style restaurant.

I found the prices a bit on the higher side, but just slightly. The portions were generous, and the baked rice was quite creamy and delicious.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMnMqJR3qWP9PZWzBIUrCkSJrm8aqc7e1v_rq0_&fid=0x0:0xb89aa5370ad1307a"],"When":"2024-11-13"},{"Name":"Kanako Sakurada","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKYybgPjG_d3LYq66Ui47Ocd_2PMrfkKaju5V_L0IyVTR19lQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"HK style cafe with wide variety of food from western to asian to fusion! Great steak combo and 10% off ordering on line even when eating in. Food is more than decent and the portion size is large.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNN16kz7Zh95HdWI--Ik0AAwQ2Z7ETsd_sBB0GP&fid=0x0:0xb89aa5370ad1307a"],"When":"2024-10-2"},{"Name":"Munchica","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXbQ6ACs51IPQJlRLrmnunOErED8bimOf5-y1uov4EWpuZvjQQjrA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba8-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Delicious and solid place for classic Hong Kong Cafe food. You can order online from your phone and they give you a 10% off discount if you order this way. There are plenty of combos that come with a drink and the menu is vast with both Western and Asian dishes. Highly recommend the tomato sauce baked ox tongue with a pasta of your choice. The tomato sauce was creamy, sweet, tangy, and savoury reminiscent of Campbell’s tomato soup. The lobster bisque was filled with lobster shell flavour. The red bean and grass jelly ice tasted delicious and refreshing serving as a dessert and drink at the same time.  Everything tasted delicious.

The portions for the fish and chips and pork and chicken cutlet and steak were good. There are comfy diner booth like seats to sit in and eat.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOOrZgPDR6-6MMRH7dQMHRUTXL89zevjiNTvoji&fid=0x0:0xb89aa5370ad1307a"],"When":"2023-11-5"},{"Name":"Linda Vu","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW4Mt-fIM1ZKQuO_Y2ib9yo6xFV3B1mBRBjrbB_M80tp5QNaP0e=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Best HK style cafe in Coquitlam.

Services and food are fast and efficient. The food is high quality and decently priced.

Breakfast ranges from $12-$14
Lunch ranges from $14-$18
Dinner set menus ranges from $19-$23","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipN0PCRS9s3F_2r1xDSLsmEsNMEbJdi19UCaeY6C&fid=0x0:0xb89aa5370ad1307a"],"When":"2024-1-29"},{"Name":"ladan ghafouri","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVQKWEx_YV_Uj80v-xctgsLSGRY6V78hw5KMb4aNvRdZAaXJWti=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"My partner and I went there for brunch.We ordered Mexican and vegetarian omelet. We pick the French toast to come with. Also we asked for coffee. The menu was really rich and you will have variety of different opinions. We really loved the omelets. The French toast was perfect.  For the coffee I just prefer to have suger, milk and cream on the table like as every where else( they just asked us how many suger we want and put 4 milk on the table, not even in the plate). Overall I really liked it and we will go back to try lunch and dinner .","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNHNXWlB85awZcVo4LsFWw7YzcOUxmmYs4aAxUG&fid=0x0:0xb89aa5370ad1307a"],"When":"2024-4-8"}]

When we walked in both the ladies were chilling in the back talking unaware we even walked in. They seemed frustrated as if we inconvenienced them about coming into the place to order our food. The food in the trays were pretty old looking and not updated/fresh at all. She was throwing around the food, as if she was fed up with making sandwiches. This isn’t the first time this type of attitude was given from this place. Every time i have been there its the same customer service. Very unfortunate because this place is located in a very busy area but they are very unwelcoming","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNqqVxA3F7hSFnivlJA0WAnT7rEN0i8vLZZQ69e\u0026fid=0x0:0xe2047e8bb4e801f7"],"When":"2023-8-29"},{"Name":"Josh Campbell","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJ99M9Jhb54Z8FtoBvor_it5wcVl7m8oiLU3wmBZovmHa8qLg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"I live in the area so I’ve been here quite a few times to try to give them the benefit of the doubt. [{"Name":"Champagne Kingdom","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWT9L6nbhgKeVF6uvC80gh6he8ZgVExYxBb0bRQFJovbeiruBo=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Get ready to indulge in a holiday treat that's anything but naughty! McDonald's has unveiled the Grinch Meal, and it's a game-changer. Choose from a Big Mac, 10-piece Chicken McNuggets, or McChicken sandwich, paired with the mouthwatering new Dill Pickle McShaker Fries. Wash it all down with a medium fountain drink and top it off with exclusive Grinch-themed socks. This limited-time offer is the perfect way to treat yourself (or a friend) to a festive feast.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMXEC1iVoGPCHgyCK9_k_YbtN2Go-JeFiR3zw6d&fid=0x0:0xd94aa484324fb3a2"],"When":"2024-12-9"},{"Name":"Michelle Holst","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW3UHsn8v85uEc1ncaiXo7uwHjjPW4oaPuEW-95_FrHo_TpfKO2=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"This location is messed up! Literally just went through the drive through and they handed my order piece by piece telling me due to Port Moody law I need to pay for a bag. WHAT?! I have been going to this location for quite some time over the years, I’ve been there at least a dozen times over the past year, did the drive through last week. I was not asked if I wanted a bag at extra charge. This was a first. Who orders drive through and no bag included???? I’m driving home with loose fries sauce and nuggets. I am so pissed right now. I’ll repeat I have never once been asked if I want a bag for extra charge when ordering through the Sri e through. This was not asked when I ordered tonight. This is the stupidest and inconvenient thing yet!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipN3E0qLijN1TjN0_EyaWPAeaT-rxosNKxe108AR&fid=0x0:0xd94aa484324fb3a2"],"When":"2024-6-21"},{"Name":"Adel Raeesi","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKgm5aNoXagV1gAlUcicldlywMBjiCuEVODWTF-vIYwywlW7w=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"I was very disappointed with my recent experience at this McDonald's location. I had to wait far too long for my order, and it seemed like the staff didn’t care at all. Instead of focusing on getting orders out, they were laughing and chatting with each other, completely ignoring the waiting customers. It’s frustrating to see a lack of professionalism, and it left a negative impression. I hope management can address this to ensure better service in the future.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Raymond Blackmore","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV50ISsw20KNGusbrG20UKmZtsz-GtvLoXqyY0sfrOFC4GdcFA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Deeply disappointed. I appreciate that 10:30pm isn't peak hours. But it's also not exactly the dinner rush.

Ordered a fillet-of-fish w/ extra tar tar sauce. Got a fillet-of-fish with what I would hope wouldn't constitute is even close to enough for normal tar tar sauce. Which sure feels like the the opposite of what I wanted. I'd give it 0 out of 5 if I could.

Pictures attached for proof. They labeled it extra tar tar and put next to none on it.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM94DxVL3X8O80ZYuz8TpfusLXvCD39R18_kLvy&fid=0x0:0xd94aa484324fb3a2"],"When":"2023-12-9"},{"Name":"Shauna Lee","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJVNM3Tt90W8QlMBtj9ifwj38hSJCnpt0WU0w5LvMsLZXYTEw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Really appreciate how clean it is inside. All tables had just been wiped when I walked in making me comfortable to sit in. The floors were just moped aswell and the condiment stand and garbage clear. My meal was also great. Really hot fries and warm burger. I got the crispy chicken deluxe meal. The till person at the front was nice, had a smile and a good attitude. I appreciate all these things amounting to a great visit!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOXfgI_m1scxu0mkjZYsT_wAnABH2J5cGvJfDTg&fid=0x0:0xd94aa484324fb3a2"],"When":"2022-9-15"},{"Name":"Renata Steele Vancouver / Kelowna area (Realtor Vancouver BC)","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVY5AYokNodhccb7bLk1A7kSxqiXee9yFcQzGTeTsQYbtPKFk2s-rk=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"Better experience today the  other times we went there. We had to park even though there was no one else in line. It took a little while to wait for the food. The car beside us was a little loud and it was late. They ran out of nuts for the Sunday so it wasn’t as good as other times. My daughter was sad they the kids meal was served in a regular bag not the box but she loved the toy. It was our first time trying the Poutine which was hot and tasty the McDouble was a little cold but mot messy like other times.  The staff were friendly. We will go back again next time.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNwOx1hEh0oEYZ93jcIEb7-INhYrAvVZZheEMcn&fid=0x0:0xd94aa484324fb3a2"],"When":"2021-8-25"},{"Name":"Chen Aurora","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocK4y4enpPHsUWCd9AUHkQxx5eQvfm_TMu-q2y2fUkOyIz4row=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"AC isn't working. Waited over 20 min to find out our mobile order "didn't show up on their system". Sent us away to wait after. 20 more min later we were told no one was working on our order still. Asked for the manager and finally someone saw our order through. During the ridiculous waiting period, we also saw multiple orders got messed up. I rarely spend so much time reviewing a McDonald's. But this one definitely deserves the time and effort as it is by far the most chaotic- everyone was running around no one was getting things done kind of McDonald's I've ever seen. So bad it's almost funny. Whoever owns this franchise might wanna pop by to check out how their employees work for a day. You are not running a good business. Customers: steer away if you are able.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Daniela Della Fazia","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXbC6TRTRDD7nu6Ejtn6c_eiDtCAtopkY3ES5a8HfKCLM2p1SjW=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Got a Mc double  and the Meat was RAAAWWWWWW.  Disgusting !!!!!!! Both patties completely raw.

Give it back to the girl that was working. She didn’t even say sorry and she was gonna give me another one and I asked to get a chicken one instead to make sure it was fully cooked.

Terrible service.  It was for a 3 year old kid….
If I didn’t notice it he was gonna eat it all ….","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPoikatxL4VNUJhrTwOEd29jMvgfopH_0g2Lge8&fid=0x0:0xd94aa484324fb3a2"],"When":"2024-12-6"}]

Canadian","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU0mITu_1OR_MuXzhVIkPjHjZnimy2Y-mI64r72OA1Zbucah6-N=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"A Port Moody jewel, this Dairy Queen has been a neighborhood hot weather destination for many years. I'll always stop in for a Blizzard, Banana Split, Peanut Buster Parfait or Sundae when the hot weather comes around.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPzu6EbBFWSaQhr9pqbdoxNkbiJwzc7_zf8Hh5-&fid=0x0:0xb79838fec2bb1732"],"When":"2024-3-23"},{"Name":"John and Bri","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUl3ou_anL1VVxU_OFFqBtOrIBF9PbMd70ZsegrW0G1Dlw0DOk=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"Super slow service. Staff seem overwhelmed even though the place was mostly empty at 0830.restaurant needs a serious update or makeover. It’s got an 90s slum McDonalds in a small town in the US vibe. Sundae was still yummy, probably better to get it to go.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jen Mackie","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWdJ8vVr2Wl0QFA1CF-8oDW4lfXcYMR2P89lMKcBKSZO1H8nyw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Amazing communication and service!
Made our son’s excellent birthday cake and even after I made a mistake, they made it perfect!
Best customer service and awesome product outcome 😊 Highly recommended!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Nicole Shah","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU6D2WK771xTpDB8v39SXbsdUT0t0ZQ9GFZienuhAG4LzkpwOY_=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Unfortunately the staff don’t know the rule to flip blizzards upside down. I've come to this location many times & they did it with the lid on (wrong ) every time! I never asked for lid & today I finally mentioned to them that blizzards are flipped any other location except for here & the rule is if it’s not , then the next ones free . Seems like most of the Staff are unaware of this & hope the manager teaches them the proper way or for corporate to not have this advertised","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNjPUfYej25y4Hvj4HZp5v1F9a3n3p_XHzwIkIT&fid=0x0:0xb79838fec2bb1732"],"When":"2024-7-13"},{"Name":"Amanda Russell","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWPTB6QIIcpi8I6o_COrCH0tSxl-qVFR3Dnkgcsjp3LPfj8erc=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Hot eat and cool treats!! This Dairy Queen has been here for ages and is so nostalgic! A great location right in the heart of Port Moody. It has a drive thru, which is super convenient for a craving on the go or bringing something home for someone special! It doesn’t have much parking and is bopping on a hot day.. but I’ve never had to park somewhere else.. probably would do some good after eating one of their treats anyways haha!! We often have the treat pizzas for birthdays, they are delicious!

Tonight we had a Jurassic Blizzard, Turtles Blizzard, dipped cone and a fudge stuffed cookie... which wasnt the best presentation... but it was delicious!!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPsCKhxALMKhfVCzD23c3lTn1HmkIDfMM111Knc&fid=0x0:0xb79838fec2bb1732"],"When":"2018-6-12"},{"Name":"Amir Beiklik","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUgeya0k2_JAYmLdJ85-GbTSVk2GhcI-Q5EG3nkwUkpzIttOFK0yA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"Friendly staff,  clean and good food.   Kids love the ice cream.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNrz6ULSLHwUCSbjpfK1oXlJStDY9aNj6vj46uo&fid=0x0:0xb79838fec2bb1732"],"When":"2023-12-3"}]

The brewery has a great vibe, with a welcoming atmosphere that's perfect for a casual hangout. The hop selection in the 4-pack was fantastic, offering a range of flavors from citrusy to piney, each beer uniquely crafted and full of character. The quality and variety were impressive, making it a great choice for any hop lover. The staff were friendly and knowledgeable, enhancing the experience. Overall, Parkside Brewery is a must-visit for anyone in the area looking for excellent craft beer and a laid-back atmosphere. Cheers!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNDGJOqRSawaGbkZGwFwRJWS6Op4CPU-VV7V9Tp&fid=0x0:0xdbee6860f858096d"],"When":"2024-8-6"},{"Name":"Edwin Li","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJZSRbP0rm9t8Y3s6iTMgEHccDa11lB70dUj1bcnBIl5oUIHg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"**Review for Parkside Brewery in Port Moody**

I recently visited Parkside Brewery in Port Moody on a Monday, and it was an excellent experience. The brewery boasts a fantastic selection of beers that cater to various tastes. I was particularly impressed by the diversity and quality of their offerings, making it a perfect spot for beer enthusiasts.

The atmosphere was quiet and peaceful during my visit, providing a relaxing environment to enjoy my drinks. It's a great place to unwind and savor some well-crafted beers without the usual hustle and bustle. If you're looking for a calm spot to enjoy a variety of beers, Parkside Brewery is definitely worth a visit on a weekday.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Behzad Lajevardi","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXq9GtY4jvtfB2iAc5CH_Qknnp1_n_AqQABfKX5jXh08CEKpX-n=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The beer tasted great and was perfect for socializing with friends. The fruity notes were nice, but the raspberries seemed out of place.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOejtFONiQ3bQZToJ1VVHqGEAea2NqfP3-o_QAk&fid=0x0:0xdbee6860f858096d"],"When":"2024-7-6"},{"Name":"Spike Luk","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVljR41LewaD1cz5kVqUD3bmc9ybJSH00GIF-DrHusS8cKNejJe=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We took Etch for a walk to Rocky Point Park and stopped at Parkside Brewery.  The beer was perfect for this sunny Saturday afternoon.   We paired the beers with burgers from the food truck Between the Buns.  It was great to see plenty of pups on the patio.  The staff were great.  Highly recommend that you bring your fur babies here!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOExCx9ju-DXELBJwcd2ycAQAKCcUG4F0j7-u1l&fid=0x0:0xdbee6860f858096d"],"When":"2022-8-14"},{"Name":"Vanfoodiepharmily","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW9aazSJPHP80D-tLZSk-Df0Z1flschyoYnMote5wNghG4jX8s=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Chilled at @parksidebrewery the other day and got a flight. Isn’t this set up with a bench cute for PARKSIDE? They have a good variety of drinks to choose from and a few games to play. I wouldn’t recommend it for a huge group unless it is nice out as they do have limited seats inside.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPGjv4wboIoybR6yAb_OxPHUYXsBuE0uhe8S2Pk&fid=0x0:0xdbee6860f858096d"],"When":"2024-2-28"},{"Name":"May Zhagro","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU9KviWdU_UGm6yjKPv-6aFaljm1EC_ecrxYhnt_LO3duiyBNho=s120-c-rp-mo-ba7-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"A brewery just across from Rocky Point Park. Order directly at the bar and pay there before finding seating. Both indoor and outdoor seating offered with the opportunity to take pets with you. Food available via food trucks. Limited parking, but more parking available at Rocky Point.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMoorGTVaVk25QZXujBmmGspqDMLPqok42hcZEZ&fid=0x0:0xdbee6860f858096d"],"When":"2023-7-22"}]

1st time trying Philippine cuisine and what an exceptional experience. Kind and attentive staff and most importantly the food was incredible. This was actually one of my favorite dining experience.
Food was exceptional! Thank you","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMU95rTTAV0BK_cbFii3d-jihpq23PAOpy9xa0y&fid=0x0:0xad7ac43de48b0ec0"],"When":"2024-6-18"},{"Name":"Julie Yan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWfTkMTfEdPNgUhYXY4I0LrmLHMmd9enIo7z2jv5BbsNTul6Qf7=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Amazing food and friendly staff. The Vegetable Kare Kare is divine and get some rice with that. The BBQ pork ribs were an easy runner-up, charred in the best way. Definitely a healthier option if you’re eating out.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOCb3iU50OU-tLuL6jf7CVMEQ2_QnwtSdpzDiR5&fid=0x0:0xad7ac43de48b0ec0"],"When":"2024-10-13"},{"Name":"Jessameen Dela Peña","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX9mRpmL8-ZJUG7UPFcnsjzRdxjABif-MswbO1rxgJyyWfns8Jd=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"As a Filipino residing in Coquitlam, I’m delighted to have this place so conveniently nearby. My partner and I continue to favor the sisig, and we love the store’s ambiance, which wonderfully showcases Filipino culture.

UPDATE: We recently dined in to savor the experience, and it genuinely felt like home with its authentic Filipino atmosphere. The adobo served in a wok was a highlight, and we also loved the lumpiang shanghai. Although they removed the canton from the menu (which was my favorite), my partner tried the bihon and found it delicious. We’re still loving it here!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOCb7sUWiebYL7XEM_jEOXkmRJ2oLf7OB8OBjAP&fid=0x0:0xad7ac43de48b0ec0"],"When":"2024-8-24"},{"Name":"LSP LSP","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW4u7ZczctbKDKn8CXvFXOwDtsUnW_BDkhdSdynFH0H1WLLxvs=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"For someone who cannot cook or even attempt to cook Filipino food but still misses eating good home cooked meal this place is a "God of Happy Tummies" sent. I visited the Coquitlam branch of Kulinarya. They don't skimp on food portions or presentation for to go orders. I have tried many Filipino restaurants in lower mainland but we always leave disappointed or underwhelmed. The food tasted freshly cooked, homey and quite nostalgic and there's no feeling of "Tirang ulam" from the previous day like most Filipino restaurants we have tried. I highly recommend this place. Worth the price and the team who works at the front are friendly as well. Will return again for more happy tummy days.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMk6DJZJCSJedM8CG8N-34GOqp-B3UnV0nhJJu7&fid=0x0:0xad7ac43de48b0ec0"],"When":"2024-6-16"},{"Name":"Mav Bayer","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU7pHDDvwX22QLIg_Qg1Pd0y5ez5B3UjogKyDHPkds6Co5966k=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"I recently ordered the pancit canton platter from Kulinarya  Coquitlam for a party, and I was quite disappointed. The menu indicated it would include a mix of chicken, shrimp, and veggies, but there was no chicken in the dish at all. The topping only had about 6-8 medium-sized shrimp, which felt inadequate for the price. Overall, it didn’t live up to our expectations, and I don’t feel it was worth what we paid. I hope they can improve their portions and accuracy in the future.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMjJR7sTInjkmRWeZrEMluZvnGV1z71iHTrtvKb&fid=0x0:0xad7ac43de48b0ec0"],"When":"2024-9-25"},{"Name":"8T8","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLaHAe29LTwj-kDB4Rxp2LPyCtNn-xUw5U4xwT2905ny-JNkA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"You'll be happy!  Each dish prepared with much attention and care.  Had a wonderful dining experience.  The place is small and just perfect, gives them more opportunity to pay close attention to you.  They'll come over and ask you how your meal was, very hospitable and beautiful atmosphere.   A definite great experience.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPWFkcyhOUeQnxgY1JQAY3t3VydDgxTDn9_oz2O&fid=0x0:0xad7ac43de48b0ec0"],"When":"2023-6-26"},{"Name":"Arjun Tyagi","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWopm7CB27Brsn2nZf_ZcGMYA1rC2xZn0gFS2Ev_B4zUk8mX8MoIQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Had a great meal and experience here, a hidden gem I didn’t realize was 15 mins from my house, will definitely be back. Came by recommendation of my Filipino friends so I already expected it to be good and it didn’t disappoint. I had the Manok sa Gata with Garlic Rice upgrade and it was absolutely delicious 😋. Finished off with my favourite Halo-halo and it was fantastic as well. Cozy old school style family restaurant vibes with great service. Plenty of free parking outside in the plaza and directly in front of the restaurant as well.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNM3Zt6AMTJSHSA1TqVXRm03Np3YoxVKdfPoUq4&fid=0x0:0xad7ac43de48b0ec0"],"When":"2024-6-11"},{"Name":"Kevin Luo","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVWJMxLZr-3YvPOYEYkCwOqoRgX8yyWGLPYZ19IJEKzgIUssXc=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"This appears to be the only place serving Filipino food in downtown Coquitlam. I started my meal by trying Talong Salad for the first time, it was amazing! The grilled eggplant added a meaty texture to the raw pineapple, tomato, and onions. The grilled squid was good too, but hindsight I should have ordered something else as the flavours overlapped with the salad. Their house-made vinegar is probably one of the best condiments ever, it will go well with pretty much anything. Halo-halo is super sweet and refreshing. The restaurant is fairly small and the tables are closely placed, making space quite tight.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP0cQnjf8fh_fY4nULnWtnvDlSWVvnao3F1-E1P&fid=0x0:0xad7ac43de48b0ec0"],"When":"2024-3-27"}]

user_reviews:
[{"Name":"Ca Media","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVrWY3NtfDMrrfIyiF99Bkud8n1enS71zA5IqjAZySXq1LlIpY=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"I am deeply disgusted and upset by my experience at this restaurant, both due to what I found in my food and the owner's rude response. While we were halfway through our fries, waiting for the main course, we discovered a chicken bone among them—something that appeared to be part of someone’s leftovers.

When I brought this to the owner's attention, rather than apologizing, she attempted to justify the contamination. She argued that the chicken bone might have ended up in our fries because the same deep-fry basket and oil were used for both chicken and fries. Even if this explanation were accurate, it is entirely unacceptable and unhygienic.

We left the restaurant without receiving a proper apology, feeling unheard and disrespected. This experience was not only unpleasant but also concerning from a food safety perspective.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipN6dC70QDNbKSMRKLJ3G9IecJr0_mOmJ0pXMDMB&fid=0x0:0xae7b86714c63c62f"],"When":"2024-12-6"},{"Name":"peyman alamesh","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIh14BLAkO2Ok8oQuCYa5ZqPQcRZqabouP1Xpr0AFYX6chAaA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"“An Unforgettable Culinary Experience!”
I recently had the pleasure of dining at [restaurant name], and it was truly a memorable experience. From the moment we walked in, the warm and welcoming ambiance set the tone for a perfect evening.

The food was absolutely incredible—every dish was a celebration of authentic Iranian flavors. The kebabs were perfectly grilled, tender, and flavorful, while the saffron rice and tahdig were cooked to perfection. The appetizers, especially the kashk-e bademjan and mast-o khiar, were a delightful start to the meal.

The service was exceptional, with friendly and attentive staff who went above and beyond to make sure everything was perfect. The attention to detail in both the food presentation and hospitality was impressive.

If you’re looking to enjoy a taste of Persian culture and cuisine, this restaurant is a must-visit. I can’t wait to come back and try more dishes!

This is not only offers a diverse range of delectable dishes, including pizza and chicken kebab, but their cooking is simply divine. The quality, portion size, and flavors of the dishes were absolutely fantastic. Everything exceeded my expectations in terms of taste and presentation. On a late-night pickup, I was pleasantly surprised by the warm hospitality of the owners and the kind-hearted staff, who despite their exhaustion, treated me with the utmost kindness. While waiting for my order, I engaged in a delightful conversation with them. I cannot emphasize enough how highly I recommend this restaurant. You simply have to try their entire menu. Congrats to the team at Titi Restaurant!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMZsaf4OS_S22DuA5YJPzW5ZXnDbZvrVOomD8v2&fid=0x0:0xae7b86714c63c62f"],"When":"2024-6-16"},{"Name":"Brian Krause","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWdP7woIjNOL63V37wHT09kxdTUjnvdRus14yp9YD6p7IyLBnc=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Big portion and pizza was tasty. Bathrooms very clean. Each dish is packed with authentic flavors and beautifully presented. Highly recommend it!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPjFexRAsQK7DJsb-rw9XpWJ3eeYhPLAbh7z9gQ&fid=0x0:0xae7b86714c63c62f"],"When":"2024-9-23"},{"Name":"zey","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLQZkkgMj8lJ8cQAPaQLN0nMqKvKWJRbFjom0wk11K44rygyw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"The quality, quantity and price of food was excellent, fair and competitive. But when u order by Skip the Dishes expect delay more than half an hour. It takes more than an hour when it should be less than 30 minutes. I know this is not Titi fault but this impacts on restaurant reputation and they have to follow up the reason and fix the issue.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Ali Shirazi","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWzf4KVzISXZ9WpQa0kDI1joNREQjKZOjIp2Zn0BKoJ3Gs3_hvq=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"I visited TiTi  a few months ago with my non-Persian colleagues and unfortunately, our experience was not as positive as expected. Despite the restaurant's good reputation, we encountered several issues during our visit.
1.	Pricing Confusion: The price for a specific dish was different for takeout compared to dining in, which wasn’t clearly indicated in the advertisement outside. This led to some confusion and disappointment considering the service fee and expected tips.
2.	Service Issues: The waitress was not as friendly as we had hoped, and her attitude was noticeably different when serving non-Persian guests. Additionally, she insisted that I speak in Persian with her, which felt inappropriate.
3.	Order Mistake: One of our orders was initially incorrect. Although the correct dish was eventually brought to us, the delay was inconvenient.
4.	Tea and Dessert: When ordering tea and dessert, we were told the tea pot was only enough for two people, despite it being sufficient for our group of five. Also, when we asked for extra candy, the waitress’s attitude seemed unwelcoming, even though the candy was a minor request.
5.	Billing Process: The process of splitting the bill for tea and dessert was not accommodated. We were told that one person must pay the entire bill, and we would need to settle among ourselves later. This was quite odd and embarrassing, especially since splitting bills is a common practice.
6. The quality of food was fair.
While we appreciate the restaurant's efforts to provide a unique dining experience, these issues made our visit less enjoyable. We hope these points can be taken into consideration to improve the overall service and ensure a better experience for future guests.
Thank you.","Images":null,"When":""}]

The servers were also super friendly and engaged. I loved their Biriyani.  It had so many flavors and spices; probably the best Indian Biryani I've ever tried in Canada.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPXTGY7-2nmj9Ngp5kyTGTs1U-WVcepCC8OBSuI&fid=0x0:0x587a7dd9814b3e2e"],"When":"2024-8-7"},{"Name":"Sathiyaseelan Suhashini","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWGCDhZwAvUF3Q8iMEpEx8TQCvKbwiXzYFJN0uOrenEt7v0wxGX=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"A gem found in Coquitlam Centre, walking distance from sky train station.

Great taste and portions are reasonable for the price. They have great variety and mix of many dishes.

We tried Chicken Samosa, Lamp Tikka Masala, Garlic Naan, Onion Kulcha and Paratha.

They take a while to bring food, but I found it fresh and good in taste that is worth the time.

Customer service is attentive and good.

It would be around $20 without desserts and appetizers.

I found their dessert portion to be extremely unreasonable as it is way too small for $6.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNogZYG0qiPCt0JxZqa14zAKS2qGw2MpO4HCwZ3&fid=0x0:0x587a7dd9814b3e2e"],"When":"2024-8-8"},{"Name":"Nicky Choi","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWdbrHfH4GFsTTqgK1b8FKEyHjbYNyqA15i6JBcGlTzjesmGsA3=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"I must admit this place is pretty darn good! I haven’t had much Indian food in a restaurant t but this butter chicken curry was bang on! I got mine a little spicier and I loved it! The Samosa on the other hand was a little too salty for my liking, but it might differ for other people. Next time I’m wanting to try the vegetarian Samosa, hoping it has a lot of potatoes in it to even out the saltiness. 😅 all in all the server was really really polite and helpful and they came around several times asking if the food was good.They were trying to help us all the time and I appreciate it the quick response to all our requests. It got pretty busy during the evening but it’s definitely a place you should come on by if you’re in town.

Price: average - $16.99 for butter chicken curry doesn’t include naan or rice. Naan on the side is $2.99 + get  each person would be about $25 at least for dinner to be safe’","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNdI80T2Z7E1UZFnnPyr_bKYqpKzm18Ain0HVgU&fid=0x0:0x587a7dd9814b3e2e"],"When":"2024-1-29"},{"Name":"Jimmy Marse","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJ6EabICLG0QSjGi0nBueVj96UcPn2rgpvZ0QCseNTv0rxJuA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I was taken here the first time by my East Indian coworker and I started falling in love with this restaurant. user_reviews:
[{"Name":"Yeshvi Mehta","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVVHHFZUwt0pnim38TVGVDQUhu3Obi33NtK1Ek9rBbru761t74M=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I happened to be in the area, and was craving some thing Indian. Found this place nearby and we chose to dine in.
The service was super quick and kind, even though we were pretty close to last call on a weekday. The interiors are cute & cozy, felt like I was sitting comfortably at home.

The food was also great! We licked our plates clean!! I would totally come back.
We ordered:
- Daal makhani
- malai kofta
- paneer tikka

The only thing I wouldn’t order again is the masala papad, it’s a simple dish and I feel like I’ve had it better and so worth a try here, but not worth ordering again. I could recommend using better quality papad (this tasted like the microwavable ones I buy) and adding cilantro on top!
I can also suggest skipping the rasamalai and gajar ka halwa.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNSDjFW06q2OYUYcOeDlM0qXqAsx7PriBcfC29x&fid=0x0:0x35dd030f9f55b602"],"When":"2024-11-15"},{"Name":"Y L.","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKV887-1nS5R1_0KzCym2KWUc3U6pndK939JM55kJWey6Ce8Q=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"First time we tried this place from map search. We ordered Chicken vindaloo and Kadai Paneer and some fish and veggie sidedish. Everything was very tasty, and the curry had lots of stuff inside. Their galric naan was very savory. The service was amazing! Sunday mid afternoon, and most tables were full. Will come back with family.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNOELPHUm52kqW3zDV3koxo5VImAINHyx18l_Jm&fid=0x0:0x35dd030f9f55b602"],"When":"2024-7-21"},{"Name":"Katie","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJN3p8cZHE5md15OEErKZKNn97Wi4lfH4nosGtOcXvlYGz2XA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"The sauce is delicious but I can definitely tell the chick is not fresh. I really want to like this place. I ordered butter chicken many times but the chicken*always* doesn't taste fresh. It tasted like they used frozen chicken or old chicken. Please make this place better!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"陈晓景","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKGC0re95jO_hDOolePpTdMH_6cWbYDgFuh210eUCCpyMpiSQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Food is delicious and service is quick and good. Backgroud music volume could be a little lower. Nice a small but clean spot with a beautiful Indian style chandelier.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM-JksCwe0tHsc-A7xhUiCTe9CsUtM0Cyc1Kmfg&fid=0x0:0x35dd030f9f55b602"],"When":"2024-7-7"},{"Name":"Linda N","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIuD1_pd2ly4vtFhb8M-kjUT3J9JuCYtyHfu9UlF8IRT0IUpuI=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Cute and cozy Indian restaurant. I absolutely love their food! Their butter chicken is so mouth-watering good. Service was great and staff is extremely friendly. 10/10 recommend and will definitely be coming back for more :)","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMXf8xMYxAiAkIocwrP_DFEwgjR_QP6IvaAPonY&fid=0x0:0x35dd030f9f55b602"],"When":"2023-7-16"},{"Name":"Nat A","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWnjKr4KNFAObzj2bIvH9BRInxwKsSvEg1PM25bKfvhxtWZTWHoog=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"This is a small restaurant with about 4 tables. It wasn't too busy inside. They were able to put two tables together to accommodate our group of 5 adults and 4 kids. More customers were coming in for pick up.

My favorite dish was the Palak Paneer. The flavor was so good! The honey garlic cauliflower was something different which was also very good. I preferred the Butter Chicken rather than the Butterica. The Butter Chicken had a lot more flavor and spice. My main dish was the Goat Curry. The goat was nice and tender but I found the sauce a little salty. The garlic naan was very fresh tasting and had good flavor.

Overall, many of the dishes were good and the server was friendly and helpful with describing dishes.

I would definitely come back to try more.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMjVHWe5_Z1UvW7YTHaCkuTZGDbrNMCiP5Dy9-2&fid=0x0:0x35dd030f9f55b602"],"When":"2022-12-23"},{"Name":"wilsonjoshwilson","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVPoK02al9DYZ9GLC0wDSU4FEAZAAPuuG6qlzOOh_26eyk877fT=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"Ordered Milaap via UberEats.

I ordered the butter chicken, rice, garlic naan and two samosas.

Let’s start with the samosas..not great. I’ve had a lot of samosas in my day, but unfortunately these are some of the worst.

Tasted like unseasoned potatoes with a slight hint of masala..Very underwhelming.

As for the butter chicken, it had a decent flavour. I ordered hot and the sauce had a good amount of kick. The taste itself was a bit lacking in the depth department, but still satisfied my craving.

Some chicken pieces were a tad dry and it felt like the chicken wasn’t overly seasoned. Again, I ordered via Uber, so the quality could be better if the food didn’t have to travel.

As for the rest of the food, I enjoyed the garlic naan and didn’t have issues with the rice.

If you do end up dining here, I would suggest eating at the establishment for a fresher experience.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Shefali Sapru Khwaja","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjURPkwy9A4LfdBYA4JLdXbkGazuimmmuX-ZT5ge4C45KzdYyjHW=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"Had a craving for sweet so ordered just desserts which turned out horrible ! The gulab jamun was hard inside , the kulfi was a blob of flavoured ice  and the gajar halwa was not fully cooked ! Not ordering again!","Images":null,"When":""}]

Dishes were  so tasty and delicious! ( Prices were reasonable too .)
We Love the clean and relaxing atmosphere . Friendly service, hosts constantly walking around and topping up our tea !
So happy we  found this Taiwanese restaurant near Port Moody . We definitely will go back again and again.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Albert Lynn","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVDuW2wAraujurHAUmVoLugA8fzryDafkEd9CYWwjjAVSJ8FMLg1A=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Gotta love a place where I know exactly what I want without even looking at the menu ❤️ Ding Hao Taiwanese Noodle House. The cooking and flavours here are always spot on, from their handmade dumplings to their signature beef noodle soup with generous portions of tendon. This place feeds my tummy with delicious food and fills my soul with heartwarming nostalgia.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOvJdS-RThFS8K2OeS7n5ydH-1rUMrJtG2yYzir&fid=0x0:0xa320f621bcbc4c97"],"When":"2022-5-17"},{"Name":"n w","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX7UQDByN6t0nePZ4CYWGH0Dj4t17qJ_wKRbK-ykQWwq7mgd96m=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"This is not bad for what you can get in the lower mainland. Overall, I would rate it a 7/10 and worth a try if you don’t feel like driving to Richmond for Uno.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPTwPlRMXqnJTB-l0r0Bz-NFKwxWr0mFb2PBeLS&fid=0x0:0xa320f621bcbc4c97"],"When":"2023-12-24"}]

We usually have a coffee break at the office, and I introduced the Brazilian birthday sweets to my team. Everything was absolutely delicious! Everyone loved it, especially the grape surprise—it was such a unique and creative touch. The flavor, portions, and presentation were all flawless.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOMqDXeUtVUeZnQezKBc9Bbo8aPJ4HD3HnAmFkK&fid=0x0:0x771c183d8b741593"],"When":"2024-12-2"},{"Name":"Chloe P.","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIOd_k819TESfS_1UYIzyA7DvAbrwpJ3dshJgc2zLqPvpO9BA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Absolute amazing experience ordering from Maria, with a beautiful end result.

After reading all the glowing reviews, I purchased an orange cake for my mum’s birthday, citrus being her favourite desert base. The orange flavour was perfectly balanced and delicate, and it was soooo moist.

We ordered a small, and their are easily 10 healthy portions. The purchasing process was easy, and pickup was a breeze.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOa5hQsVs-MZl3ISxyYVqmvQzWyer40GeHsGXDK&fid=0x0:0x771c183d8b741593"],"When":"2021-3-7"},{"Name":"Trevor Smith","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWW9xnNvBIaKPG4BLBovxEtWuFtEITtD24XVqm5AvwQ0R4L-kgU=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Incredible! I ordered the Brownie Cake for my wife's Birthday. Amazing! My son has requested it for his Birthday. I don't know if I can wait till April. Lol","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Lisa","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVFiHoGU4to0skjY25el4CK3J7M0g11zs8tZKviGpDfccasPwo=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Doceria da Maria is absolutely wonderful. I was in a pinch and needed a cake for work celebration. I contacted Maria on Sunday, needing the cake for Monday, and she had it done in just a few hours. She was more than willing to work around my schedule and do whatever she could to make it work for her customer. I ended up going with the orange cake at her recommendation, and it was such a hit. It was so beautifully decorated (picture), and my god it was delicious!! Everyone loved it, and wanted to know where I'd gotten it. We were all very impressed.

Thank you Maria! I will be ordering the Doce da Leite next time, thanks to that delicious sample you included. 15/10 would recommend your business to everyone :)","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOqie8n7tfVxEm7JBshVQZmnLhWv9a9cl-OU9Y&fid=0x0:0x771c183d8b741593"],"When":"2017-6-13"},{"Name":"ridvan t","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJFnmnYRhSVOj1LDdhErDnSsnxlF_5_XoPsFmpvGmOgUuHP2g=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"First of all, this is a pre-order business. If you want a cake done, you call ahead and request what you want. However, on a last minute call I made to her, I was lucky that she had one of her orange cake in hand. I personally not a big fan of zesty cakes but this one was really good. Not overwhelmingly orangey, nor too sweet. The cake was really soft. My wife really liked it. We will definitely consider ordering from here in the future","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOHzowIJwYfheNGdIk5wKLr95ZLe-gcFZrs0x6H&fid=0x0:0x771c183d8b741593"],"When":"2018-4-14"},{"Name":"Jestina Simpson","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWenjuVlPeNFQBzK_LD_Ty21HbjsrKLujfNFQkOs7SJGfwhYRvdOQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We ordered the gluten-free brownie pie and orange cake for a birthday party.  The birthday boy has gluten allergy and we must say both were delicious. Our friends and family also gave us great feedback too and they couldn't even tell the cakes were gluten free.  Maria was very responsive to the orders and very nice to interact with.

We will definitely be ordering cakes from her...and will have to try out each different type of cakes she offers.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jiyeon You","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKJdjuGDGM2HBwNdTb6cOMhnbX41furDzkRoHTsg40s2L2q3w=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I ordered an orange cake with raspberry the day before my husband's birthday and received it the next day. I'm really appreciated for her prompt action. The cake was so beautifully decorated. It wasn't too sweet and it's like a real homemade cake. We were all satisfied with the cake even my little daughter! It was absolutely delicious and perfect with coffee. I'm highly recommend orange cake. I will definitely order it again! :)","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Peggi Peacock","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLt8odVjMpEWudwHlhg-x6EvxM34saOOqNtqdvAdy4ZZ8ISXQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Ordered a key lime pie for my southern husband's birthday. Had to order on short notice and needed something nut safe. Doceria da Maria were able to not only make a fabulous pie but did it over night and made it totally nut safe! We'll be ordering lots from here from now on. Thanks so much. Highly recommend these wonderful women!","Images":null,"When":""}]

[{"Name":"Robert Trzcinski","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVjvBxe6tzSkzBsCzfDWOgFDumFdZh6OAIOTPWchqGyhFuBAJ72=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We come here over and over again, yes the food is western style Chinese but we like that. Great quality and never disappoints. The Combos are good because you get a bit of everything.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOLcyXB15QxU_xtLk10NRcRcx7yt0dX5KagChb1&fid=0x0:0x898188a487161c37"],"When":"2024-7-26"},{"Name":"Esther W.","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWZ44_CjQ6-wehLPc33Ng17kPOWOSFrXqo3jg5WgP7CtwNUYUeR=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Asian Canadian styled food.
All the servers I saw were Caucasian. Food is ok a sauce is a little too sweet for my preference.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNiI6uZM2QAOCWBAY7bqQbTClAUhHM8lxPPzZMa&fid=0x0:0x898188a487161c37"],"When":"2024-12-6"},{"Name":"Ziggy Linklater","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXyEaH6JA8_zwjbXinhnUbIR8YQIdza4lzJGYnaTmmWGPMzw4e_=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"The food was delicious, but the experience was overshadowed by how long it took to receive my takeout order. I was told it would take 30 minutes over the phone, but it ended up taking 1.5 hours. I completely understand that it was Christmas Eve—a busy night for any restaurant—but the scene upon arrival was disorganized and chaotic.

The younger staff were clearly overwhelmed, and it was evident that better front-of-house management is needed. I’d highly recommend hiring a manager with more industry experience to guide and teach the team during high-pressure times like these.

A special mention goes to Violet, who was incredibly kind and consistently checked on my order with the kitchen staff. Her hard work and professionalism stood out despite the stressful environment—thank you, Violet!

Ultimately, the responsibility falls on upper management for not equipping the front-end staff with the leadership and training needed, and for not properly staffing the kitchen for such a busy night. While the food was great, I hope to see improvements in organization and preparation during peak times in the future.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jennifer Bee","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXFO0fgPBTIA1yxL3IXSghRJ6EmshLC1YB1a72b-xeg3kpjHx0=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We like ordering Chinese food for New Year’s Eve and after seeing positive comments on the local Facebook groups, I thought I’d try Woking Dragon. I called a bit after 4pm and was surprised to hear we could pick up our order (seven dishes) in twenty minutes, or delivery before 5pm.

All dishes were perfect, and good portions too. The ginger beef, crispy breaded prawns, and dragon mixed greens were stand outs. We have lots of leftovers which means I don’t have to cook for a while. ;-)

We will definitely order again and I can’t wait to get my leftovers for lunch tomorrow!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOvoll5x-ugmDwlCnBNcz1AEX7mNqnRA8VRWng2&fid=0x0:0x898188a487161c37"],"When":"2024-1-1"},{"Name":"Brittany G","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVRln3edCQZy4eIJWxl6Z_lj8lSlxw4wvRKO5IkeK_2Xd1MZTZURQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Our usual go to was closed when we wanted to order. We ordered 4 individual meals and one of them was missing a sweet and sour order. With paying $90 for feeding my family I called in and let them know not expecting them to only replace my item but they exceeding it with great service. They didn’t just give an individual serving of the pork but an entree portion and fried rice to compensate! The service and phone service was amazing! Will be ordering again","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Frank Reiter","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW15lY4LVpS801XttkePhwWnIgWbJbkUqbRqcmq17Hr9jQY8EeN=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Food and service were both very nice.  I love the garlic calamari and the hot sauce (not part of the dish, but a nice combination if you enjoy some heat).","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNpNO5wwTmiIQs4xcAobMPYPvawIkSkE5I5ze2u&fid=0x0:0x898188a487161c37"],"When":"2024-5-10"},{"Name":"Ed Saxton","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWNb4QcEnLutDQ1n6BX1NRrkvTayY3wJJFW3Qi0N3gL0iuAYAA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"Prices at this place have gone up 40% in 3 years and the portions have gotten a lot smaller. Just let that sink in.. The food here used to be worth the price but it really isn’t anymore.
Something that used to be a rare treat has become unjustifiable/ unaffordable.
If someone can explain to me how these prices make sense I will be more than happy to remove this review, however the math ain’t mathin’.
Unless someone tells me eating this food will cure my knee pain, I will not be coming back.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Marly Sas","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJDkU3WXHU8p4mUFPDAgNwKlyF9aXYw-JJYUVo7s3-y7grmZA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"we ordered a variety of dishes off Uber eats! We loved the Szechuan Fiery beef,Szechuan Fiery chicken, combo 3&4 and potstickers! It was absolutely delicious and fantastic ! We will be ordering again in the future!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMuz49HMyVmg8hQyjaN-3AodOU6Eq875CwgNZf7&fid=0x0:0x898188a487161c37"],"When":"2024-3-8"}]
