user_reviews:
[{"Name":"Kim Withers","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXKKnnFnw4jT31ns6Kf5JAE_mqFWTs-3cVvpPNOg1rsbgYPYGl3=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"The staff are very friendly and the service was fast. The portions are size is huge. Unfortunately, the food was just ok. My beef broth was warm water and the spring roll was abandoned after one bite.  I love Pho with usually great layers of flavour but this was not it.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMVHQeNQdBSdRvMLithlCAHQ5clg64xex06Ja41&fid=0x0:0x55e781ca19889a62"],"When":"2024-10-25"},{"Name":"Tyler","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX5pgqDcV4jXxCDs44gFpKqBE7-kpDe9pqH0qySpykt9h70rZWn=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I recently visited Pho Super Bowl in Coquitlam and decided to try their pork vermicelli (#66), and it did not disappoint! The portion was generous, with a perfectly grilled, tender, and flavorful pork that had a deliciously caramelized edge. The vermicelli was fresh and well-cooked, served alongside crisp vegetables like bean sprouts, cucumbers, and lettuce, which added a nice crunch to the dish. The fish sauce was light and tangy, complementing the savory pork perfectly without overwhelming the flavors.

The balance of flavors in this bowl was spot on, and the accompanying spring rolls were crispy and packed with flavor, a fantastic addition. The presentation was also great—very appetizing with vibrant colors.

Service was quick and friendly despite the restaurant being busy, and the atmosphere was casual and inviting. Whether you’re a fan of pho or looking to explore other options on their menu, I highly recommend giving their pork vermicelli a try!

This captures the key aspects of your experience while emphasizing the flavor and overall atmosphere of the restaurant!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM5qsIkpneH8Vr6cu3bOhK43yolHJZKWNakgeS-&fid=0x0:0x55e781ca19889a62"],"When":"2024-10-11"},{"Name":"Brandon Collins","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXJftMou5k5OJyPtZPxUAjCRk0hWFHK-OghGtQJYsSNzGar9YlLzA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Saw this place on an Instagram reel showing of the variety of traditional veitnamese dishes , all of the meals looked amazing so I had to try it for myself . My son ordered a banh mi ga ( veitnamese sub with chicken) it was ok at best I probably wouldn't order it again . My wife ordered the gom ga ( chicken and rice) she said it was ok also.  We ordered the appetizer of chicken wings they were great ! And for myself I ordered the pho thai bo vein ( pho beef ball and steak ) and yes it was definitely a homerun not only a large quantity but good broth and lots of meat . I'd definitely come back but I'd stick to the pho as that's what this place does best at .","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPtldi51cOIJHaWHgfDa1MC5B_neT-gvoQ0M2R3&fid=0x0:0x55e781ca19889a62"],"When":"2024-8-26"},{"Name":"jay Ko","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKx55LCvOrGRPp-bz8WbkRCn4gZDlDBBz0K8yV1EKgnLoTqXw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"The food is good and the price is reasonable. BUT I AM NOT COMING BACK, for sure, because they keep messing around with the bill. This is the third time it’s happened to me. Yesterday, I paid, left with my receipt, and noticed something was wrong—they charged way more than the listed prices. I went back to the store with the bill, and they just said, ‘Sorry about that,’ and handed me back $19 in cash. At this point, I have to say this feels intentional because it’s happened three times now.

Be careful about overcharging here.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOXU-etp9J401XNl8xOiZZVO7Htrv6WKijYtByj&fid=0x0:0x55e781ca19889a62"],"When":"2024-10-26"},{"Name":"Shivanie Kumar","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVFbollGMNfPGQeQeE1iu9uspIWWpZ_q45kMCmZRZ6VvynDEjM=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"WORST FOOD EVER!!! Its not even cooked properly. The first wing was okay but others are like they just served it as undercooked tried checking it with fingers before eating. I guess Getting order in 5 mins is no surprise that they serves u raw. And servers are talking to each other and I am seeing the man using his hand to clean his teeth I am not sure if he has tooth pick or what.. NEVER GOING BACK HERE!!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMhaby_MvrAfawZ9TQcyI0HYpdTLgg7iknx9dta&fid=0x0:0x55e781ca19889a62"],"When":"2024-12-11"},{"Name":"Jade Chin","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLJWSVoZW1CCY-_xhdgdeWOnL28P_e39FAE_t38PKZ_hYo17g=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Comfortable dine in experience. Washroom was clean. Food was fantastic. Service was top notch, fast and efficient. Had the beef stew, large, great portions. Reasonable price. The appetizer fried spring roll was done perfectly. The fried chicken wings were fantastic -- crispy, tasty, not overly salty, lots of meat, juicy. Strawberry smoothie was excellent. Nothing bad to complain about.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Huang Recca","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIDF647f8wTC9xYKRRSNQV8CPkQJrc1Y81nFNPZerRiknh_jw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"Heard raving reviews about this and came to try. Portion is big. So you might want to have a take away container just in case. Noodles and soup were on the bland side. But to make up for it, the lemongrass chicken was kinda salty. Fried squid tentacles were replaced with non tentacles part and it didnt even fill up the plate that was served with, so lowkey felt scammed. Service was ok, just that had to call out a few times to get too up for tea (as the chicken seems to have overdosed on salt) , it is also in a busy complex so it depends the time you arrive to snag a parking spot.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOCYENXaTqEtkYSY2lS33ozYXVgNFIqK7rnSj28&fid=0x0:0x55e781ca19889a62"],"When":"2024-5-5"},{"Name":"Hannah DG","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU037jR4UWeBkpznNrgaH8CsxofxgLROiN8hrJaQSHBDftuIk7R=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"SPOILED MEAT- DO NOT COME HERE AND RISK GETTING FOOD POISONING.
My boyfriend and I have been loyal to Pho Superbowl for over 2 years since moving to the area. I have also been to their new location on Kingsway. We have tried many different dishes from their House special pho, spicy beef pho, house special with saté broth, their rice dishes, vermicelli dishes, chicken wings, salad rolls, and their bahn mi. We have brought our friends and family several times to eat at Pho Superbowl because we loved their food and generous portions.

Today, I ordered #66 grilled pork and spring roll vermicelli which I have had plenty of times before, but for some reason, the grilled pork tasted sour and off, like the meat had already gone bad. I waved down one of the servers to let them know and she was nice enough to offer to change it to a different meat. I picked out all of the spoiled meat into a small bowl which she took back to the kitchen. Then, I heard the head cook angrily yell in the background. Shortly after, a different lady came back with the same bowl with the spoiled pork and said they can't give me a new one because "I already ate it". What do you mean I already ate it? It wasn't like I finished all the food and asked for a new bowl for free! I just took out all of the spoiled pork out of my vermicelli bowl and planned to eat the rest of the food!

I am beyond disappointed especially since we loved coming to eat here and we were always generous with tipping.... but we are not coming back. I understand that restaurants can sometimes have a one-off, and I am usually willing to give another chance. However, since they did not want to fix the issue after I brought it up (especially regarding food safety like spoiled food), Pho Superbowl doesn't deserve another chance.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOmdrUm8xnjIm9gt1H0Nz5JcPG-4epoJmnZ1RFQ&fid=0x0:0x55e781ca19889a62"],"When":"2024-4-28"}]

user_reviews:
[{"Name":"Connie Robson","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVcD3CpjQ2KIT9ukXOt3q6p8B8SMkttAVRJsUo328I8e2x3t4I=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"I ordered the apple cinnamon French toast but there was not a single piece of apple on it. My friend ordered the same thing and again, no apple. It was still very good but I don’t know if the missing apple was an oversight or if it doesn’t come with it then the description is misleading.

Overall I liked the restaurant - very lively and popular and will come back to try some of the other menu options.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipN-O4q7PCGAe_Q_exHXbh66W5xF0fvIy5DjDcX0&fid=0x0:0x23a839fa4c1f06bf"],"When":"2024-11-17"},{"Name":"BABAK TORABI","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXte01Tl3Efa_m0ADFo96Kz1F79A0-Ap8jSjGIMNFygHZjHQcocIQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We recently visited this restaurant again and noticed that the portions of some dishes are quite large for one person. This time, we decided to share, which worked out perfectly.

The food tastes great, the quality is excellent, and the staff is incredibly friendly. The environment is clean, modern, and welcoming. One of the highlights is the open kitchen, which lets you see the chefs at work—always a nice touch.

The only downside is the noise level. The sound seems to reflect a lot, likely due to the ceramic flooring, which is easy to clean but amplifies noise. The ceiling also doesn’t seem to have much for sound absorption.

It was a bit crowded on a Saturday morning, but that’s to be expected for such a popular spot. Overall, a great experience!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipN5kNNNIObhREuuSscKObbYbvBBCdaYd8SvrHjg&fid=0x0:0x23a839fa4c1f06bf"],"When":"2024-11-20"},{"Name":"Annie","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJAG4UtHNdn-C74S5I053c9lMdRMdh_AH35u090AgjHoFmF2GSW=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"So happy to finally have brunch and it did not disappoint!  The location is easy to find and lots of free parking. The atmosphere is easy and friendly and the food and service were excellent. Can’t wait to come back.

Returned with my family and it was even better. Our server Gurleen was an absolute delight while she managed a busy restaurant full of guests. Today was savory and it was amazing. The boys shared the big 3 and it was more than enough. Can’t wait to come back!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPiCPG4ng_rPed3P8NoMqKZwG2zyzEYpkFnrOYt&fid=0x0:0x23a839fa4c1f06bf"],"When":"2024-7-12"},{"Name":"Craig’s Food and Fun","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUha2Q8WiUjbezKLoCbc8g-ZcFkFuHpjx0PE6RArmNeLmTAwJN4=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Food was amazing! And the staff was very friendly and professional, definitely coming back! We had the fried chicken eggs Benny and the fried chicken sandwich. The potatoes and fries were tasty and seasoned and the chicken crispy. The eggs were farm fresh and the hollandaise sauce was excellent!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPx6ygBpCV1nh9QvLFAAD3WtpH8Ta9carJ7YKDn&fid=0x0:0x23a839fa4c1f06bf"],"When":"2024-12-4"},{"Name":"Nick Wang","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocK9cUtJY153nRWD4hzNcIo_gDDe44hWUa0zRGkneCYmPYO49A=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great place for family!  We came here on a Sunday morning for their Kids Eat Free Special.   Between 7~9am, for every $25 order of an adult meal, you get a kid’s meal for free.  We ordered a Canadian breakfast and Pesto Philly steak, both tasted amazing.  Usually when you order a kid’s meal from restaurants, it’s small portion and not very appealing.  But the free kids’ meal at Pur and Simple, were full size crepes and waffles, filled with banana, chocolate chips, and strawberries.  I also really like the country style decor that they have.  Great vibe, great value and great food!  Definitely worth your visit.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO2uPEhDiPYzzlUmh-jAKSk098DjZpOsiek7DqQ&fid=0x0:0x23a839fa4c1f06bf"],"When":"2024-6-30"},{"Name":"Sia Ghaem","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUEMQ83Io5sE_IiypwGW5tpjSnD5RcP1dPzKLkdTOi-SisSW8bCuA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"We have been to Pur and Simple a few times and it has been a satisfactory experience every time. They are border line Good/great time restaurant. Not great to blow you away, but good enough to draw you back.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO1cabewFzUoYl0Ck3t7YQ0X5raQ_yGu8-dips2&fid=0x0:0x23a839fa4c1f06bf"],"When":"2024-9-23"},{"Name":"Tyler","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX5pgqDcV4jXxCDs44gFpKqBE7-kpDe9pqH0qySpykt9h70rZWn=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"During a recent visit to Pür & Simple in Port Coquitlam, my girlfriend and I enjoyed a delightful breakfast experience. The restaurant’s bright and modern ambiance created a welcoming atmosphere, complemented by attentive and friendly staff.

I opted for the Coconut French Toast, which featured thick slices of brioche infused with a subtle coconut flavor, topped with fresh fruits and a light dusting of powdered sugar. The combination of textures and flavors was both satisfying and indulgent.

My girlfriend chose the Gourmet Breakfast, a hearty platter that included perfectly cooked eggs, crispy bacon, savory sausage, and a side of their renowned P&S potatoes. Each component was prepared with care, resulting in a balanced and flavorful meal.

The service was exceptional; our server was attentive without being intrusive, ensuring our coffee cups were always filled and promptly addressing any requests. The menu offered a diverse selection of breakfast and brunch options, catering to various tastes and dietary preferences.

Overall, our experience at Pür & Simple was outstanding. The combination of delicious food, excellent service, and a pleasant atmosphere makes it a top choice for breakfast in Port Coquitlam. We look forward to returning and exploring more of their menu offerings.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOLLZ6a2rGBYbAJu6qxbOFMZlUqdNznKM-GgC9i&fid=0x0:0x23a839fa4c1f06bf"],"When":"2024-11-25"},{"Name":"Nazanin Tehrani","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLNvnOcnvQZmQRfgcZ1xIfiff0XhYrv3BK46Bu6rg2GKUDhBQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I had an excellent breakfast experience at Pur & Simple. The atmosphere was welcoming, and the food was just what I needed to start the day right. The menu offered a great variety of options, and everything I ordered was fresh, delicious, and beautifully presented.

A special shoutout to our host, Dyson, who provided outstanding service. He was attentive, friendly, and made sure we had everything we needed throughout our meal.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPtjwERVXfcA2zNYNfAsBJWo_5Pds5RsfhS84G2&fid=0x0:0x23a839fa4c1f06bf"],"When":"2024-8-22"}]

user_reviews:
[{"Name":"Dan Yang","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWn20SO-hez6CdOPY0et6YJIfsXqZVK2JjuFROy8lc6ciazjVwLCQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We were staying at the Poco Inn for several days and we decided to try Izba. We had gone once last year for breakfast and wanted to try other things on the menu this time.

Food is absolutely amazing here. Service was excellent. We dined in and did take out a few times. We can't wait to come back to dine in when we visit BC again. The Pork Hock was amazing and I had to order it twice.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOkeN1QD0k77gLzuWNTChtSslZ8MsYKszhisKyY&fid=0x0:0xc4417d5c6f1e0d7d"],"When":"2024-9-19"},{"Name":"Ewa Jagla","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJt2Lx4cSyXVMUtHz5GqW2QX5giQiHT25H1LY2KPyEyH86PMQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Delicious food freshly cooked from scratch, awesome atmosphere, superb customer service. The best place to have Christmas party as well as small gatherings.
Highly recommend 😊","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNhWkgmxDtyb6rEjrVCF6m82pasIw5N0DVS3SmQ&fid=0x0:0xc4417d5c6f1e0d7d"],"When":"2024-11-22"},{"Name":"Angela Jeffery","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUtGyld6d4wIU2Lb7oe7xsoiq4r77iaBdF6nkFQ8ek01eF1q7c=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"We ate here as we stayed at the hotel for work, and I may come back to try some of the other menu items, based on the compliments of the others in the group.

The server was pleasant, as well as enthusiastic and knowledgeable about his menu recommendations. He was courteous about checking in and giving us space for our meeting.

The seating was comfortable, and even when it got busy at dinnertime, the ambient noise level still leant to easy conversation.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNqeLGhHKnP50PS663FCp_-g_jpbS2XjZyg9vTH&fid=0x0:0xc4417d5c6f1e0d7d"],"When":"2024-10-18"},{"Name":"Laura Thomas","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXJ1taLWiLR5Kqy6TcBzB6ZWgyoj4UBO3ZptGvBaE7P-Aow2HBl=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"We visited Izba last week and while it's a regular in our family gtg's I'd be remiss if I didn't brag about this terrific PoCo restaurant, with its cosy, modern, diner feel. They have booths and tables and they can easily accomodate large groups.

I am hearing sensitive and I find the noise volume in this restaurant to be perfect for my needs. I can hear my company's conversation, while not being too quiet. It's a great place to eat & catch up with family or friends.

While they have a terrific  breakfast & dinner menu, we usually visit at lunch. While we've tried many delicious items (shout out to their pierogies, schnitzel & cream of carrot soup!) we tend to have our favourites on their menu. Their chicken tacos are a huge hit with our family, although I lean towards their chicken club sandwich myself. Yum!  And for the late in the day breakfast lover amongst us, the brie & berries stuffed french toast is ah-mazing.

This is a great lunch spot with great service and great food. We love this local gem.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOR6It5KMGfKdXdWFlwEe9CsEMI6164BfCS_2qP&fid=0x0:0xc4417d5c6f1e0d7d"],"When":"2024-6-22"},{"Name":"K Kunz","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVJritYkEeakN5S6DMeaooDNRMG4rg18kYdKvuJy7Hp_4TwqoG2=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"It was our first time at Izba Bistro and we loved it! Our server Brenda was great! She was nice, attentive but also let us sit for awhile. Food was excellent. We started with the battered brie that came with fruit and a spicy berry compote. I then had the spinach and feta chicken and it was SO good. I loved that it came with spaghetti squash as well. You don't see that too often. My partner had the Vienna schnitzel with an egg on top. My partner being Austrian said it was different than what he's used to, but still enjoyed it. Lastly we had the sacher Austrian chocolate cake and that was also really fantastic! We definitely will be coming back soon!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPTHEmdhYUMMgbRx5jBghp47Wwy64aw3PImFw7B&fid=0x0:0xc4417d5c6f1e0d7d"],"When":"2024-4-22"},{"Name":"Varoujan Makdesian","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKfL2mqaxtwIkiG0HlyGX_xrPtFgM36rEWRUZvaEgqUWz0Duw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"****AVOID AT ALL COSTS****
I was really excited to try Izba, given its reputation for authentic Polish cuisine, but unfortunately, my experience was far from what I had hoped for.

First, the service was extremely slow. Despite the restaurant not being very busy, our server seemed disinterested and hardly checked on us. We had to flag them down multiple times just to get basic things like water refills.

The food, which I was looking forward to the most, was underwhelming. The pierogi were bland, lacking any real flavor or seasoning, and the filling was far too dry. The borscht was greasy and tasted more like something that had been reheated multiple times rather than freshly made. It was also way too salty, which made it hard to finish.

The manager/owner, when I raised my concerns, was dismissive and unhelpful. Rather than apologizing or offering a solution, they seemed indifferent to our experience. It’s always frustrating when management doesn’t take feedback seriously, and it only made the situation worse. It felt like they weren’t interested in improving their service or maintaining customer satisfaction.

Overall, I won’t be returning. There are plenty of other places offering better Polish food and a much more welcoming dining experience. I would not recommend this place to anyone.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Tones Jyler","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKK4GXgTVLnajqhYm0hfamOs6EgRB-CcfZKNyrEZSlfbU3odg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I have driven by this place so many times and wanted to try it. Really glad I finally did and you should too! Had the platter for 2 and it came with everything in the picture for 47$ (2 potatoe pancakes that are so crispy and delicious, polish sausage, a huge amount of perogies with lots of chopped bacon and sausage to go with it, 2 large cabbage rolls, salad, and some kind of carrot mango salad) me and my wife both left stuffed and our baby even had his fill too! It was so delicious and you can tell everything is home cooked with care! I highly recommend it!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNF0XwsVtW1OfgUUiRRKbghfLTu0ovz1VSWdmvU&fid=0x0:0xc4417d5c6f1e0d7d"],"When":"2024-7-6"},{"Name":"Kat s","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV2PheeHlSTOrgESZq7PphUL-4YpUmC6odPCrLoBmlFoDLLyzPn=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We had breakfast almost every day here while on our trip. Service was great, waitstaff was kind and accommodating of food allergies, and the food was always high quality. This will definitely be a spot we continue coming back to whenever we're in PoCo!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPKp-lMImM02uuFAI1z4isRNhCXkLkbDt4Yr4Xj&fid=0x0:0xc4417d5c6f1e0d7d"],"When":"2024-7-22"}]

[{"Name":"Leon Chen","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWPOnBvlGz2k_WzxOhCiURR3aRaAE5ffHXfUBJJ4GP7GBC5Wn8K=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"A cozy little cafe/brunch place with plenty of delicious dishes to choose from! They've got a nice portion size and we especially loved the way their toasts are made. I highly recommend their omelette :)","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMZ5K-Qmil3-5FfOu3HV6suOUB5_gTZaSdx6lXR&fid=0x0:0xc5b1d5425c13c8b1"],"When":"2024-8-24"},{"Name":"Joanna Fahmy","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJTznlA_q5Xa6Whv5wHF-yEDXEyOSOXOXBiPU7xtZRDBuF4Yw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Came here for breakfast, food was decent for the price. We were surprised by the cheaper prices compared to other breakfast places, our plates each were between $10-15!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMzu-Xt_jxAyTGDfs4rTT284gusElPuQMtjRPS0&fid=0x0:0xc5b1d5425c13c8b1"],"When":"2024-11-19"},{"Name":"Joanne Shih","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXximxdR2J0MX38SMpQXvX83o69PGyHXNObNbbK0mDK-tz8T9Z6=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Cozy neighbourhood brunch place! Came here years ago, I had a pretty good overall experience. This time revisiting, it’s as good:) Have lots of options on the menu with pretty good prices. If you’re looking for an easy layback weekend brunch with friends and family, this is the place😉😋","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOAEYQcbo_wZ58s9yrSFOG1879NJa2cpm6b4Dzw&fid=0x0:0xc5b1d5425c13c8b1"],"When":"2024-4-28"},{"Name":"Chanelle D","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXCEGtGi_rnAXcez2UGfi8tPvkrtnC3uoCyaDz_NpX-tJAfWp2A=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Great little local breakfast place in downtown PoCo. I like supporting local businesses especially when you see them trying so hard to give good service.  Food is delicious and if you are looking to take a break from cooking, this is a place to go. Many familiar dishes for breakfast and brunch. The prices are very reasonable so tip well. The portions are sufficient. Good value and easy on the wallet. Fast service. Great for walk in because parking is a limited at the front.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMC2XT0W0I6LPk5xzrNiIq7KCmlFqE6wzuS3_ZZ&fid=0x0:0xc5b1d5425c13c8b1"],"When":"2024-1-8"},{"Name":"Imran Cuttilan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKz9vHOBlaUTXNDsWXAFrX2NjKnPFKZDmrrx2BKyP3U2hXEVQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Don't be fooled by the outside, this place is a great find!
Honestly one of the best breakfasts I've had since moving to Vancouver. Don't expect gourmet meals, but hearty, well-cooked food for less than $50 to fill a hungry family of 4? Yes please!
It feels like a family run place and the wait staff clearly know their regulars. I'm almost considering moving to PoCo so I can eat here every weekend.
If I have one recommendation, skip the hash browns (fried potatoes are pretty much the same everywhere) and go for the wonderfully fluffy pancakes.
Cannot recommend this place enough.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Chun Ho Lau","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWeN6tyeslrX1zBXDjrKJdBmn-J6R7mrVei78Pf_EwSNa0qPEvB=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"This place is great for the price that you pay. Never did i imagine that you can find a less than $10 breakfast and with this amount of food. Swiss Sandwich with fries was great. The pancakes and eggs and sausage was good however next time we probably won’t get the sausage as the bacon on someone else’s table look better. The pancakes were light and fluffy. The hamburger steak and eggs - hmmm. I will skip next time and not great for 14.95. The pancakes and eggs and sausage was better got less than $9. I did change a hamburger for two sausages with my wife so the pictures won’t look right. But you can see the amount of food there is for such little price. It’s definitely a 4 star and I think next time I will find something that I will like to bring it back to 5 star. Not today though but close. For some reason they are not doing soup with the sandwiches so just beware. I certainly be back as there’s plenty to choose from.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPFN8PXpXtYRseN6e6FzlaSNbb833AYUq_pm39k&fid=0x0:0xc5b1d5425c13c8b1"],"When":"2022-9-10"},{"Name":"Emmanuel Carino","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVJ9g6OsewbE5PvEJQG0W2MrejjY87xqZcS0O_-lbnLLATuQeGq=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Amigo Pancake House is a delightful spot for a classic, no-frills breakfast. The pancakes are perfectly fluffy and made with care, offering a comforting start to your day. The atmosphere is cozy and welcoming, making it a great place to enjoy a relaxed morning meal. The service is warm and attentive, ensuring you feel right at home. If you’re looking for a simple, satisfying breakfast without the fuss, Amigo Pancake House is the perfect choice. Highly recommended for anyone who appreciates good food in a friendly setting","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Yvonne Chow","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKwIOIAqx6fGEXpwJ9wznPD-K-TC6RqVahvNzt21E-visP9PQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"The food may be decent, but the kitchen service is exceedingly slow. We were here for brunch - arrived at 1120 am, and we’re still waiting for our food more than 40 minutes later. This is for a table of 2 with no additions, sub-outs - just two breakfast mains. To be fair, they comped us a fruit salad but with other brunch options in the area, it’s not the fastest service for simple food.

We visited about a year and a half ago and had the same issue. Their kitchen management needs to be much better.

To be fair, it might be a weekend issue as my in-laws said they liked it when they visited on a weekday.

Probably won’t be coming back though. The service is lovely and we are happy to tip them well, but the kitchen management leaves much to be desired.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM4xqBL2ofcHFLZBewBZKBDJPaSYa0OSM7cCuox&fid=0x0:0xc5b1d5425c13c8b1"],"When":"2022-10-24"}]

I’ve just had one of the best burritos in my life 🌯","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Y Man","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUB62F2-VitrTkpd3TexeBmDt6LJ-Ec6lzQvbbyCIp7HJAIiB3b=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"I am actually surprised about the high star rating this place it has and I feel deceived by it. I ordered a Mexican salad bowl with chicken and a burrito. Each $13 dollars. The portion is very small for price. The burrito is smaller than my hand - it looks more like a small panini about the size of Iphone 11. The beef didn’t have much flavour. The chicken is bland and overcooked. [{"Name":"Sarah Okut","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLTH-O9yHrUXXSzwuweULzXw1pBbME2AVL3wPUzYMdoLT_dRg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I recently visited Pizza Pietra and really enjoyed their pizza and San Sebastian cheesecake. The pizza had a crispy crust with fresh, tasty toppings. It was delicious! The San Sebastian cheesecake was the best part—it was rich, smooth, and creamy, with a slightly caramelized top that gave it extra flavor. If you love desserts, you should definitely try this cheesecake!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipN3wU0_wer5w028bhetbEqdDgTlTPAd9mr8aiH5&fid=0x0:0x4640aee62581d2d2"],"When":"2024-10-16"},{"Name":"Mucahit Mert Alagoz","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUlZFzlr8OmJ6ReNSeqILjiXkPYOR-Wi6HlJhjaTTE_xGsRl7kohA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I really loved this small and cozy Turkish café run by two Turkish women. The staff is very warm and friendly. Although the menu is a bit limited, the breakfast options are quite delicious. I loved everything, from the sucuk (Turkish sausage) to the eggs and meat-filled pastries. For four people (we ordered a bit too much), the total was $105.
I definitely recommend it—a lovely café!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOZkVllSrfsqQVnk7-eaCEQy80caDFl6QFecd6N&fid=0x0:0x4640aee62581d2d2"],"When":"2024-11-16"},{"Name":"방새단Jp","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXPRFl5X_2oRYVKyp5YOzyZvBiFq4LXRAXvUH4K1gSFuhrTkvIu=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I ordered the poached eggs with avocado.
They took a while to get the plate ready, but it was much better than what I had hoped for. Ingredients were fresh, tasty and I would definitely come back again","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPW5MCUo0Kn75oa42Blt_gR0Ah7EI2gXYUVdZhL&fid=0x0:0x4640aee62581d2d2"],"When":"2024-11-6"},{"Name":"Mahesh Vanga","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU_R99DIUm3YNCVBnH6ipuMklk--v4TSFTsQ7Tybr4ECj_qR-ZP9A=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This is by far the best pizza place I have ever been to in the Mainland area. We explored this place as part of checking regular pizza places around, to our surprise this has been the best random pizza place ever been in fact the best pizza I ever had in the mainland area. Any food/pizza lover cannot miss this place, they got a wide variety of pizzas to offer as well.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO263l3lNZQ04gOHPrnihMubx8QyholXqUTO6DE&fid=0x0:0x4640aee62581d2d2"],"When":"2024-9-28"},{"Name":"Graham Sutton","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocL8UeAA1nmB6Ej3WgCR3VioNDAdhDivzoWDT4UCyjNTsgC4MA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Breakfast was awesome!  Traditional Turkish meals with lovely fresh bread and Turkish tea.  We'll definitely be back on a regular basis.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipODmWArQZDzyV5LCBa5m3uJi_01rXQ5LyF0EMno&fid=0x0:0x4640aee62581d2d2"],"When":"2024-11-20"},{"Name":"Onur Kaan KOÇ","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLl3-LHlkDHqQOafBmwY6xCPBlOCHVa2JkVR6DeNJcaxq3QYw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Clean, Happy and delicious Pizza Pietra, siezed my day 😋

At first I was hesitant because of the mixed reviews but I really wanted to give it a try, especially because of the praised stone oven and authentic dough.

I've been to most regions of Italy, ate a lot of very good pizza and I must say this pizza restaurant reminded me the times I was in Mediterranean.

You must use good quality ingredients and have precise dough craftsmanship, and have the right oven with the correct temperature to make a delicious pizza. But every body knows, in our modern times, this equation is quite impossible in big cities because of the cost and profit concerns.

But in this pizza shop they nearly got the perfect combination.

They have a real stove oven at the right temperature, good quality ingredients and handmade authentic dough.

Both pizza and Foccacia are nicely crusty and juicy. The Tomato sauce is not bitter nor too sweet, just yummy and fresh  ;-).

Toppings and mozzarella have a very good price to quality ratio.

All the ingredients are really really fresh 👍

A suggestion for them, I think you should make a pizza with different ingredients which are hard to find in PoCo

And for me the most important thing , people in this pizza shop are really happy, hospitable, positive and energetic. They really smile to you because they just want to. The total vibe is just like the warm and welcoming family owned pizza shops in Italy too 😍😍.

Ps: I asked the owner to tour the kitchen because of my cleanliness obsession. And yes he let me to quickly tour the kitchen and I'm amazed, this is a really really clean kitchen for BC standarts 😉","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipODw8DnBQZ_EDJZzRNN9UlLF96GZOid--UDy1PJ&fid=0x0:0x4640aee62581d2d2"],"When":"2024-3-28"},{"Name":"Aamir Sheergar","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUTKU4wfuc0kwoyEwJxy3N-nmGgBy-VjbHs41hImisM4pU2gpbxyQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great pizza, loved the thin crust. Friendly service from the ladies in the kitchen. One of my new favorite pizza places.

Also tried the cheesecake, it was not too dense and had just the right amount of sweetness, a great balance.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"M. Murat Kucuk","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWQxmakxls5MdK3S6o9QjUak841XsiEQ7PpJlT7cOAjNN9ECiE=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Prepare to be amazed by this extraordinary pizza haven nestled within town. Without hesitation, I wholeheartedly recommend this remarkable establishment to all pizza enthusiasts. During our recent visit, we indulged in their custom 2-in-1 pizza, an exquisite combination that left our taste buds in a state of pure bliss.

The staff at Pizza Pietra were not only kind, but also exceptionally helpful, ensuring that our dining experience was nothing short of perfection. Their attentiveness added an extra touch of delight to an already exceptional culinary adventure.

Do not, under any circumstances, allow yourself to miss out on the opportunity to visit this exceptional pizza establishment. It is an experience that promises to tantalize your senses and leave an indelible impression.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPPoC8qGLwQyu83S1THS9PbLQVeSXqTbUxjDY8X&fid=0x0:0x4640aee62581d2d2"],"When":"2023-6-25"}]

It was good, but I did prefer regular soft-serve one. other one is pineapple one, not on my taste. it might be good if it's a hot summer day. kinda mix feeling between gelato and regular ice cream. Their service is okay. The atmosphere is awesome, walking distance to the park. nice view. It feels like back to the 90s cafe, awesomely cool.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMY_597GMTaUTpDPVWsTl-ynpMQVvr_G0c35yFV&fid=0x0:0x767d5da688e131ec"],"When":"2024-9-6"},{"Name":"Kaitlyn Jung","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU3Z8RTVAtMfrX6uG6JFFOYzsyTXI7YKgjW6WLd73YQIb_urJDkYQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We were coming back from a hike and this was a great treat! Good selection of baked goods, sandwiches and salads. Atmosphere is great and service was friendly. Decent variety of vegetarian options. Nice outdoor seating area. Fortunately no dogs permitted inside. I’m looking forward to my next visit.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMeZleCGlboyXvdrttCoSq0tVnfVjNfm1cYNYKM&fid=0x0:0x767d5da688e131ec"],"When":"2024-7-1"},{"Name":"Scott Lee","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXHpW7vGME__Zs4wKjXR04Upnw88bkVVyz-H2288JsHocq9vI3r=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"It’s a small cafe in Rocky Point that serves good coffee and solid dessert! We got the ice americano because it was 30 degrees outside and a ferrero rocher cream puff. They were both delicious and the cafe provided a much needed refuge from the sun. We didn’t get to try the ice cream but we already know that it’s going to be amazing.

Come check it out if you want some good coffee and dessert in Rocky Point!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNOjLTNHVILzloQN2HDBWsl7zzcmaPCqrLneDs9&fid=0x0:0x767d5da688e131ec"],"When":"2024-8-4"},{"Name":"Champagne Kingdom","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWT9L6nbhgKeVF6uvC80gh6he8ZgVExYxBb0bRQFJovbeiruBo=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"We've passed by this place numerous times, so we finally stopped by on a warm day to try their creamery treats. We opted for a soft-serve ice cream and the bubble gum flavor, which was absolutely delicious! We also picked up an Aussie pie to go, but unfortunately, it didn't quite live up to our expectations.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNenA_pguyXZdV4JQ4R4gJmiipKqFis1w67fdqa&fid=0x0:0x767d5da688e131ec"],"When":"2024-7-27"},{"Name":"Phyllis Tee","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXtHTl5JLpAHiaGIa8m_bWtHrZ84dJMWFq9MtMaT4ZwV6hFBwY=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Best cream puffs I’ve ever had. Got the vanilla and Ferrero rocher flavours. The puffs were so light and the creamy fillings were oozy delicious. Would def come back again!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipODLxhunT5qrllRZISW0ElcSmID7pUNZCvYjRSc&fid=0x0:0x767d5da688e131ec"],"When":"2024-8-22"},{"Name":"J Koo","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVjFfTA1VnOQ6njd8inE8tUWA2rlWt4bUy_SkmPUgHZq-4VXWnK=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"I like coffee and soft icecream, specially the pumpkin soft serve was the best but their sofa condition was gross. I won’t never sit the sofa. I ordered chocolat cake, it was super dry and the texture was rough. I think this place will get better if they make better bake goods.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM1Bfk9wpsQoAnsO8Q8-qXsTeWcR6Afhy1ZT7wx&fid=0x0:0x767d5da688e131ec"],"When":"2021-10-9"},{"Name":"Tyler","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX5pgqDcV4jXxCDs44gFpKqBE7-kpDe9pqH0qySpykt9h70rZWn=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Nestled in the heart of Port Moody, Rocky Point Canteen by Rocky Point Ice Cream is a true gem, perfect for those seeking a delightful treat in a picturesque setting. Recently, I had the pleasure of trying their famous Dole Whip, and I must say, it was nothing short of extraordinary. The creamy texture and the perfect balance of sweetness and tanginess made it the best Dole Whip I have ever had. Despite a bit of melting, even on a cool day, its delightful flavor was an absolute winner.

The Canteen offers a cozy and welcoming atmosphere with both indoor and outdoor seating options. While seating can be limited, the nearby park provides a perfect backdrop for enjoying your treats outdoors. Alongside their renowned soft serves, they also offer a variety of delicious sandwiches, cookies, brownies, and more, catering to diverse tastes and preferences.

The customer service here is commendable, with friendly staff ensuring that your experience is enjoyable. The Canteen's popularity is evident from its glowing reviews, consistently rated highly across various platforms for its quality offerings and pleasant environment.

Whether you're a local or just passing through Port Moody, Rocky Point Canteen is a must-visit spot. I will definitely be returning to relive the delightful experience and try more of their offerings. Highly recommended for anyone with a sweet tooth or looking for a great place to unwind!","Images":null,"When":""}]

[{"Name":"Ping D","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV-_KBk5-yIGzGmKAkX1L-6QPRrz_RZKkgRnIY4il5exhoL_sw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"It was a perfect lunch. Kids menu pizza was the same size as the regular pizza. Food and service were both very good. I’d suggest they offer more selections of pizza flavours at lunch time. It’s definitely a good deal to go at lunch. The comfortable meal started with complimentary dinner rolls with garlic oil.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipN47_Do9ZdDwPr-MU16mYYSZu6ND1uoZmOWqwg4&fid=0x0:0xcb392bf507fb5484"],"When":"2024-9-29"},{"Name":"Amanda Green","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWX2-QkU6r0X4DLM6-w27hOoQabXaFOXnHBh92gU3KWWKAd6KWGjA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We have ordered takeout before and loved it, so we decided to dine in this time. Very cozy atmosphere and lovely service. The food was so, so fresh and the flavours were outstanding. I ordered the Scusa Mi Pomodoro and I understand now why it's a challenge winner - it was to die for, and I can't remember the last time I had such good, fresh, perfectly cooked prawns. Will definitely be back!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO0E5mjnxKtwgfWXwsftGkVtde8Fcyw_qHRefWm&fid=0x0:0xcb392bf507fb5484"],"When":"2024-12-20"},{"Name":"Jessameen Dela Peña","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX9mRpmL8-ZJUG7UPFcnsjzRdxjABif-MswbO1rxgJyyWfns8Jd=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We had a wonderful family dinner at this restaurant! The ambiance is truly lovely, creating a warm and inviting atmosphere. The staff went above and beyond, being both accommodating and welcoming throughout our meal. We highly recommend the Baked Chicken Parmesan—it was absolutely delicious! A great experience all around!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMC3AKdGWBqxc-jukm25cD5f_HXE9kVmRakX-oM&fid=0x0:0xcb392bf507fb5484"],"When":"2024-12-8"},{"Name":"Nathan Ferlan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUBBwm7N9m9VsEZe8oXWT3QVjEQHlJhduQ22vfMGOziLtc2Ouo=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"A Culinary Experience to Remember!

⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️

If you’re looking for a dining experience that leaves you craving more, look no further. I recently had the pleasure of indulging in the most exquisite Pasta & Prawns, and I’m still savoring every memory of it. Each bite was a masterpiece—perfectly cooked pasta with tender, flavorful prawns, all bathed in a rich, savory sauce that danced on my palate. The balance of flavors was simply divine, making it one of the best dishes I’ve ever had.

But what truly made the night unforgettable was the outstanding service. From the moment we arrived, the staff made us feel like we were more than just customers—they made us feel like family. Our server was down-to-earth, warm, and attentive in a way that made the whole evening feel special. Every request was met with a genuine smile and care that is rare to find.

The ambiance, the incredible food, and the impeccable service all came together to create a perfect dining experience. I had such a great time, and I’m already counting down the days until my next visit. Highly recommend!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP6ocpt4jzjfqUqjB2OE7Fa55VrOmI8L5U_KNDR&fid=0x0:0xcb392bf507fb5484"],"When":"2024-9-30"},{"Name":"James Mendonca","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKDOYVs1G-8iT9QF6Fj3_nUauDo1DS6zISrEp3lZ9wij4inDQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Pasta Polo is an exceptionally great Italian restaurant that serves quality food. You know the workers take pride in their food and service when they post the restaurant's review articles on the walls.

I ordered the Osso Bucco with the Virgin Purple Sour drink. I was served complimentary bread with my entrée that included butter and a bottle of fermented garlic. The bread tasted pretty great on its own while the garlic made it taste much better. The Osso Bucco was delicious with the Bolognese sauce. The side pesto pasta was very good and was well seasoned with parmesan. The non-alcoholic Purple Sour tasted excellent with its exceedingly sweet flavours.

The servers were very formal with their customers when it comes to preparing their tables. They check on me as often as possible during busy hours while maintaining a positive attitude. The establishment was dark yet classy and clean.

I look forward to eating as this restaurant again to try their other entrees.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNXlV9QLG73dgmJm2MgWDAp3IaT80Wb7UqKSEgR&fid=0x0:0xcb392bf507fb5484"],"When":"2024-12-15"},{"Name":"S Lee","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWDCpcHtfixdQ1nlZ-cnjxErMYcSiJY3vif9B2kRQjg0W11mPsG=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"It’s been a few months since we were here last. We ordered the chicken Marsala and gnocchi.  Both were delicious!  I love the Marsala sauce!  My husband enjoyed the garlic oil that was served with a bun.  The bun was ok. Could have been tastier.  I enjoy good bread and this wasn’t anything to write home about.  Service was excellent. We had Thea and she was great!  I also enjoyed their art gallery.  So much talent.  We will definitely be back.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPZaMW99B_vyd2v_54Cdz758FoKxJtAP-r08b85&fid=0x0:0xcb392bf507fb5484"],"When":"2024-12-1"},{"Name":"Y Man","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUB62F2-VitrTkpd3TexeBmDt6LJ-Ec6lzQvbbyCIp7HJAIiB3b=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Lovely Italian restaurant. The carbonara was tasty and creamy,  pasta is fresh and the sauce was enough to cover all the pasta and not drenched in it.  The meatballs were tender and mixed with fresh herbs,  a perfect meat side to the pasta.  The tiramisu was delicious,  creamy melts in your mouth.  Definitely coming back to try other dishes","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOdg_N9cATCFpMd2RK_yR7Qj4KSOp6mP1XOgxD7&fid=0x0:0xcb392bf507fb5484"],"When":"2024-9-20"},{"Name":"Marnie Eudela-Umlas","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXg_gVRD_Hd9V3XIUh6_P71KHCryea9xsHYGqrZHTuXW_jdxEU=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Spent our Mother’s Day celebration in this restaurant and we had a great time. Everything was awesome from food to their service. Our server even took our photos, too bad I forgot his name. The pizzas were all soo good and my fave was the Anchovy pizza. Pastas were yummy and their desserts too were all a treat. We will surely be back :)","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPbGw58cAzM4X4wXEw-LloHV5v2YTXfNlioydQo&fid=0x0:0xcb392bf507fb5484"],"When":"2024-7-2"}]

[{"Name":"Avis Woo","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXh4Pb-SJt2DTMUggN2-tIRxEo8pAErRU5SI_TxM4gC-gvdVBym=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great place for family brunch and dinner! Dishes all come in n big portion! Coffee refilled unlimited times! Tables and environment is hygienic and seating quite spacious and comfortable even for senior citizen with backache like me. Toilet is clean! Waiter and waitress crew are all very nice and professional too! Love this restaurant very much❤️❤️❤️❤️","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPza0ew2GjCDcnw3yaVoLhK8iMmk0FFxjlS2rw5&fid=0x0:0x1d1cd1ad544caa40"],"When":"2024-8-10"},{"Name":"Kai-Chun Lin","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUjTiDNcTKlmyRrDWdGPFt530dlO3QJbviz_GUObBc3bQ0rNmRp=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This is one of my favorite restaurants in Coquitlam as it's a place where I'm guaranteed to have a good time.

Food - the food isn't the most amazing thing I've ever tasted, BUT every single one that I've tried was at least good or better. There's basically no bad choice in the menu.
Service/atmosphere - the seats are spacious and comfortable, the waitresses are always friendly (even more so to kids!), we never had to wait too long for our food... it's just a great experience all around.
Price - with the above points, it would've already been one of my restaurants of choice, but then they went ahead and kept the price reasonable and that just seals the deal for me.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipN90L9zlD4vK0EDnXwB3NnlbNYPDfIUE5NcHqHh&fid=0x0:0x1d1cd1ad544caa40"],"When":"2024-9-22"},{"Name":"Omid Dadgari","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWXY5oTTgmTf1M1XQYNbrrLX-SdVGDzUB3Iw3aDSyAgQLf2_BwYgw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"I visited Coquitlam Grill for breakfast today and ordered Steak and eggs. The overall quality of the ingredients was very good. However, I ordered my steak medium, but it arrived well-done. Despite this, the quality was still good. The quantity of the food was very generous, offering great value for the price. It made me full, even though I hadn't eaten dinner or supper yesterday. The servers were attentive and friendly. The atmosphere was typical of a North American restaurant and quite enjoyable. Overall, a decent experience with room for improvement on the steak preparation."","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNT61QeH3ufJtT_GqPt1Sg0rufpTlP24BeUhlEu&fid=0x0:0x1d1cd1ad544caa40"],"When":"2024-7-9"},{"Name":"Julie B","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW4pd43YT5KSqkORSPaVbra7_KcodZ1kkwID5yaolZD_WuCOEiQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"What an amazing restaurant. We went just after noon on a Sunday only waited a few minutes and were seated. The place was packed. Everyone thoroughly enjoyed their meals and beverages.
Food was Ultimate Omelet
Mexican Pulled Pork Hash
Tex Mex Omelet
Eggs Haida Benny
Drinks were margarita, mimosas and a Ceasar.
The service was fantastic and Susan was amazing.
Everyone raved about their dishes and everyone cleaned their plated and both styles of harsh browns by far were the best we have ever had.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNatRTF11J76msxdL31ksun0mlD6h6LFwhaBmNW&fid=0x0:0x1d1cd1ad544caa40"],"When":"2024-7-30"},{"Name":"Thomas Chen","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUITuDRjw9J9Us45xAUXKSfp8lG2sJ2s04TW_lNAi_G6a5d62ur=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Just came here for a dinner. Thought it was good overall. Satisfactory but not amazing. I had the steak and it was cooked nicely. I wouldn’t rush back because the value isn’t very good.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOJH7QVel_maomATRS9LUNPh_6vm10Rj-xcyjR2&fid=0x0:0x1d1cd1ad544caa40"],"When":"2024-8-19"},{"Name":"Rakin Hassan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXandqMb5qdp3U7pCkKHH5i5AInuGc7KeC3c0mJR9W6MOUUvQAlEw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"Don't order the turkey dinner if you like flavor. Butter, chicken, lamb, curry, Mariani rice, curried calamari all were excellent.
No need to drive into Vancouver anymore for this type of food.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMF0BTwhAg7PfswQh1pM6oJ8WOC0K4ozUBmqE6c&fid=0x0:0xf7cc60cb2ceeb0c9"],"When":"2024-11-2"},{"Name":"Luke Weng","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXn1tdfwXfRnZVszKV8bZBNwooyRqfHv0VT8T0EAQWyUrqTrrO6aQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba7-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I love this place. Right when you walk in, the ambience is just dimly lit and romantic. They even have a mini waterfall fountain.

The staff were very nice and welcomed us to our seats. The menu was a bit expensive with the smaller portions, I kind of wish there were more curry, but the naan were huge! 😁 Our server even checked on us to see if our food was good.

We tried chicken korma and goat vindaloo. It was my first time trying goat. It tasted just like beef.

They even complimented me on my goose bag hehe. [{"Name":"Neda G","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXcXBADLi2CMhn5hf9f-JdbOlYYM_LHhdjb9JmX03VjxzMph4k=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The reviews are legit! This place is a hidden gem. We had a lovely breakfast with my kids, mom and husband. The service was good despite only one person working, she did awesome and they were very respectful of my daughter's allergies.

More importantly, the FOOD was AMAZING!!! Crispy gorgeous potatoes, really yummy pancake and waffles and great coffee. Will absolutely go back!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMZm2JrIJBpWvMNrTgyP1KWz2ol7OXkf14yCZLp&fid=0x0:0xde5d02ec9b39e76b"],"When":"2024-8-23"},{"Name":"Cherilyn Morris","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIFSsTxkRHOvnhVnL21RRcRzjanEDvQ_-BctHEQEFo9i_I6jA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We ordered via a delivery service and were very pleased with the food from PK's Diner. We gave a 5 for atmosphere as we have read reviews stating how comfortable the diner is and therefore had to give a 5 for that reason. We had the Bacon Cheeseburger and Clubhouse sandwich. Both were delicious. My husband said that the burger is one of the best that he has had. The burger was loaded with tomatoes, bacon and onions and he really liked the burger sauce that came with it as well. The bacon was thick and my husband said that the caramelized onions made the burger. I also found my Clubhouse to have been very good also with thick bacon, ham, and a generous amount of grilled chicken. The fries were crispy and the picture with the Clubhouse did not have all the fries that came with the order. We both have left overs for tomorrow. We are always cautiously optimistic when ordering home delivery due to the food not being fresh out of the kitchen. Well, we were so pleased with our meals and will definitely be ordering again. We are looking forward to trying out more items on the menu. Thank you so much PK's.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOLTqRnbF0525X_IBQ69XBMilRq6EUKYroOWi1f&fid=0x0:0xde5d02ec9b39e76b"],"When":"2024-11-3"},{"Name":"Kim Nguyen","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIR3fyXypuJm8ILEdOCVPODC97_SULpf89BUpmEUxYYnr0uBA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Breakfast tasted great. The service is excellent, super friendly staff. Their breakfast menu is almost like desserts, especially waffles and French toasts are unbelievable delicious, moist and crispy at the same time! I love my chicken lemongrass, so tender and flavourful. We can’t wait to try all of their dishes. To add to how wonderful this place is…the price is so affordable!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNfrFZiCKbIhIzaUyEMRXaImFdwP6Ap1U7eiGgh&fid=0x0:0xde5d02ec9b39e76b"],"When":"2024-4-8"},{"Name":"Deborah H","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIsXwwC3s9WyQKJ7Zs95PXuhLbAGHn9sk0S1KGXgVkYpWzFwg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"What a nice surprise to find this great brunch place! [{"Name":"Geraldine Sangalang","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUcAsqfNVs6uRfmsJ5FtsU66GdsPGBE4zo_tn8DnG79e7VADqel9Q=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Very popular local breakfast and brunch spot. Be ready for a wait, but it's worth it if you're looking for generous portions and sweet rewards.

We ordered a few dishes to try:

Apples and Cinnamon were exactly that. Sweet and delicious with just enough tartness.

The Mexicasa Omelet was savoury and spicy. Wonderfully satisfying, and a huge portion.

We had a hard time deciding between The King Kong and Bowser. But the toasted coconut won, and we went with Bowser. Believe it or not, it wasn't too sweet. The flavour and texture of the pancake helped to balance the dish.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNtawtl5BET-xx7jUpEtFONFxkBUI9Bfsvlqihi&fid=0x0:0xaaebff47a4a99ef2"],"When":"2024-10-15"},{"Name":"Juan José Salaya","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX1Ln__1lVc-JSwJxu3Sudj7VGGpDHTTaI6ATzhk7kkdUk_WRTN=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Amazing service from Shauna, fast en friendly.
I had the chocolate waffle, insane! And huge portions.
But the savory pancake not the best, hipster hash. The pancake was good but the side of hash and vegetables were not very good.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPmaviqW2sU_R_MfMRdvFHaU01XhNLfVwSVCcOH&fid=0x0:0xaaebff47a4a99ef2"],"When":"2024-8-9"},{"Name":"Mar","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWWTdC3Cu0qquRYQVKhOdWcOmJsma73tOEyPAbRghfK5B9Xyfw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Quiet and cozy place on weekdays. My favorite dish of all time is Veggie I Love You, which comes with a pancake. The veggies are always fresh and neatly sliced. The only drawback is the high price","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNoiGISJgSmJLSHz_XDKv3UeFGIR2oQ23GqinXJ&fid=0x0:0xaaebff47a4a99ef2"],"When":"2024-10-9"},{"Name":"Jeff Downer","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXl3HQ-1C4N-_a7ykvhIi5aM883AB-cDQVYb1xeenCY7zekayvZ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"I had high hopes for this place. The hash just didn’t deliver. Pretty average Sysco quality potato hash with premade tasting hollandaise that resembled cheese. One slice and a half of avocado : ( I just wish it tasted more homemade and less store-bought. The pancake was good! Sweet and caramelized. Not worth the price of the dish (Hipster Hash)
My partner’s chocolate banana waffles were a hit though. Very good and nice portion.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNtalSDrAz-3j5GtPKct2PF6onzeKeFu4j88AIk&fid=0x0:0xaaebff47a4a99ef2"],"When":"2024-8-11"},{"Name":"danakhatib","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVkw_MS-bFFQL-DqU_kCatDuVYGKImx-f2Z5AnYQHBCy9-uZ6_t=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Service was fantastic! They split our foods onto seperate plates (without us asking) because we wanted to share some dishes, which was very kind! Food was great, we got the chocolate waffle, which was delicious and the smoked salmon benny. I’ve had better hollandaise sauce but overall everything was awesome!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOcXsNe5b-w07YgnnqAfyFuObJiLP2t5VicwA1B&fid=0x0:0xaaebff47a4a99ef2"],"When":"2024-8-15"},{"Name":"Kiah Rose","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWTVXBfiLNTJ8gFd9zcQjhLGEsYxsifqJuzzyh3SEwJwRrMplme=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"If you’re looking for incredible food and an amazing atmosphere, The Big Flat Pancake is the place to be! The quality of the food is absolutely top-notch — everything is fresh, flavorful, and made with care. The pancakes are delicious, and the portions are generous!

What really sets this place apart, though, is the staff. They’re full of positive energy and always make you feel like part of the family. We shared lots of laughs, and their warm hospitality truly gave us a fantastic start to our Saturday!

I love supporting local, family-owned businesses, and The Big Flat Pancake is exactly the kind of place that deserves your attention. I highly recommend giving it a try!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMy6zOwu4HHfJ_gTbG6krgQtrhQd5D-xVfx0wsj&fid=0x0:0xaaebff47a4a99ef2"],"When":"2024-11-9"},{"Name":"Davina Johnsen","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXOWfxjdUo4u1LYvAiA8xMOSJlaFjaSMXKmyFbVlITAYWYoqbeaXw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This was our second day in a row here because it was sooo delicious yesterday. I liked our server from yesterday better (purple haired girl- I think her name was Tasha?) she was great. The food here is out of this world. It’s a cozy little hipster place, great music. Clean washrooms. If you show up and there is a line up, please stay, because I promise it’s worth the wait!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNk5YdsWzVNzwwA_kkRWs6GwvBXaSg7LV_7oKIg&fid=0x0:0xaaebff47a4a99ef2"],"When":"2023-10-21"},{"Name":"Adam M.","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXBezQ5u52QUPfNCS-XISW7oETfNlf5RvdoikJTFUzauPV7HEINiA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Big Flat Pancake has been one of our favorite restaurants since the day they opened. Whether with my family or just the two of us, we’ve enjoyed countless breakfasts here, including many Mother’s Day and Father’s Day celebrations. The restaurant's modern design and simplicity create an upscale breakfast experience, even though it maintains a casual and welcoming vibe.

Seating is limited, and I still recall waiting outside with social distancing protocols in place during the early post-COVID days. Last week, we visited again, and as always, I ordered my favorite: chicken waffles with whipped cream and strawberry topping on the side. My wife, on the other hand, loves trying something different every time we visit. The food arrived quickly, and as usual, it was very tasty.

However, (our visit on Nov 30th)  I do want to share one piece of feedback from this visit. My wife and I were enjoying our coffee after finishing our meal when the server brought the check—completely understandable, especially when tables need to turn over for waiting guests. But this time, there were four empty tables, and no one was waiting. Moments later, while we were still sipping our coffee, the server returned with the cordless payment unit and stood by our table. We were both caught off guard, thinking, “What…?” We paid because the payment unit was already there, and the server was waiting, but the interaction felt rushed.

Having owned a restaurant in downtown Vancouver, I understand the need to turn tables efficiently. That said, there’s an unspoken etiquette between servers and guests, and this instance felt a bit abrupt—particularly since the restaurant wasn’t busy.  It’s a small issue, and I’m sure it wasn’t intentional, but I wanted to share this experience in the hopes it’s not repeated for other guests.

Of course, we will continue visiting Big Flat Pancake because we love the food, atmosphere, and overall experience. This is just some constructive feedback for management or ownership to consider.

Thank you, and see you again soon!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipN3DgZTp8jMRgeo2EOBKceMPW-1SSt0lYSYOwaO&fid=0x0:0xaaebff47a4a99ef2"],"When":"2024-12-10"}]

[{"Name":"Jodine Morehouse","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWkI3ILmstAY-XeAWqv2CETEpjWiJVODW602jRpnYogrvfslqk=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I can’t wait to come back here again! Such fantastic food and a fun environment. The fried chicken was top notch and the waffles were some of the best we’ve ever had. The breakfast truly felt homemade and with care. The kids breakfast was a great size and my kiddo was very happy. Service was okay; you can tell the servers are very busy maintaining a constant flow of customers. It was efficient and we didn’t have to wait overly long for our food. We did have to wait 20 mins to get a table initially, but we wrote our name and number down and were called when our table is ready. There is plenty of free parking around. This has the be the best breakfast I’ve had in the tri cities.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMKJgj8sWDLDS9qegVktaFJLY6wHAIH52u_I1Iw&fid=0x0:0xa167a404bce0a118"],"When":"2024-8-27"},{"Name":"Christina","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVAZU__kcA5bzRg06Xj5DBBJ8cZ62N3LvOHAgj11jS16XxVPZvg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We had a good brunch. Can’t say anything bad about it. Not to pricey and the serving is neither big or small. Customer service is superb. We’ll definitely go back.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPvn0YrbOK9PQexBbmH0uzrLD7g4XyCGtU_9RmR&fid=0x0:0xa167a404bce0a118"],"When":"2024-10-3"},{"Name":"Maria Fernanda Mejia","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIuRq66bP7uwZvuWOAzrXMaIaP65fNk1AbmES51ho5i654OFOA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This is the best place Ive had brunch in Vancouver. Food was delicious, the place was so cozy and had the perfect temperature. I went with my sister and we share the Benny Eggs with cubed potatoes fries and pan cakes and hot chocolate. Everything was so tasty and well done, the eggs were pefectly done and the pancakes werw so fluffy.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMOrT4XQKDGK2dJViD6VsKyNO0Zqf0UnFIb9_9w&fid=0x0:0xa167a404bce0a118"],"When":"2024-10-19"},{"Name":"May Zhagro","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU9KviWdU_UGm6yjKPv-6aFaljm1EC_ecrxYhnt_LO3duiyBNho=s120-c-rp-mo-ba7-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"Korean western breakfast and brunch joint located in downtown Port Coquitlam. Lots of exciting dishes to try with Bulgogi dishes being the most exciting (Bulgogi Benny, Bulgogi pasta, Bulgogi sandwich, etc.). Service was a bit slow as the restaurant was busy. We had to wait around 10 minutes after we put our name and number down to get called. Food was good and presentation was impecable, but the taste was not particularly memorable. The door of the restaurant was open so it attracted a lot of flies from the outside which wasn’t ideal and really made the entire experience not super great.

Interior decor is very interesting with a lot of Lego input.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP4awtX1JY8GFBJy9bWY0sS6Pd9fHU7-n1sKPpK&fid=0x0:0xa167a404bce0a118"],"When":"2024-9-10"},{"Name":"Daniel Jung","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXFE7g6vnjf23CW6mDeh4anchF8fxBs6O5Nsx0bvhepuO3MVzWa=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great brunch spot in the center of Shaugnessy. Came in Sunday around noonish, luckily no lineup. Food took a little bit but was definitely worth it as it tasted great!
Seems like service is team based? It was a little confusing who was taking care of our table. Overall great experience","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPGRk5-xoM7MNas2Lf8X9-8tL5TPa1NyfeG2t5K&fid=0x0:0xa167a404bce0a118"],"When":"2024-7-8"},{"Name":"Helena","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLiYVJyd2ntFwLRumbYS9Kznuj6jXHoPn0UkQ_zdJDM29rWiQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"It’s easy to find the small and clean restaurant on main street in Port Coquitlam downtown. We ordered a Bulgogi Benny and a Corned Beef Skillet. The portion size is quite large. I love the soft and fresh eggs that danced in my plate. The pan fried potatoes were crispy on the outside and tender on the inside.  Overall, their food is so delicious and service is great as well. The only downside is that the food is too salty.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOodTPBFYt_-JZobr-pvtMCbt6_xvN_fc6G6khW&fid=0x0:0xa167a404bce0a118"],"When":"2024-6-20"},{"Name":"JESSICA","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVB2i5CpRP7UX8-wv47l2MrFmMz2VuMLPi87EdWVFtliHFbqvwR=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Cute spot, warm and cozy. Reasonably priced and tasty. Benny’s made on sweet English muffins/crumpets versus traditional. Potatoes very tasty.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNpj7mBBwvQ0YWcrdYBHVE_81woZdvdFQHDUKKA&fid=0x0:0xa167a404bce0a118"],"When":"2024-12-19"},{"Name":"Mike Liu","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocL20X_OxbcK6Mq4LfB8wD0MzYN5bZWaRAXw5XJobEo4cGthsw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I love how everything is flavored really well and that the Korean fusion element is delicious. I got a simple 2 eggs with sausage and hashbrowns. Everything was done really well. Note that the hasbrowns do have a layer of onions as a filling. The cubed potato’s were delicious.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOzoRfYSvHs4qQ-gqmZ89EYwZ0drtW3HbqfgRVO&fid=0x0:0xa167a404bce0a118"],"When":"2024-7-11"}]

[{"Name":"Golnaz J N","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXwh094AvMjRiNSQoo9HjnFTPUMh8c3XSGOFZ78okUlI4KLdqnN=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"While the flavors at the restaurant were good/mediocre, I found the portion sizes to be rather small, especially considering the prices. It left me wishing for a more satisfying dining experience in terms of quantity for the cost.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPwrpADd79VB_I10tydfiqVZopI4cNiy_xhuHjt&fid=0x0:0x165fca77eea385b"],"When":"2024-1-5"},{"Name":"Ayrton Reyes","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUqaKyysn3U53NAKVb3xU5V20dgqy5rNRa3y-q25zmRfboMLVYC=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"I think the restaurant is really good.
A small group of people serve you and they are super friendly.

I’m not to experience in Persian food (actually, is the first time I try it) and I like it. Specially the stew is sooo good, I love it.

So, go and try it, they have good prices and good flavour.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMbQzyJDBPy4CM0XwRO2cgJEuYNWGIuGIKSIwab&fid=0x0:0x165fca77eea385b"],"When":"2023-8-18"},{"Name":"Caspian Painter","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWvx-eR53dJSw__oa-ZvDP8mNQVyf77me-ZC-_9C7210bM7j-Q=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I order Koobideh with Joojeh,cheken boneless,with rice,was completely cooked and tasty marinated.friendly personal.cozy nice music help to have nice vibe.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipN53TeWKSrnWNHLLDjCcPir-aAzAqYi9Vx5Cxov&fid=0x0:0x165fca77eea385b"],"When":"2024-11-9"},{"Name":"Romina K","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV-S5jP3_k1CvTHIXok6wJMjW5UHsiiy2y476TICsrgpKIfmmVG=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"We were disappointed with cost of the food. We ordered Soltani and koobideh, along with zeytoon parvardeh, but found the taste and prices unsatisfactory.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMrbVbkTf4_grwLD3dKeNgT-7V2WiI84WKrqtnc&fid=0x0:0x165fca77eea385b"],"When":"2024-4-22"},{"Name":"Earl Flormata","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUHEYR5crfzT5mFZF5yY6PmVwTawXCmDPm3U8WVZUqH5mb8rOP9MA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Solid food - ok service. Calamari was a little softer than I’m used to but flavour was good (I like it really crispy). Lamb was super tender and delicious but the real MVP was the chicken - cooked to perfection and basically melted in my mouth. I’d visit again.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPu-BeMkBT864bVacd4CCZOj0Rotd2hQMPdCcEi&fid=0x0:0x165fca77eea385b"],"When":"2021-7-9"},{"Name":"Reihaneh Kaviani Rad","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWMqZSe1qXS1AsTFsph8ACG1GgtS7WyGZHzbxgpPr_5zFJRQUVb=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"I recently ordered the Baghali Polo with Lamb Shank from this restaurant, hoping for an authentic Persian meal, but I was extremely disappointed. The lamb shank had an unpleasant smell, and it was undercooked, making it impossible to enjoy. To make matters worse, the rice was also poorly cooked and lacked the fluffy texture that’s expected from Persian rice dishes.

For a restaurant that markets itself as a provider of quality Persian cuisine, this was far from what I anticipated. I won’t be returning, and I certainly cannot recommend this place to anyone","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"n w","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX7UQDByN6t0nePZ4CYWGH0Dj4t17qJ_wKRbK-ykQWwq7mgd96m=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"One of my favourite Persian restaurants in Coquitlam. My go to is the koobideh and it alway delivers! The meat is juicy and flavourful! Sometimes you get lucky and get an extra few itches of meat.

Generous portions, friendly service and reasonable prices…winning formula!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNh5_dvVhZ2WdNhfcPAjtf7aQSYbNBeP0HeQYqR&fid=0x0:0x165fca77eea385b"],"When":"2024-1-25"},{"Name":"Carmen P","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU-nb9czyY24UJWiII_N5K8yz1xXvygxnvgXKZGewDZPl_L__eb=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"A small restaurant that serves delicious and fresh Mediterranean food.  Portion sizes are good. Clean and nice set up. Good customer service.  The place is only a few steps from the Burquitlam Skytrain station. Will definitely go back.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNjYw3P2bENtej52N6d1HZrIxpOAcnuITwjV-3Z&fid=0x0:0x165fca77eea385b"],"When":"2022-5-30"}]

Amazing drink selection, and great prices. What a nice place","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOBoA9lGF-UiunA0jw6LcMMEuu95RwdwkPSA1ob&fid=0x0:0xc29909442b15211c"],"When":"2024-12-14"},{"Name":"Jason","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocK1PnYN1qpNcp156q41vDoPXSrGwSFknRuvrEDhgFtudYYIPw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"I regularly go here to eat mostly every month.. but today it seemed like the lady was in a moody way as I look at her. I know that her older sister works here as well, and she knows my order and knows how to put it and shows respect. It was 1/5 overall and the price was not even worth it.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPnhLd7T6c5qAiZFdgwJHP7Bh7kLkVLFQ_9iWoa&fid=0x0:0xc29909442b15211c"],"When":"2024-7-9"},{"Name":"Scott Lee","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXHpW7vGME__Zs4wKjXR04Upnw88bkVVyz-H2288JsHocq9vI3r=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Staff is super friendly and the Donair is some of the best in town!
