user_reviews:
[{"Name":"Rachel R.","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV8jVjnRga5YL7aTezZpTCt_6ZsgK_4rtqhAOo2ynzGa5S3gkVauA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The food was excellent and very tasty. The prices and portion sizes were reasonable, and the ambiance was perfect. However, the service could have been improved; our server didn’t check on us frequently enough to refill our water or offer us additional drinks. On a positive note, she did give us a complimentary dessert—a slice of cake with a candle—since I was celebrating my birthday. Overall, it was a great choice for a dining experience.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOQMZ8Ffd-cqer3BB8ck4z2tpthF000_2uW65dk&fid=0x0:0x8a834a2eb78c2221"],"When":"2024-11-28"},{"Name":"John Cantillas","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXcyiYFg8BGPrNb-kZxFHp3rbTEqWVw5CXGDd2KlPDKQrWr3m8=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Me and my wife celebrated our wedding anniversary here at The Keg last night. It was our first time dining in into this restaurant. The experience was so great. The food and drinks was phenomenal, the Prime ribs was so good that I finished all the 14oz steak. The complimentary Billy Miner Pie was so freaking good that I want to order another one.

Also, that awesome guy Alex, he is very informative and his service was great. We had an awesome night because he always provide what we need.

To sum up everything, we just had a great experience and definitely going back.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMf39Ur7X14QdujZ1BLpm4yOKMxM-heMK5-5tlC&fid=0x0:0x8a834a2eb78c2221"],"When":"2024-7-10"},{"Name":"May Zhagro","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU9KviWdU_UGm6yjKPv-6aFaljm1EC_ecrxYhnt_LO3duiyBNho=s120-c-rp-mo-ba7-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The Keg is our go-to to celebrate special occasion in our lives. We love the ambiance, the servers, and the way that they cook their steak. Appetizers are also great like the oysters which came with three sauces to try. The potato mash is a great side dish with your steak. The Caesar salad this time around wasn’t as good though, which was a little bit disappointing as I was looking forward to it. Otherwise, we had delicious food and an enjoyable time at The Keg.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP3_RBZeeep_5_lgaUQa4EBUD2lBOw9rDMwVK4s&fid=0x0:0x8a834a2eb78c2221"],"When":"2024-8-24"},{"Name":"Penny Rusty Sophie","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUkGfXMIDqwS_yD1axTk6tkHoLsnybE2ErvKrHMoMIElMJWekI_=s120-c-rp-mo-ba7-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"One of the many Keg locations - we visited in mid-September.

Here's what we had:
Agua Fresca ($7) - not bad.
French Onion Soup ($14) - I liked this and it was cheesy but it was a bit light with the actual amount of onions in the soup.
10 Oz Prime Rib ($42) - Super thin slice of prime rib. They said they were running out if prime rib and I'm wondering if this was actually 10 oz or if they were just trying to stretch it out so bit.
Brussels Sprouts - One of the better items we had on this day.
Sticky Toffee Pudding - A bit of a let down as it wasn't really sticky. It felt more like eating a dense cake. I really wish they would bring back the brownie sundae.

Service was slow","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOqac-co_Pn31iQgOAY87hCJ3joU7ZRzuoy23j_&fid=0x0:0x8a834a2eb78c2221"],"When":"2024-10-22"},{"Name":"Jessameen Dela Peña","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX9mRpmL8-ZJUG7UPFcnsjzRdxjABif-MswbO1rxgJyyWfns8Jd=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"We were quickly accommodated and seated in a nice, cozy booth. The staff was friendly and attentive. While the steak was a bit rarer than we ordered, the lobster was absolutely outstanding—one of the best we've had! We also really enjoyed the generous calamari servings. Overall, a great dining experience!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNtIMhIcglzxiTk1_p7t0oojF32vDHS7aNAPWKq&fid=0x0:0x8a834a2eb78c2221"],"When":"2024-8-24"},{"Name":"Supanun Ploy","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLD8x1Dkib5UdzUFO77N8E3T_ZS53RX2FTmd37gugrcEvk9Yw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"It was our anniversary and we went on Saturday night without booking as we forgot.  Luckily we didn’t have to wait for a long time coz someone cancelled their reservation. In terms of food, onion ring was not seasoned and bbq ribs smell a little but we really enjoy our steak and calamari.

However, before we leave our server try to clear our table but he carry to many stuff at once then he drop cultery on my back. He did apologize and said sorry it’s only a fork. However, once i got up i also found a knife and the back of my shirt is dirty!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNSbRX3nEUs1B5S1OV0vyO9agkfQf7a-0VyVeNe&fid=0x0:0x8a834a2eb78c2221"],"When":"2024-11-23"},{"Name":"Amir Heidari","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVhtGF44y-l1pQZ17Cs4MnWp1KWCMVfN_sfbl-_OCbn3gyQLgGR=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"“The atmosphere of the restaurant was nice, 🤓but the food quality didn’t meet expectations and was average. 😒We ordered lobster, American steak, and French onion soup. The staff weren’t very friendly, and it seemed like they were not in the mood. 😣Overall, it wasn’t bad for trying once.”","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPLcuPlcBy7mVZb2T4r6UZaN-1KvPOqSiSixTM0&fid=0x0:0x8a834a2eb78c2221"],"When":"2024-9-23"},{"Name":"Morteza Khoramshahi","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWXteADRppBLe3Hw2555GOmIwdeoF4ju3YY6aXL5EdFqkJ30LWz=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The best appetizer in town: baked shrimp
Options for all tastes, Steak, seafood and for vegetarian.
Usually I order 2 plates of baked shrimp for start.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOJEyvRrSf7WY14KXQHGEJcvplwZltjyoVzgyQx&fid=0x0:0x8a834a2eb78c2221"],"When":"2024-12-9"}]

user_reviews:
[{"Name":"Marcus L","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXZLCsGchamGOA-Wtg05cndL2yjt6EBGtYR9Y9cWGpcdNb3N09u=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Visiting Pajo’s Fish and Chips was a delightful experience! The bottomless fries are a fantastic treat—crispy on the outside, soft on the inside, and perfectly salted. They pair beautifully with the fish, which is always cooked to perfection with a light, crispy batter that enhances the fresh flavors. The portion sizes are generous, and the ambiance by the water adds a charming touch to the dining experience. The staff is friendly and efficient, making sure that every meal is served hot and fresh. Whether you’re a local or just passing through, Pajo’s offers a memorable meal that you won’t want to miss. Highly recommend for anyone craving quality fish and chips!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNHxNnQvLrsrD_a0OPfXFGXRo-dLjOZDxmJ20I&fid=0x0:0xd47db28fd48f7a58"],"When":"2024-8-10"},{"Name":"Tyler","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX5pgqDcV4jXxCDs44gFpKqBE7-kpDe9pqH0qySpykt9h70rZWn=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"My recent visit to Pajo’s at Rocky Point in Port Moody was a delightful experience. The setting is absolutely stunning—nestled right by the waterfront, it’s the perfect spot to enjoy a meal while soaking in the beautiful views of the harbor.

I ordered the 2-piece cod, and while the batter was a touch soggy by the time I got to it, the overall quality of the dish was still commendable. The cod itself was fresh and perfectly cooked, with a flaky texture that paired well with the flavorful batter. Even with the slight sogginess, the taste didn’t disappoint, and I could tell that the ingredients used were of high quality.

The portions were generous, and the classic combination of fish and chips hit the spot. The fries were crisp and well-seasoned, complementing the fish nicely. What really makes Pajo’s stand out, though, is the atmosphere—there’s something special about enjoying your meal with the gentle breeze from the water and the scenic backdrop of Rocky Point Park.

Overall, I would recommend Pajo’s to anyone looking for a classic fish and chips experience in a relaxed, picturesque setting. It’s a great spot for a casual meal, and I’d definitely return, perhaps a bit earlier next time to enjoy the fish at its crispiest!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOuaZoS9bEz0VVYK3HTmUtNX4MiOs-sXAITMdyV&fid=0x0:0xd47db28fd48f7a58"],"When":"2024-9-1"},{"Name":"Nowell Alcancia","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLDqmFfelGK9VUjuTkW_fGkawlR7g8hmDyutgBrf42CtjnR7rw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Pajo’s is still the best Fish and Chips for me in BC. Nothing beats their crispy yet airy batter that makes every bite so good. It also comes with unlimited chips and drinks which makes the every order worth it.

They also serve fish tacos, hotdogs, and burgers. You can’t go wrong ordering these too.

Only downside is they can get really busy on a crowded sunny day so a lot of patience is needed. But the long wait is truly worth it. A weekday visit should be more quiet.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOeQc-FCoTOjuZIBbGZwZNqHou2W1eMAJ9EYN0D&fid=0x0:0xd47db28fd48f7a58"],"When":"2024-10-8"},{"Name":"D F","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXx4Ba6nMzHNErbU_lUoxlYUXpTpOT6hkVq11LhLdcnXMc9jQAh=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"We received an extra piece of fish on our two take out orders, but we were disappointed to know the reason behind it after. Majority of the chips were from bruised or blackened potatoes. Unfortunately we have a guest who loves chips more than fish. So it was a negative experience to us.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMX-FEXT6roSB7dzCyKglIyMurcUwQq_kh0NPrO&fid=0x0:0xd47db28fd48f7a58"],"When":"2024-7-29"},{"Name":"Ross Duck","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXvGTXjRfmz03idOyXl1jO19QrSo-eJVi7iuRNC3LfSMCt5c8o9=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"I enjoyed the halibut but the breading could be crisper, the food I quite pricy but worth the price , the drinks and chips are bottomless and the employees are friendly but extremely busy even at random times , I appreciate the decision to keep the old tables once you got new ones to create improved  seating","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPV9dPXqtPyMPUHUTqfD5OgKTxBv3WwXZKs_wOQ&fid=0x0:0xd47db28fd48f7a58"],"When":"2024-8-6"},{"Name":"Matthew","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW5iydY0u4F5rNajxlfLEGtl5LlLWi7bPLgFCMpJT9LRW5eTPy4=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"I recently visited the Pajo's location at Rocky Point and had the two-piece fish. Unfortunately, the experience didn't live up to my expectations. The fish was quite soggy, and the breading fell right off, which was disappointing. This location doesn't compare to the Richmond one, which has always been the best in my opinion. The Richmond location consistently delivers a much better quality of fish and overall dining experience. If you're looking for the best Pajo's experience, I'd recommend heading to Richmond. It was good fish though.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPVhn4VpZjc2bfQOZOXoa5jDjPjDe088I8Sm0T3&fid=0x0:0xd47db28fd48f7a58"],"When":"2024-9-2"},{"Name":"K","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXRwpWAz0-Yg4cI6ZsOAY9CncZqRN4a6o8nP7KlskI9G71qjLadgg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Stopped by World Famous Pajo's fish and chips today on my trip from Niagara Falls .  I got the one piece cod and chips which was enough for one. The batter was light and airy , the cod was fresh and delicious and fries were some of the best I've tried .

This place is inside Rocky Point Park which is beautiful! The staff were very friendly and quick taking orders.  There are lots of  parking spots around here .Picnic tables not really enough for this place as it's very busy take away.

Definitely recommend trying this place out! 👌 . I only gave 4 stars because there are too many Crows that prevent you having a peaceful place to eat 🙄 but amazing scenery makes up for this 😁","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNVJwEAK2M48GK6zkVXe2rlgQ4j9Ns1UN28FzWd&fid=0x0:0xd47db28fd48f7a58"],"When":"2023-8-8"},{"Name":"Saskia Asyari","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXOw-vGRppaZWH-87l0DTjRp6cH2-cGmCr2why8D5leomPAj1GywA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Decided to try this because of the review and because I heard that they don’t use beer on the batter. I ordered the squid because it’s their seasonal menu. Surprisingly the squid is sooo soft and not chewy at all. Easy to eat. The batter is light. And for this seasonal menu, they have different shapes for the chips. The sunset view at Rocky Point is a bonus while enjoying it as a dinner. They’re open until 8pm throughout the summer but I’m not sure if the opening hours will change in fall/winter.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOdtn0aHF5YdkGzEZjy7oXoUHIXdQ-KVLKCqOyP&fid=0x0:0xd47db28fd48f7a58"],"When":"2023-8-29"}]

[{"Name":"judy lam","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJxQFsQ_JnNA4CIO0ttfhv0mp59ggfnPiiIcA0n0F4ju1lLlg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This is the location that I return every year for my Christmas dinner Great atmosphere, great food and inviting customer services, making this a great places for any occasion for hang out. Especially Jennifer, she was a fantastic staff who look after us all the time. Gave us recommendations that exceeded our needs. Thank you for spending the night with us!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOQRHmPptwa-QTYI6RBVTzuf0k2O0LCeiTgymy1&fid=0x0:0x29a9313c1a6dc6ea"],"When":"2024-12-15"},{"Name":"Martin Dichupa","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXNDFb5fEpdn1lV1xMh2_IBXJ0jnoQ6_jFy0aGbcE01nG9ImDpM=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We recently held our joint Christmas and retirement party at JOEY Coquitlam, and it was an absolutely fantastic experience! From start to finish, the food was exceptional, and the service was top-notch.

A special shoutout to our server, Lexie, who truly went above and beyond to ensure our group felt welcomed and well taken care of. Her attentiveness and cheerful demeanor made the evening even more memorable.

Thank you to the entire team at JOEY Coquitlam for providing a 5-star experience that we’ll all be talking about for a long time! Highly recommended for any special occasion or group gathering.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP3n5_s8dop4ZL1-3yNhteI5QvPuYJCiRWWE2GX&fid=0x0:0x29a9313c1a6dc6ea"],"When":"2024-12-20"},{"Name":"Jennifer Bee","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXFO0fgPBTIA1yxL3IXSghRJ6EmshLC1YB1a72b-xeg3kpjHx0=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"My first time at this location and I was happy with everything. My MIL and I were offered sparking wine while we waited for a table - that was a treat! Fish tacos were good and my husband and MIL ended their meals as well. Lovely glass sculpture in the dining room - great atmosphere!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOO8s2wbmxDA3OW_Q-Fei91wBIxqxuBwFkGJq2I&fid=0x0:0x29a9313c1a6dc6ea"],"When":"2024-10-11"},{"Name":"Annie Lee","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXeiXkcyhTInf8H3hsa41qWaj0-pj73GTGWAJSoVjdLilWPzd7b=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Upon arrival, guests are warmly welcomed with complimentary champagne. They also surprised us with a complimentary birthday dessert, making the experience even more special.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPd2rvjU8Iq0HggwcxRdQ3iUjkHCt1i_xlP_Pk&fid=0x0:0x29a9313c1a6dc6ea"],"When":"2024-11-25"},{"Name":"Kayla Cochrane","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLPCxHm8VITPtk2g9XDHBWfyZtomSP_ai-b0ipoJVYmIOKKEg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We had our staff party here tonight; Bianca and Jesse were amazing to us! Bianca was so sweet and attentive - Jesse gave us a great set up and was so welcoming! Food, overall service, and atmosphere 10/10","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO4lMwDnQhZroZ3cc7kUnByVwVgdllfheVWkikv&fid=0x0:0x29a9313c1a6dc6ea"],"When":"2024-11-10"},{"Name":"Jamie Brand","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXKYZgBpqiELo9hDY5N-5k-gorixQvb36QqVW-qrYDjhXG_wuiwQQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"One of the best dining experiences I’ve had in a long time. Our server was extremely personable, and I don’t think I’ve ever had a French dip like that before. Our steaks were done to perfection, and I appreciated a couple of drink recommendations they made. We were treated like royalty, and I can tell the GM takes great pride in her restaurant. After 15 years of enjoying Joey, this is by far the best time I’ve had.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMnXXGCOP-ZGWLV7lPed7ddiNLbfTV_EgEvP9fY&fid=0x0:0x29a9313c1a6dc6ea"],"When":"2024-8-16"},{"Name":"Jim O'Grady","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWJGgsb2sCcFjV1Mve3M5vv3QuR2DK9KBJEfmo_m9dlw5ULu0-QIA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I recently arranged a birthday lunch for an old friend at Joeys, and the experience exceeded my expectations. I would highly recommend Joeys for any special occasion.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPl7xObgarUbqZ5ioLnryyK2VjAiQ9nUewKH8G-&fid=0x0:0x29a9313c1a6dc6ea"],"When":"2024-8-16"},{"Name":"camille sal.","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU7Ks7QNJJsJdwwFb2BHOVyVy0T4aFfD9IIuenSGN5xn7y4mt27=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Joey’s restaurant, specifically this location, is an amazing dining experience! Highly recommend this place to anyone looking for great food, excellent service, and a fantastic overall experience!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPEvE0G517vl-jg_1k27I_p0eCrQDbGt4SvClOA&fid=0x0:0x29a9313c1a6dc6ea"],"When":"2024-12-23"}]

2 stars - I do not recommend it.

Service was great and the server was a great helping us figured out what to order for our group.

We ordered a combo B for 8 ppl and some extra dishes. The food was amazing ! Really loved the fried rice, ginger beef, green beans, and fried squid ! I also love that they have seasoning at every table. I am a sucker for their hot sauce.

We noticed that they had an extra room with a bar , tables, and a karaoke system. Looks like a great place to book an event/ gathering.

Would definitely come back here again for some comfort canadian chinese food. I'm also interested in trying their breakfast in the near future :)","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOqd9fV6wMT1TELGzoTSGTelTMfPiwt0tnUEvag&fid=0x0:0x318b3df216b4a874"],"When":"2024-3-19"},{"Name":"Truckloadofrhymes canada","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXkND8fxIF1Oqb83wPDair5hXJ85P4wpjp70bDsHPXiyojrgbkuIQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This place always has good food. Servers were super friendly and food is so good. Given the fact that you cannot really find the restaurant this affordable this good.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMT4_PggqssU5QpyUWU0Ylqz8PNHV91LwR0XZsh&fid=0x0:0x318b3df216b4a874"],"When":"2024-3-16"},{"Name":"kiana Liu","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWKoxfjAHBiXenysk2Q-KlulFH1fxjGp6FrGPGGTkK41ibofwbwig=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"I got food poisoning from this place and been living in the washroom for past 7 days. We ordered 3 dishes which they got 2 of them wrong. One dish we realized it’s wrong, when we asked her, she was like “what about this dish? Do you want to try this instead?”
My husband can’t have seafood and the dish had shrimps in it, that’s how I knew for sure we didn’t order that dish.
The second dish we didn’t realize until the end.
The quality of their food was really bad. We went there for all the good reviews and we were super disappointed. Will never return.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO-wQu4pwQGfRKnSX8sP3y7dUGvJGajvqAJG35E&fid=0x0:0x318b3df216b4a874"],"When":"2023-8-5"},{"Name":"KA T","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVaR7ml2dkrIOrwgU_-kQ-HRh1gdXFY-Mwfz5VTGuLsK_EtLSkR=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"We stopped in here for breakfast as we were staying at the attached Ramada. There was 4 of us (two young kids and two adults). The breakfast itself was ok, nothing special at all. The coffee was really good though. The service was embarrassing. The server walked away without taking one of our orders and seemed almost bothered that we would come in to have breakfast. The prices are definitely not worth the quality of food. When we received the our bill, the prices were higher than what was noted on the menu, so this was quite alarming. They need to update their menu to reflect what they charge because that was really shady. Our bill was over $80 for four simple breakfasts. Save your money and go somewhere else.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Mike Medcalf","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU1rixyxiw07idcZpYCUo6royGxGKqfnZDSFo9vAAuERRuqgDflAA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Amazing prices. user_reviews: [{"Name":"W P","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocILxAIkDJOMkU9eiOhUr1vp_EVknYE6-JpPp2DlzYH5UXNOLQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The food at JFY is absolutely amazing! Every dish was full of flavor and beautifully presented. Highly recommend if you're looking for a great meal.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNX6Vqs_OyudkThAmeHarsQ8Us00FjV57PICm5g\u0026fid=0x0:0x741d98414591f8a2"],"When":"2024-8-22"},{"Name":"Cher Lin","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKuJb4AXSXpx8-KCPDQBZHJ2K3rRI-J71p19_u0fIii9KOuBhQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I LOVE the food here and I believe the service and atmosphere will improve once they have more dine in customers! I’ve been looking for authentic Chinese food restaurant like this in Coquitlam especially with spicy cuisine but also the typical noodles, dumplings, etc… I was told the chef is from more northern China and the lady helped us is from Guang Dong and they have been in the restaurant business for decades, I didn’t ask too much about their stories but all I know is this is their newest adventure! I am glad!!!! I see people order for take outs and some people even order everyday but from 7:15 to 9:30 on a Saturday, there were only 4 dine in tables including us, so they do not have extra servers, which is totally understandable… therefore if you are looking for services like cactus club, it’s not going to happen any time soon… nonetheless, I rate the service 10/10 for their friendliness and knowledge of the food, suggestions, the only reason why I give 4 star on google is because I want to stay true to what to expect for the next customers, atmosphere is 3/5 because it is a little dated but to some people this could be a 5/5.. nostalgic feeling! Overall, this is a must try and if you are a local, you might make this restaurant a regular thing… I am going back to try more dishes! Everything we ordered were amazing! Not overly salty or oily and packed with the right amount of spices without being too spicy, we did ask for mild spice. 10/10 for food! Please go!!!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOYRx0aAchW6Be7b-wVxwYTWSPczodN3XwfU85Q\u0026fid=0x0:0x741d98414591f8a2"],"When":"2024-3-10"},{"Name":"Pej Namshirin","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXt8TlEL2i2Xn40BjhRE9J4no4CShDCK1NmCQWJYbCcLJNbs-s8rQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"A little bit quiet on a Thursday night, but we came in hungry and left completely satisfied with full bellies. Excellent service: as if we were guests in their home. Everything was tasty, nice portions, good value. Get the House Special Crispy Noodles. We'll be back.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOHVvR21V2RyCPQ2Kgq5IyCxs5g1UwLpS-WTUxy\u0026fid=0x0:0x741d98414591f8a2"],"When":"2023-12-15"},{"Name":"Rob S","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKl1FCoFebTKBGR8qu0CXJcgOpg1C_GaPiRgmFNkViRrR_-bA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Came here for dinner. Something we didn’t quite understand is how they measure how much to put into each burrito/ bowl. She kinda just eyeballed it . It ended up being a lot for me so I have a lot left over. The food was okay, gave me Chipotle vibes . The beef was not that good, and was pretty watery. The shrimp tacos were good though , lots of toppings to choose from","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNv3DAoyCc7AbEsEv8sSPT1-pEMwSLFFzWYvn32&fid=0x0:0x52fdc8e4b81cb23c"],"When":"2023-5-13"},{"Name":"Ethan Zargo","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKr14nMiH0arOiNIGBCVUJZASKmpuMReAAHWxIU0eaIBW6X4w=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Food was fresh, and tasted really good.
Prices are on point and affordable specially considering the quality of food.

The lady that served us, was friendly and did her job nicely.

From out side seems a Mexican fast food, but inside, Surprisingly great food and service

U can modify your meal to be a keto friendly food.

Not sure in their food, and if there is, is acceptable amount.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Melanie Dixon","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWJEt2dgS3rw3x9ZLO2754OWoBp-FwxRXEw0ZX9bvTBfCKLzkzF=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"I only ate half of my veggie quesadilla. Besides the half tomato/half onion non-salsa, I couldn't quite figure out why I didn't like it. The next day I took the last 2 slices out of the fridge and heated them up and figured it out. The mozzarella cheese was awful. The veggies were heavily coated in salt. This is unhealthy. Should have had some chili pepper spice in it and more than onions, tomatoes and beans. My advice is to head to Chopped Leaf nearby, as their quesadillas are good. Why? The quesadilla wraps are crunchy on the outside, just the right amount of salt and seasoning, a variety of veggies, not just 2, and the cheese tastes like real cheese.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Aspen Barker","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIM_O_wJ2-kAj73KcPl2xdRYLphhULu7JrQ4BP2S-44M6KvEg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"First time visiting, Anita behind the counter was so friendly and helpful! Thank you!","Images":null,"When":""}]

[{"Name":"May Zhagro","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU9KviWdU_UGm6yjKPv-6aFaljm1EC_ecrxYhnt_LO3duiyBNho=s120-c-rp-mo-ba7-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Jimmy’s Place Restaurant really has the old timey diner feel. Serving breakfast and lunch, it is conveniently located at the plaza with Lifelabs and is easy to find parking. The menu board is all in chalk and it seems like a Korean couple who is running /working this place. We ordered the big breakfast, French toast, and a cup of coffee which came to $35. Food came out within 15 minutes and the plating was nice and neat. With the booths and the older decor, it really felt like a nostalgic diner film scene and a great place to enjoy homey food and catch up with friends.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP6q_0noapEk5_Wf4UXkv8j8w491LWKMjmP7NTY&fid=0x0:0xe9900134f02548b5"],"When":"2024-11-13"},{"Name":"jsflysrc","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX4HguzwfacbLZjrtaRdONz-ndjKHzniCouQ6QvYeTAM2_r7Nk=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I had the egg benny with ham. I requested egg medium, and it was cooked perfectly. The hash brown was amazing. It was thin and spread out and it was crispy on the outside. The atmosphere was nostalgic and cozy.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMSOZ6vilACZEb3ydgCdKEVZ3w2udG1VxhlJQNF&fid=0x0:0xe9900134f02548b5"],"When":"2024-12-14"},{"Name":"Kim N","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXbdjDpWyXnvjc80j1Uggeb1c_m_wfTt6lOvg1Z_TeE5AinsEnY=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"The egg benny didn't have enough sauce on it and the amount of toppings kinda overshadowed the egg flavour. However the harsh browns were done perfectly, soft inside, crunchy outside.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMTAmrbxOpmEngo8zpyDzgNfS7zlzrnxop8lJrt&fid=0x0:0xe9900134f02548b5"],"When":"2024-12-11"},{"Name":"Helen D.","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXyu5Lt8dplX_J1Zs_BtplHu93y_yusuUNzg33OmEALysRDnBlb=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I never would have guessed in a million years that the food at Jimmy’s is this good 👍 I ran out of lunch options and decided to roll the dice - randomly check out a restaurant with decent reviews on google. That’s how i discovered this hidden gem. I ordered club sandwich with a side of fries, perfectly golden and incredibly crunchy! Also 💕 love that menu was hand written with chalks - adding so much charm to this place","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM65HEEiDJvwD9oWXkN5hNgEoYbELib1cZicna7&fid=0x0:0xe9900134f02548b5"],"When":"2024-6-25"},{"Name":"Daisy Shim","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocL7FlXh5li6Gu28BxP6ht6L_GsITqqbf4cvI2UudicO556H1w=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I found this place to be a cozy and warm Western-style brunch restaurant. It feels like a granny's home, with clean and high-quality food that's reasonably priced. I hope they keep the restaurant running forever so I can visit from time to time when I need that cozy and warm atmosphere :)","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOPKnKkLYPsKxF-BiIKdw6Otwg74DVWf7EpxCyw&fid=0x0:0xe9900134f02548b5"],"When":"2024-7-1"},{"Name":"Zach R","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVNyXkBQi0QB1KYWxYBw3_TLlNrsg-jgaNGjTyuUBUiNpV93KBD=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"My favourite breakfast place around the hash browns are incredibly delicious, very reasonable prices and quick service I would eat here every single day if I could.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOJ-3-q5CTC-u4Kmgk7xe1_79XDfTVQpsykLq7i&fid=0x0:0xe9900134f02548b5"],"When":"2024-12-21"},{"Name":"Monette Perez Mendoza","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLz9X9ntKCoshwxo5hjj_35EdDYpSvyTQYpdQotXn5no4bDwA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"We were so disappointed with this place. My daughter and I ordered 2 eggs 2 pancakes and 2 sausages. Pancake is very thin and dry and very small. For the price it wasn’t worth it. Another order was French toast which tasted just like toast and bacon which was over cooked and burned. There was no refill on coffee because she never went around. The order cost us over $50. We should have gone to another restaurant.
I’m just sharing how we felt. Maybe we just ordered wrong. Now we know NOT to go back again. Sorry.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOeTp5XuKH0_Uf6BP_Z559hhKuO9HLsJn6W4Zp2&fid=0x0:0xe9900134f02548b5"],"When":"2024-10-21"},{"Name":"Nathan Woods","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWYlKwIGO9PHjqLgc7mRGN7qYIzJ_Yb1JOij4343pL12ye4fG4D-w=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Everybody reviewing this place like it's a five star restaurant.

It's a diner.

The breakfast is on the expensive side. Two eggs, two sausages, shredded hashbrowns and a couple pieces of toast. Add a coffee and it's nearly 20$.

I might be inclined to give it another try for a hamburger. But for breakfast, I think I'll pass...","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOrR37BOe0dFo67nOCgCyVZYXFFhAOByccIj-AW&fid=0x0:0xe9900134f02548b5"],"When":"2024-7-31"}]

[{"Name":"Jizelle Garcia","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJyzSeMMMmQJNd8WDethczxr3uXNdjORpbX-butxHOVp0pXxetz=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Some of the best pizza I've had in a long time! The toppings were very creative, flavourful, and generous, and the dough was perfectly fluffy yet crisp. However, I do wish there was a vegan protein option for the pizzas. As for the salad it was a bit plain, and could use salt and some citrus, sweet, or creamy element but other than that I love it here! It was clean, cozy, modern and the service was great. They refilled my water before I even noticed it was getting empty, which is rare, and made conversation with us. Super sweet and attentive and the menu was accomodating for vegans. If the other pizzas are just as good as this one it'll definitely be my new go-to pizza spot! Will be back for sure.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMcvNmtsIkLhcyj8JI6yUt7uQnvyfkT5VRXrazo&fid=0x0:0x5b0831c3c22b0f30"],"When":"2024-7-6"},{"Name":"Jacki Steenken","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW9lMdLA_qxtmWTAQxT5wEGeD8f4GuKMxB8fTHyr7TGaIRX-Vt7=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Pizza is delicious!!  Original brussel sprout is definitely a favourite.  Hand tossed crust, always fresh.  Service is friendly, timely and unobtrusive.  Casual atmosphere, good wine choices, if a bit expensive.  Devon is awesome!!!  We have seen this place go through transformations and its current character and menu is the best!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"TJ Bar","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVNV5JMIsKH69fAGV6iM37bM0CI-DVYRNcijWMK-jJBIbmjr1g=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Nice little Place great comfy vibe menu is a bit small not much selection but must say the Buffalo Cauliflower Wings are By Far best thing on the menu..","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNWwzmqMTGv036UKxUNe_VBSfTGsP7-qYDJqKOC&fid=0x0:0x5b0831c3c22b0f30"],"When":"2024-10-28"},{"Name":"Tal Gill","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXdcX5lteMW7YGdoBC5XzBwLnJaPXqogWXPCXIWpiTDj9lk9pSg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I recently had the pleasure of dining at Scratch Kitchen, and I must say it was an exceptional experience. From the moment my wife and I walked in, we were greeted with warm hospitality and a cozy ambiance. The star of our dining experience, however, was undoubtedly our fantastic waitress, Jacoba. Her attentive and friendly service truly enhanced our evening.

One of the highlights of our visit to Scratch Kitchen was undoubtedly the pizza. The moment our pizzas arrived at our table, we knew we were in for a treat. The flavors were out of this world, and the attention to detail was evident in every bite. The crust was perfectly crispy on the outside while remaining delightfully chewy on the inside. Each slice was generously topped with high-quality ingredients, creating a medley of flavors that danced on our taste buds.

What impressed us even more was the restaurant's commitment to catering to different dietary preferences. My wife, being a vegan, was thrilled to find a variety of options tailored to her needs. Her vegan pizza was a masterpiece in itself, with a delectable combination of plant-based cheeses, fresh vegetables, and a flavorful tomato sauce. It's not easy to find vegan pizzas that taste this good, and Scratch Kitchen exceeded our expectations.

Beyond the exceptional food, the atmosphere at Scratch Kitchen was warm and inviting. The rustic decor and cozy seating added to the overall charm of the restaurant. The staff members were attentive and friendly, and it was evident that they took pride in providing a memorable dining experience for their guests.

Overall, I highly recommend Scratch Kitchen to anyone seeking a remarkable dining experience. Whether you're a pizza lover or have specific dietary preferences, this restaurant caters to a variety of tastes and will leave you craving more. Make sure to request Jacoba as your waitress for exceptional service. With its phenomenal pizzas, commitment to dietary options, and inviting atmosphere, Scratch Kitchen truly stands out as a culinary gem.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOK0K5gpP7ptzf4xbCBZ-G_2uArYscd_dPS7qzs&fid=0x0:0x5b0831c3c22b0f30"],"When":"2023-6-1"},{"Name":"Adele Barnett","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJlKeNpkF3-ajmNXl3fkiMG0jQqNqTy_pscUNVSFDGdQdanzA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We love Scratch Kitchen! First of all they’re at Dollarton Village so parking is never an issue. The restaurant indoor outdoor seating is so comfortable. The tables are nicely spaced so that you don’t feel like you’re sitting on top of each other. We are always very warmly welcomed by our name every time we are there. And we know some of their names too; Eric, Devin, Jacoba, Danielle. Sorry we can’t name everyone.
